Batman TellTale Series Season 2 Enemy Within;Batman TellTale Series Season 2 : Enemy Within;Batman TellTale Series Season 2 Enemy Within;;videos\Batman TellTale Series Season 2 Enemy Within (2017).mp4;OK;images\Batman TellTale Series Season 2 Enemy Within (2017).webp;;Amazon;Telltale Games;Telltale Games;08/08/2017;In this latest chapter, both Bruce Wayne and Batman will be forced into precarious new roles. The Riddler has returned to terrorize Gotham City, but his gruesome puzzles merely foreshadow an even greater crisis. With the arrival of a ruthless federal agent and the return of a still nascent Joker, Batman must navigate uneasy alliances while Bruce Wayne undertakes a perilous series of deceptions. Which of Batman's new allies will you choose to trust? And how deep into the darkness will you let Bruce descend?;Adventure, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/675260/154595/5808ccefec2dc5c5ffe96940995410102265a638/1750569836/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1522170171;amazon_12b2a663-73da-46cd-938a-5e4fdcac7d38;steam_675260;gog_2135854393;xboxone_338995079;psn_CUSA09155_00;psn_CUSA09313_00;psn_CUSA09158_00;psn_CUSA09238_00;humble_batman_theenemywithin_thetelltaleseries_telltale;test_CUSA09313_00;nswitch_0100E6300AA3A000;humble_batman_theenemywithin_thetelltaleseries_steam;xboxone_store_idC0DGRH3HK0VK;itch_49ab5efda6b420ac7cd92165049ae35244801b68a108fc8f9f771432;origin_b79b50796e1e00f18b28681202f29137b664cee8;origin_85af873cb8ef937340b96d49e6337d27df2357be5829238f1456cd880236f622;humble_batman_theenemywithin_thetelltaleseries_bundle_steam;twitch_12b2a663-73da-46cd-938a-5e4fdcac7d38;amazon_12b2a663-73da-46cd-938a-5e4fdcac7d38;test_5c3bb1b7cdf10ccfea1aace51482d7069b4af0c7;amazon_04bc29a1-f689-4978-b074-fe84bda5f5bf;generic_51141473860007695;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
10 Second Ninja X;10 Second Ninja X;10 Second Ninja X;;videos\10 Second Ninja X (2016).mp4;OK;images\10 Second Ninja X (2016).webp;;Amazon;Four Circle Interactive;Curve Digital;19/07/2016;"10 SECOND NINJA X is a blisteringly fast, satisfyingly difficult and surprisingly methodical sidescroller which tasks you with completing each level in ten seconds or less. No lengthy checkpoint gaps. No cluttered control scheme. No hand holding. Get that three star rating, yo! You got this.

1 star. Again. 1 star. Again. 2 stars! Again. Back to 1 star. DAMN IT. Again...

100 levels including all 40 original 10 Second Ninja levels remastered in HD. Individual leaderboards for each level. Unlockables and collectibles.";Indie, Platform, Puzzle, Arcade, Fighting;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/435790/63051/7889665d389a4fbe8bbefd6e4f3a56a5fc9d7d62/1751284716/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1466609338;amazon_13a0d6e1-fce9-4b6c-9f3a-582a0f04b6b7;steam_435790;xboxone_28833378;psn_CUSA04692_00;psn_CUSA04748_00;humble_10secondninjax_gamemakeredition;humble_13a0d6e1-fce9-4b6c-9f3a-582a0f04b6b7;amazon_13a0d6e1-fce9-4b6c-9f3a-582a0f04b6b7;twitch_13a0d6e1-fce9-4b6c-9f3a-582a0f04b6b7;psvita_CUSA04748_00;test_CUSA04748_00;3ds_13a0d6e1-fce9-4b6c-9f3a-582a0f04b6b7;humble_10secondninja_x_steam;test_CUSA04692_00;steam_steam_435790;amazon_425c51e1-daf6-47ed-a0de-143b2d0478a0;generic_51141226417445796;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
