The Secret of Monkey Island Special Edition;The Secret of Monkey Island: Special Edition;The Secret of Monkey Island Special Edition;;videos\The Secret of Monkey Island Special Edition (2009).mp4;OK;images\The Secret of Monkey Island Special Edition (2009).webp;;Amazon;LucasArts;LucasArts, Aspyr Media;15/07/2009;"Relive the swashbuckling humorous misadventures of the wannabe pirate Guybrush Threepwood!
Back by popular demand, The Secret of Monkey Island: Special Edition faithfully re-imagines the internationally-acclaimed classic game.
The game's twisty plot leads our naive hero on a hilarious, swash-buckling search for the fabled secret of Monkey Island. Tales of pirate wealth lure him to the port of Mêlée with high hopes, no money, and insatiable curiosity. If clever enough, he will win the confidence of Mêlée's pirates and find himself blown by the winds of fate toward the terrifying and legendary Monkey Island - an adventure that would chill the bones of even the most bloodthirsty buccaneer.";Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/32360/571298/ac40002b704d40ec4fe2a6d91d0f8a883468a1a0/1750480953/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1684960482;amazon_6ea8a67f-b21c-425b-9d1b-ce207e30ae2f;steam_32360;gog_1207666253;xboxone_1055569898;gameuk_monkey;gameuk_monkey-vga;egg_monkey;egg_monkey-vga;egg_monkey-1;egg_monkey-ega;amiga_monkey-1;amiga_monkey-ega;amiga_monkey;amiga_monkey-vga;amiga_monkey-de;psn_NPUB30197_00;psx_The Secret of Monkey Island®: Special Edition;test_/the-secret-of-monkey-island-special-edition-free-download/;steam_32480;xboxone_1480657301;amazon_6ea8a67f-b21c-425b-9d1b-ce207e30ae2f;twitch_6ea8a67f-b21c-425b-9d1b-ce207e30ae2f;test_ce5af8db3c531ecc33d8484534405539d18eef46;test_0e4f678be8d003539fbe0a3c5bd60f86950fcb2f;test_f669af3509242c15895b3a3b4af8048c72b0e03c;test_cbd3737144ca969a9dee1843580bf9572d3a96ec;test_085f35a040aa77ce3e4fc4176bbd5dddeb62230b;test_695853be13003d08701fecb425772d8b945c9f69;test_32407b3200e17d2f4e1ded159a602be85b152b85;amiga_The Secret of Monkey Island: Special Edition;test_4e419ebe4daf209028c80bdc212dbd0933adb9ea;humble_secretofmonkeyisland_specialedition_bundle_steam;test_8e07ef8fc0e2248903da9064bd4b3e10b352c737;test_b6125bbd2a4bffac7a314bbf7359df5a48036df7;amazon_4abd554e-0bf8-3c5b-8761-f04d45a3a41e;generic_51295403152042794;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Beholder;Beholder;Beholder;;videos\Beholder (2016).mp4;OK;images\Beholder (2016).webp;;Amazon, Epic Games Store;Warm Lamp Games;Alawar Entertainment;09/11/2016;A totalitarian State controls every aspect of private and social life. Laws are oppressive. Surveillance is total. Privacy is dead. You are a State-installed manager of an apartment house. The State requires you to spy on your tenants, and report any illegal or subversive activity. However, you can also choose to keep the information to yourself, or use it to blackmail the residents, resulting in a multitude of choices and endings.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/475550/76568/a0694df89bb0332d5283719a84a9cb266057a842/1750535248/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1476703328;amazon_77616bb4-bb8e-4029-9ddf-b51a9e5b761d, epic_6fa12837a99e4b16bc21d7719b3c401e;steam_475550;gog_2146639343;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001958;steam_535610;humble_beholder;humble_beholder_bundle_steam;humble_beholder_steam;nswitch_0100D1300C1EA000;xboxone_1760657439;test_/beholder-free-download/;test_beholder;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001958@subscription;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0000499@subscription;amazon_77616bb4-bb8e-4029-9ddf-b51a9e5b761d;twitch_77616bb4-bb8e-4029-9ddf-b51a9e5b761d;test_467d2c71c1508ebe7831abbb3dec8488bac473d5;test_11eb50a6a7db4b04d4c82d8f83ea3706c1921de9;test_618858d5bd5ca6eb6d90efbbc187c9a6be5b9ba7;3ds_77616bb4-bb8e-4029-9ddf-b51a9e5b761d;fanatical_beholder;test_3b55ce371f6492f45f79af0990be9befe39e00a4;test_fa95f45b3e16427b781f2d0110dcaf73ce3e1497;test_gfn_475550;test_016e7965301aece7cd8e4c468d6f5682d1b74679;test_890f8ee2e23851609ea4746d296d3d201e033466;test_475550;epic_6fa12837a99e4b16bc21d7719b3c401e;amazon_fcbca3ec-6883-fb04-079f-5f4316ba65c3;generic_51141486310553403;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
