Twinkle Star Sprites;Twinkle Star Sprites;Twinkle Star Sprites;;;OK;images\Twinkle Star Sprites (1996).webp;;Amazon;;ADK;25/01/1996;Twinkle Star Sprites is a 1996 competitive scrolling shooter arcade game originally created by ADK. It was ADK's last production for the Neo-Geo platform. The gameplay, which can be characterized as a combination of a fixed shooter and a versus puzzle game, uses combinations of shots, as well as timed power-ups to attempt to damage the opponent. These attacks also serve as counters to the opponent's attack.;Shooter;;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.2cc687be-9547-42ef-b07d-cb3de979671f;humble_66cea04c-bedf-4b41-b484-743ba3424657;dc_Twinkle Star Sprites;saturn_Twinkle Star Sprites;test_b708ed3cc0379f023fb1af69daf8994cf2040e50;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.2cc687be-9547-42ef-b07d-cb3de979671f;test_60e139df371c9a6f209c79fff533ae2d0697259b;test_faa1c7c18d23393494218391641956e18fe233ce;test_94eeeae18ad21779d51222d13da4fdd1f5704f0c;test_36d14de5d282376b6a304c5dceb5df3982c94bfe;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.2cc687be-9547-42ef-b07d-cb3de979671f;generic_51295415919374729;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
