Golfie;Golfie;Golfie;;videos\Golfie (2023).mp4;OK;images\Golfie (2023).webp;;Amazon;Triheart Studio;;19/01/2023;Golfie is a run-based, roguelike minigolf deck builder. Play through procedurally-generated levels, build a deck of crazy card abilities, and try to beat all 18 holes. Pick your route carefully because no two runs – or shots – are the same!;Indie, Platform, Puzzle, Sport, Card & Board Game;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1579020/592349/0f0424efc349aa899f6ee3a40d5566d77b019f70/1751005680/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1690724156;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.9274ae27-f99c-4594-a917-9cc01e3f65ad;steam_1579020;steam_1662190;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.9274ae27-f99c-4594-a917-9cc01e3f65ad;generic_54532653652798054;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Planescape Torment Enhanced Edition;Planescape Torment: Enhanced Edition;Planescape Torment Enhanced Edition;;videos\Planescape Torment Enhanced Edition (2017).mp4;OK;images\Planescape Torment Enhanced Edition (2017).webp;;Amazon;Beamdog;Beamdog;11/04/2017;"""Discover an incredibly rich story and a unique setting unlike anything else in fantasy. Defeat strange and alien creatures, engage in rich dialogue, and explore the dark and dangerous Planescape setting in this 50+ hour RPG classic.

Millions of Planescape: Torment fans have enjoyed the strange and dangerous city of Sigil and surrounding planes through the Nameless One's eyes. Now it’s your turn. This is Planescape: Torment like you’ve never seen before.

Enhanced Edition - Key Features:
- Enhanced Planescape: Chris Avellone, Lead Designer on Planescape Torment, has partnered with Beamdog to curate gameplay updates, bug fixes, and enhancements to best capture his original vision for the game.

- Remastered Music: The full Planescape: Torment soundtrack has been remastered in-game to add more depth to Sigil and the multiverse.

- 4K Interface: Sigil has never looked this good! The interface of Planescape: Torment has been rebuilt in high definition with tons of new convenience features.

