Galaxy of Pen and Paper;Galaxy of Pen and Paper;Galaxy of Pen and Paper;;videos\Galaxy of Pen and Paper (2017).mp4;OK;images\Galaxy of Pen and Paper (2017).webp;;Amazon;Behold Studios;Behold Studios;26/07/2017;Galaxy of Pen & Paper is a turn-based meta RPG about a group of players rolling dice in the year 1999! Create your own game master and RPG party, as they roleplay, explore distant planets in their imagination, fight weird aliens and save the galaxy in the era of dial-up internet and floppy disks!;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy, Indie;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/349790/106907/3c64a2037c04daf63dd8e2e62dd5c1d70e1144c0/1751268827/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1499171538;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.b5014332-35f9-4da7-a2f3-d12789a67585;steam_349790;gog_1685817496;humble_galaxyofpenandpaper;humble_galaxyofpenandpaper_steam;psn_CUSA11766_00;xboxone_1942601068;discord_f8849271-87f1-40b3-ac72-7fcf9f01524e;psn_CUSA11955_00;nswitch_0100CFD00BF3E000;test_galaxy-of-pen-and-paper;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.b5014332-35f9-4da7-a2f3-d12789a67585;test_8804e96114e9f384c01695054413e8437d98ec9f;test_58684abeecbe7856cbedb6698b98576f30fa0f13;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.b5014332-35f9-4da7-a2f3-d12789a67585;generic_51152901089935055;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Real Bout Fatal Fury 2 The Newcomers;Real Bout Fatal Fury 2: The Newcomers;Real Bout Fatal Fury 2 The Newcomers;;videos\Real Bout Fatal Fury 2 The Newcomers (1998).mp4;OK;images\Real Bout Fatal Fury 2 The Newcomers (1998).webp;;Amazon;SNK;SNK;20/03/1998;"Real Bout 2 revamps the two-line battle system from Real Bout Special. Instead of fighting in either two lines, the player is now forced to fight in a main line, while the second line is a ""sway line"" used to avoid attacks (similar to the original Real Bout). The one-line trap stages last seen in Fatal Fury Special also return.";Sport, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/3359900/720367002/038af61fe1983526008c63645bc125a3c053e75f/1759118085/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1759129505;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.b854dff2-49fd-4e55-8fde-9cd28c187492;gog_1490050478;humble_realboutfatalfury2_thenewcomers;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.b854dff2-49fd-4e55-8fde-9cd28c187492;test_b77aba5b3f38b5146b0f3bfa3af570e597c1337a;test_c8ed712ad2a9814c00a7481a6bf69d438fc43a3c;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.b854dff2-49fd-4e55-8fde-9cd28c187492;test_db8481e99393c99b6634b4a621586cd7eb77ecac;steam_3359900;generic_51154103686342517;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Max The Curse of Brotherhood;Max: The Curse of Brotherhood;Max The Curse of Brotherhood;;videos\Max The Curse of Brotherhood (2013).mp4;OK;images\Max The Curse of Brotherhood (2013).webp;;Amazon;Press Play, Flashbulb Games, Stage Clear Studios;Microsoft Studios, Wired Productions, Flashbulb Games, Stage Clear Studios;20/12/2013;"In its core Max: The Curse of Brotherhood is a physics-based puzzle/platformer and set in a 2.5D environment with a free and cinematic camera. The game has 7 chapters and 20 levels in total All levels are connected so the game feels like one long journey. Besides platforming, the gameplay twist is the magic marker which introduces a creative and open approach to how puzzles can be solved. Throughout the game the magic marker will gain different powers.

The five powers are
1. Earth pillars. You can create pillars from the earth to reach higher grounds.
2. Tree branches - You can grow trees to use them as platforms, springboards, rafts and moveable objects. Branches also catch fire.
3. Vines which work like ropes. You can crawl and swing in vines, but vines can also be used to tie objects together.
4. Water streams can be shaped freely and will move objects as well as Max along their path.
5. You must destroy obstacles and defeat Mustacho’s minions.

Each of the five powers are introduced in settings similar to the power themselves. The magic marker is triggered by pressing and holding RT and controlled by the right analog stick of the Xbox One controller and while controlling the magic marker Max cannot move at all.";Adventure, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/255390/19086/6de9a533b7e9badcd08df854fad7b25511949d52/1751261398/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447361179;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.bbdb2fca-2ca5-4589-ab85-857993089b4e;steam_255390;xboxone_1649675719;psn_CUSA08979_00;psn_CUSA09966_00;xboxone_1857969137;discord_97f27429-5d7a-4c8c-a4aa-32a98da871d5;twitch_4b011bc8-4e03-4473-b09f-62f655c2aae9;amazon_4b011bc8-4e03-4473-b09f-62f655c2aae9;3ds_4b011bc8-4e03-4473-b09f-62f655c2aae9;test_/max-the-curse-of-brotherhood-free-download/;test_max-the-curse-of-brotherhood;test_6231c3bd6a6a85222396467224d09534a9689c15;test_f21ff959fcc5d4532f800b0189ddbe421bf30782;test_3ae6751b80cfcbc3ece92a9fd7e68909550ac8e0;test_133fc99b4ae30b090331f3eecdc9b975b958bd5f;test_3f8ac154243598e9bbb48ec3f26b30d6a24fdcc5;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.bbdb2fca-2ca5-4589-ab85-857993089b4e;test_7c66e0dcce753f97e1f61805c65d955ad396f44a;amazon_38b970ce-b45f-862b-ea66-34ce7bc45365;generic_51153262255854274;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Samurai Bringer;Samurai Bringer;Samurai Bringer;;videos\Samurai Bringer (2022).mp4;OK;images\Samurai Bringer (2022).webp;;Amazon;Alphawing;PLAYISM;20/04/2022;Samurai Bringer is a roguelite action game with levels which change with every playthrough, where you cut down hordes of Samurai and Demons to collect combat techniques and polish your fighting style in order to defeat Yamata-no-Orochi, the eight-headed dragon of Japanese mythology.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Puzzle, Arcade, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1851280/456610/a4dd73bb9d135fe8098e975c066b9e35000d916c/1751040732/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1650423915;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.bcb2c9bd-b7ef-4d2b-acb0-f6b544269f69;steam_1851280;psn_CUSA32806_00;psn_CUSA32805_00;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.bcb2c9bd-b7ef-4d2b-acb0-f6b544269f69;generic_55240546338571556;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
SCARF;Scarf;SCARF;;videos\SCARF (2021).mp4;OK;images\SCARF (2021).webp;;Amazon, Epic Games Store;Uprising Studios;THQ Nordic, HandyGames, Handy Games;23/12/2021;"Scarf is a 3D Adventure game, where protagonist Hyke must use his polymorphic scarf to explore a magical environment, solve mysterious puzzles and overcome difficult challenges. Hyke’s scarf morphs into different objects which will help to progress the adventure. Hyke was born in an unknown place, surrounded by other souls. All of them will start a path through the World with the main goal being to meld with it and become part of nature.

