Golazo! Soccer League;Golazo! Soccer League;Golazo! Soccer League;;videos\Golazo Soccer League (2019).mp4;OK;images\Golazo Soccer League (2019).webp;;Amazon;Purple Tree;Klabater;11/09/2019;"Football is all about fun and teamwork. It doesn’t matter if you’re on the field or play it on console sitting with your friends on the couch. Golazo boldly recalls the glory days of the arcade soccer games, bringing back memories of cult classics we all know. With its vintage, not-too-serious, artistic and creative modern approach to classic gameplay, Golazo is certainly a perfect game for people who are weary of football managers or complicated hard-core simulators. You just grab your pad, sit on the couch and play!

Golazo is a dynamic 2.5D arcade football game with a medium sized fields, no fouls and offsides whistled. Just pure fun! Mastering the game is incredibly easy during the fun and furious 7vs7 matches. With its local multiplayer modes and crazy vintage approach, Golazo is the ideal choice for Couch & Party gamers!";Sport, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1431040/313971/f5438348f8119c7d07270d3e230321abef1649dd/1750988143/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1601919566;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e8e78531-da5e-4651-a75e-357717f42152;psn_CUSA16607_00;xboxone_1788626737;psn_CUSA16589_00;steam_1431040;epic_d29aec5e458544a288f8d9556ea63d56;gog_2029487364;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e8e78531-da5e-4651-a75e-357717f42152;test_9a1950e523f84acdf291d279f67e49f7e51c68ca;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.e8e78531-da5e-4651-a75e-357717f42152;generic_52629733351304073;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Dungeon of the ENDLESS - Definitive Edition;Dungeon of the ENDLESS - Definitive Edition;Dungeon of the ENDLESS - Definitive Edition;;;OK;images\Dungeon of the ENDLESS - Definitive Edition (2014).webp;;Amazon;Amplitude Studios;Sega, Amplitude Studios;27/10/2014;"Dungeon of the Endless - Definitive Edition

Dungeon of the Endless is Amplitude Studios’ take on the demanding Roguelike genre, mixing in Dungeon-Defense mechanics for a unique gameplay experience.
Condemned to slave labor in the Auriga system as punishment for a life of crime, your situation goes from bad to worse when you crash land in a mazelike Endless facility on an unknown planet.
Your only goal is to survive and get out of there. For that you’ll need a team: inmates, guards, and any survivors have the potential to become great allies.
Explore the facility and unearth life-saving technologies. Your teammates will also need some gear to unleash their true potential and earn powerful abilities. And don’t forget to gather Dust! Without it, you’ll be stuck in the dark.
With monsters at your heels and a merry band of misfits for a team, get ready for a bumpy ride with the Definitive Edition which, along with the base game, includes:

Dungeon of the Endless - Deep Freeze

The “Refreezerator” spaceship will let you experience the game in a different way as well as introduce a new teammate: Kreyang. Don’t touch anything related to Drakken history in her presence… you might lose a hand.

Dungeon of the Endless - Rescue Team

You’ve crashed somewhere in an uncharted part of the galaxy? No one is responding to your cries for help? Fear not, the Rescue Team is on its way! For drill sergeant Sasha, operator Zugma and… Audio engineer Wes, failure is not an option.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Platform, Real Time Strategy (RTS);;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e9b762cd-e130-4c5b-aaf5-070d785d1cd2;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_row_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.e9b762cd-e130-4c5b-aaf5-070d785d1cd2;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_XfE7x;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_UN6hP;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_VJTrV;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_Fw9ZM;humble_dungeonoftheendless_definitiveedition_storefront_steam_vjSXM;generic_56192803307050227;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
