Deponia The Complete Journey;Deponia: The Complete Journey;Deponia The Complete Journey;;videos\Deponia The Complete Journey (2014).mp4;OK;images\Deponia The Complete Journey (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store, Steam;Daedalic Entertainment;Daedalic Entertainment;02/06/2014;Showered in top-scores and awards, the Deponia-Trilogy, created by the developers of Edna&Harvey: The Breakout, The Whispered World and Memoria, managed to reach cult-status almost instantly. Thanks to its exciting story, likeable characters and hilarious dialogues and a finely crafted mixture of comedy and puzzles, Deponia is enjoyable for both, young and old. Join Rufus on his thrilling journeys, for the first time in a complete edition with many new features, that will not only be a blast for hardcore adventure fans, but also those new to the genre.;Adventure, Indie, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/292910/21142/c268cadcab7045549bdf177bcc3acf882aa15a6e/1751260134/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447362009;epic_03b7b25a77024cc0adf44777f791ffc4, steam_292910;steam_292910;humble_deponia_completejourney;kartridge_292910;amazon_292910;gg_292910;gmg_292910;humble_deponia_completejourney_freegame_steam;steam_371040;totalwar_deponia_completejourney_freegame_steam;d2d_deponia_completejourney_freegame_steam;humble_deponia_completejourney_steam;humble_deponia_completejourney_bundle_steam;epic_03b7b25a77024cc0adf44777f791ffc4;test_03b7b25a77024cc0adf44777f791ffc4;fanatical_deponia-the-complete-journey;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000002617;beamdog_03b7b25a77024cc0adf44777f791ffc4;humble_03b7b25a77024cc0adf44777f791ffc4;egg_03b7b25a77024cc0adf44777f791ffc4;itch_03b7b25a77024cc0adf44777f791ffc4;generic_51152758286150615;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
