Hell Let Loose;Hell Let Loose;Hell Let Loose;;videos\Hell Let Loose (2019).mp4;OK;images\Hell Let Loose (2019).webp;;Epic Games Store;Team17;Team17;06/06/2019;"A platoon-based realistic multiplayer first-person shooter for PC set during the Second World War. 
 
You've never played World War 2 the way it was meant to be played... with lumbering tanks dominating the battlefield, crucial supply chains fueling the frontlines, being a cog in the machine of colossal combined arms warfare. Hell Let Loose puts you in the chaos of war, complete with deep player-controlled vehicles, a dynamically evolving frontline, and crucial platoon-focused gameplay that commands the tide of battle. This is a simulation of war... not an arcade arena shooter.";Strategy, Indie, Shooter, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/686810/691006/f8254a7cd01cfdadd581fcf3bb72ce6e40ef1f3e/1750571043/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1714039340;epic_3e02273b543f4ff0a1c24d3b534a9ac3;steam_686810;humble_hellletloose_steam;humble_hellletloose_africa_middleeast_steam;steam_1504860;psn_PPSA04569_00;psn_PPSA04615_00;psn_PPSA05035_00;psn_PPSA02421_00;psn_PPSA05034_00;psn_PPSA02422_00;test_gfn_686810;humble_hellletloose_postrelease_steam;humble_hellletloose_postrelease_asia_steam;humble_hellletloose;humble_hellletloose_row_choice_steam;humble_hellletloose_asia_choice_steam;humble_hellletloose_rucis_choice_steam;humble_hellletloose_africa_me_choice_steam;humble_hellletloose_latam_choice_steam;test_1504860;test_686810;test_gfn_100354411;test_steam_686810;test_100354411;xboxone_2111829961;epic_3e02273b543f4ff0a1c24d3b534a9ac3;humble_hellletloose_bundle_steam;generic_51152961311272223;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
