Dead Cells;Dead Cells;Dead Cells;;videos\Dead Cells (2018).mp4;OK;images\Dead Cells (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Motion Twin, Evil Empire;Motion Twin;06/08/2018;"""Dead Cells is a roguelike, Castlevania-inspired action-platformer, allowing you to explore a sprawling, ever-changing castle… assuming you’re able to fight your way past its keepers. 
 
To beat the game, you’ll have to master 2D souls-like like combat with the ever-present threat of permadeath looming. No checkpoints. Kill, die, learn, repeat. 
 
RogueVania: Intense 2D action with the adrenaline pumping threat of permadeath in a castle full of cuddly creatures. 
 
Souls-like combat: Pattern-based bosses and minions, weapons and spells with unique gameplay. Roll roll roll your boat gently down the stream... 
 
Nonlinear progression: Unlock new levels with every death, take a new path. Tired of the stinking sewers? Why not take the ramparts? 
 
Exploration: Secret rooms, hidden passages, charming landscapes. A fine place for a holiday.""";Adventure, Indie, Platform;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/588650/231061/8fe407db503493211097e9898f58ae600559a2a3/1750557235/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1581426951;epic_48e9612c55fa43bd9aa95550e21d8bfd;steam_588650;gog_1237807960;xboxone_810101074;psn_CUSA10484_00;psn_CUSA11253_00;xboxone_1622132960;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003811;humble_deadcells_steam;nswitch_0100646009FBE000;winstore_9nkvx66j0zsk;origin_f377a4ba622bc03901c142afb37007de45d5ca60;origin_5f97d36c2b57697bdeb3a31b80512d50f74337885c0238991a28de2ce3be150e;humble_deadcells_us_switch;psx_Dead Cells;epic_ca0e1d19d3b640b39d8d20e966067872;test_/dead-cells-free-download/;test_dead-cells;playfire_dead-cells;humble_deadcells_steam_lwCYq;origin_OFB-EAST:109552678@subscription;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003811@subscription;nuuvem_79ae5e067d0220f58ba28f6f64fb37dd73f8142a;test_f142f071c33eb6ebcccf255051b8bcbcc4346245;test_a87511a5903e9b24dd7a839454090cb3c895e39d;test_a9cfcc669a8627e7e8f2987bc3942dd0ab06b678;psn_PPSA15554_00;psn_PPSA15552_00;nuuvem_364edb85e5343e5e18e00de1461a5a3e1e147da5;itch_141419;test_gfn_588650;epic_48e9612c55fa43bd9aa95550e21d8bfd;generic_51152743560622976;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
