The Elder Scrolls Online;The Elder Scrolls Online;The Elder Scrolls Online;;videos\The Elder Scrolls Online (2014).mp4;OK;images\The Elder Scrolls Online (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store;ZeniMax Online Studios;Bethesda Softworks;04/04/2014;"The Elder Scrolls Online is a massively multiplayer online role-playing game that was announced in May 2012. Developed by the team at ZeniMax Online Studios, The Elder Scrolls Online merges the unmatched exploration of rich worlds that the franchise is known for with the scale and social aspects of a massively multiplayer online role-playing game. 
 
An entirely new chapter of Elder Scrolls history will be revealed in this ambitious world, set a millennium before the events of Skyrim as the Daedric prince, Molag Bal, tries to pull all of Tamriel into his demonic realm.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/306130/1858354082/f35fb5d0a549d83a2a0f73880eb7601947ecdeb2/1750504397/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1748957096;epic_4d0ff75b922447649057c237c0bd1545;steam_306130;xboxone_1285166951;xboxone_1580702246;psn_CUSA00086_00;psn_CUSA00132_00;xboxone_239244046;humble_theelderscrollsonline_tamriel_monthly_steam;humble_theelderscrolls_online_imperial_steam;humble_teso_morrowind_keys;humble_theelderscrollsonline_steam;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-1057-20200411074355;beamdog_da988b6f-1717-4682-8825-7819af2048f9;minecraft_da988b6f-1717-4682-8825-7819af2048f9;psx_The Elder Scrolls Online;stadia_b17f16d4a4f94c0a85e07f54dbdedbb6rcp1/sku/2a598d522e4f4f9d818d08fe582d17e3;test_306130;stadia_b17f16d4a4f94c0a85e07f54dbdedbb6rcp1;psn_PPSA02017_00;psn_PPSA02018_00;test_PPSA02018_00;test_CUSA00086_00;epic_4d0ff75b922447649057c237c0bd1545;test_gfn_100446311;generic_51295396633784619;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
