Weird West;Weird West;Weird West;;videos\Weird West (2022).mp4;OK;images\Weird West (2022).webp;;Epic Games Store;Wolfeye Studios;Devolver Digital;31/03/2022;Discover a dark fantasy reimagining of the Wild West where lawmen and gunslingers share the frontier with fantastical creatures. Journey through the origin stories of a group of atypical heroes, written into legend by the decisions you make in an unforgiving land. Each journey is unique and tailored to the actions taken - a series of high stakes stories where everything counts and the world reacts to the choices you make. Form a posse or venture forth alone into an otherworldly confines of the Weird West and make each legend your own.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1097350/499142/386f580a84ec11de55147cf7f0a9e2d82c5d0153/1750618800/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1664270844;epic_5ab7c9b39f81481c88dce1e4f106a594;steam_1097350;gog_1421555971;xboxone_2016076229;psn_CUSA17337_00;psn_CUSA17598_00;epic_5ab7c9b39f81481c88dce1e4f106a594;humble_weirdwest_release_steam;psn_PPSA10887_00;psn_PPSA10886_00;itch_2118880;generic_52888803977424130;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
