Railway Empire;Railway Empire;Railway Empire;;videos\Railway Empire (2018).mp4;OK;images\Railway Empire (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Gaming Minds Studios;Kalypso Media;26/01/2018;In Railway Empire, you will create an elaborate and wide-ranging rail network, purchase over 40 different trains modelled in extraordinary detail, and buy or build railway stations, maintenance buildings, factories and tourist attractions to keep your travel network ahead of the competition. You'll also need to hire and manage your workforce if you want to ensure an efficient train service, whilst also develop over 300 technologies ranging from mechanical improvements to the trains themselves to workplace infrastructures and advanced amenities as you progress through five eras of technological innovations.;Strategy, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/503940/143824/da437c68645574fec77994ac9c4b71ddc7b33ddd/1750539040/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1516989879;epic_8cf7c6b964514532ad8284a376a517bf;steam_503940;gog_1556481953;xboxone_24524637;steam_730370;psn_CUSA07632_00;psn_CUSA10217_00;psn_CUSA10166_00;humble_railwayempire_eu_steam;humble_railwayempire_row_steam;itch_891cd1989c9b8303e543bb364216e4f26943a4ef6b040ff2b7e8580a;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xSYWlsd2F5IEVtcGlyZSBbRml0R2lybCBSZXBhY2td;origin_b99e9ddec01380cb7f0df59f8aab7440ad292b8b;origin_f86735aa10dd770da9c980137056f74eb3943839f10739a69ff3848991ed4634;discord_2b2a6380-59ea-4f81-8dc6-aacb81cd336a;humble_railwayempire_preorder_row_steam;humble_railwayempire;humble_railwayempire_row_choice_steam;humble_railwayempire_eu_choice_steam;humble_railwayempire_latam_choice_steam;humble_railwayempire_sea_choice_steam;humble_railwayempire_rucis_choice_steam;humble_railwayempire_cn_choice_steam;epic_8cf7c6b964514532ad8284a376a517bf;humble_railwayempire_completecollection_row_steam;humble_railwayempire_tr_choice_steam;test_/railway-empire-free-download/;test_railway-empire;playfire_railway-empire;humbl