KeyWe;KeyWe;KeyWe;;videos\KeyWe (2021).mp4;OK;images\KeyWe (2021).webp;;Epic Games Store;Stonewheat & Sons;Sold Out, Fireshine Games;30/08/2021;"KeyWe is a cute, co-operative postal puzzler starring Jeff and Debra, two small kiwi birds working in a whimsical post office. They must jump, flap, peck and butt-slam their way across an interactive landscape of levers, bells and buttons to get those messages delivered on time!

Encounter perilous postal environments and navigate seasonal hazards while waddling through the Telepost’s various mail rooms, and partner up with a pal to help these adorable kiwis complete their tasks, whatever the weather. Unlock new accessories to customise your kiwi and become the best-dressed mail bird in Bungalow Basin.";Indie, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1242980/348316/ff5e1d1f7eadc3d9792612fa3fd2eb1eee2f6bd1/1750648735/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1613570473;epic_8e13887ce02a4b5eb1a0ba17aa5405f3;steam_1242980;xboxone_1816678719;psn_PPSA02210_00;psn_CUSA25259_00;psn_CUSA25258_00;psn_PPSA02209_00;humble_keywe_row_steam;epic_8e13887ce02a4b5eb1a0ba17aa5405f3;psx_PPSA02209_00;humble_keywe_row_bundle_steam;humble_keywe_sea_bundle_steam;generic_52190417229066118;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
