Conarium;Conarium;Conarium;;videos\Conarium (2017).mp4;OK;images\Conarium (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Zoetrope Interactive;Iceberg Interactive;06/06/2017;"Conarium is a chilling Lovecraftian game, which follows a gripping story involving four scientists and their endeavor to challenge what we normally consider to be the ‘absolute’ limits of nature. Inspired by H.P. Lovecraft’s novella ""At the Mountains of Madness"", but largely set after the original story.

You, as Frank Gilman, open your eyes inside a room filled with strange, pulsating noises. Patterns of lights executing a Danse Macabre on the walls is presented by a queer device on the table. Having recalled nothing other than that you’re in Upuaut, an Antarctic base located near south pole, you find the place deserted and have a distinct feeling of something being terribly wrong. Somehow knowing that your memories cannot guide you enforces a strange feeling of vulnerability, a familiar yet alien sensation of being a part of a peculiar whole... Soon you will discover that having used the device during the expedition, you have died but then returned subtly changed, speaking of strange memories and of strange places. You have lost something important or gained something sinister...

Explore the antarctic base, as well as dreams and visions. Study clues, unlock secrets but avoid macabre beings at all cost.";Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/313780/104714/f5a7de94f5664e8222bef317c0eba2125bb9dae9/1751271444/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1495640451;epic_Canary;steam_313780;gog_1528332522;xboxone_343766256;psn_CUSA12427_00;psn_CUSA14099_00;epic_Canary;epic_6ac9ddab8e604e3ba2d4ea01e8f9fa7d;humble_conarium_steam;itch_50a8b5cbbebf0488c12e00f482324983e6297c13f9b8d83dd9a126c2;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xDb25hcml1bSBbRml0R2lybCBSZXBhY2td;origin_219d04cc7f157d070858ba917a8e5db7a82dc5f9;origin_105d859ff0c5bc65b87c432816541f142af5958284f8f6b065b39334a44a9609;discord_f0e0ae6b-bf77-4817-a90e-1d6790e5dda0;test_Canary;test_/conarium-free-download/;test_conarium;playfire_conarium;fanatical_conarium;generic_51142065701842586;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
This War of Mine;This War of Mine;This War of Mine;;videos\This War of Mine (2014).mp4;OK;images\This War of Mine (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store;11 bit studios;11 bit studios;14/11/2014;"In This War Of Mine you do not play as an elite soldier, rather a group of civilians trying to survive in a besieged city; struggling with lack of food, medicine and constant danger from snipers and hostile scavengers. The game provides an experience of war seen from an entirely new angle.

The pace of This War of Mine is imposed by the day and night cycle. During the day snipers outside stop you from leaving your refuge, so you need to focus on maintaining your hideout: crafting, trading and taking care of your survivors. At night, take one of your civilians on a mission to scavenge through a set of unique locations for items that will help you stay alive.

Make life-and-death decisions driven by your conscience. Try to protect everybody from your shelter or sacrifice some of them for longer-term survival. During war, there are no good or bad decisions; there is only survival. The sooner you realize that, the better.";Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/282070/424626/6ac5385b9c9a4a7d781b0a408e7d739999cc694a/1750489186/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1685354286;epic_Cardinal, humble_thiswarofmine;steam_282070;gog_1207666873;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001235;humble_thiswarofmine;epic_Cardinal;amazon_aa864570-a5e4-4ace-97f6-175079665488;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003656;twitch_aa864570-a5e4-4ace-97f6-175079665488;humble_thiswarofmine_bundle_steam;humble_thiswarofmine_steam;itch_9d8e35b44e45b7e83a5427c619afadcf2efd41381b41d0ee66fc64db;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xUaGlzIFdhciBvZiBNaW5lIFtGaXRHaXJsIFJlcGFja10=;origin_f715640d208f7792577f3946387da73ec99d0526;origin_c594cb2c853d511a1b7df29ee2fde19c324fb35d44b8222a225b6ab066fc80c0;origin_ad0f65affebf12913d7423777773b9b42c12902bb386a6313e401c515cf872b1;origin_a54c60f2c5e76e478666a2049c094f51d54c4a09;humble_thiswarofmine_fightforjustice_steam;test_Cardinal;humble_thiswarofmine_betterfutures_bundle_steam;test_282070;test_/this-war-of-mine-free-download/;test_this-war-of-mine;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001235@subscription;humble_thiswarofmine_humblehealcovid19_steam;fanatical_this-war-of-mine;test_epic_thiswarofminefinalcut;test_gfn_100818711;test_gfn_282070;generic_51295406589704936;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
