Bad North Jotunn Edition;Bad North Jotunn Edition;Bad North Jotunn Edition;;videos\Bad North Jotunn Edition (2018).mp4;OK;images\Bad North Jotunn Edition (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Plausible Concept;;20/08/2018;"Bad North is a charming but brutal real-time tactics roguelite. Defend your idyllic island kingdom against a horde of Viking invaders, as you lead the desperate exodus of your people. Command your loyal subjects to take full tactical advantage of the unique shape of each island. Everything is at stake: fail, and watch the blood of your subjects stain the ground red. 
 
It’s charmingly brutal, with beautiful procedurally-generated islands and adorable soldiers juxtaposed against the blood-stained realities of war. You control the broad strokes of the battle, giving high level commands to your soldiers who try their best to carry them out in the heat of the moment. It’s accessibly deep, with simple player inputs masking a dynamic combat simulation that make it inviting to new players while challenging veterans. 
 
Keep fighting, warriors. Not for power or riches or glory, but for hope of peace to come once again in the harsh lands of the Bad North.";Strategy, Tactical;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/688420/234699/51c883912e9c1c319b567237836ad2e6a83575e4/1750571095/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1563970531;epic_Chives;steam_688420;xboxone_634298669;gog_1656388860;psn_CUSA10606_00;gog_2034253881;xboxone_2015012841;psn_CUSA10969_00;discord_487564993236172802;epic_Chives;humble_badnorth_jotunnedition_choice_steam;winstore_9n4t8vcmqvdt;humble_badnorth_steam;humble_badnorth_deluxe_steam;humble_badnorth_jotunnedition;test_Chives;humble_badnorth_jotuunedition_bundle_steam;test_epic_badnorthjotunnedition;test_gfn_101821211;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000001208;beamdog_Chives;humble_Chives;egg_Chives;humble_badnorth_jotuunedition_row_bundle_steam;generic_52675403867832996;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Little Inferno;Little Inferno;Little Inferno;;videos\Little Inferno (2012).mp4;OK;images\Little Inferno (2012).webp;;Epic Games Store;Tomorrow Corporation;Tomorrow Corporation, Experimental Gameplay Group;18/11/2012;Congratulations on your new Little Inferno Entertainment Fireplace! Throw your toys into your fire, and play with them as they burn. Stay warm in there. It's getting cold outside! Burn flaming logs, screaming robots, credit cards, batteries, exploding fish, unstable nuclear devices, and tiny galaxies. An adventure that takes place almost entirely in front of a fireplace - about looking up up up out of the chimney, and the cold world just on the other side of the wall.;Adventure, Indie, Puzzle, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/221260/9751/9884fb9c08a18a14e2d120b10fcc4cd62b274a08/1750481652/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447357040;epic_Clover;steam_221260;gog_1444053723;humble_littleinferno_bundle;humble_littleinferno;epic_Clover;humble_androidbundle8_littleinferno_steam;humble_hib8_littleinfernosteam;humble_littleinfernosteam;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-784-20200408214058;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-784-20200408223931;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-784-20200408233931;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-784-20200409003932;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-784-20200409080600;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-829-20200411074355;beamdog_0d37eb6c-9cb7-4799-8e16-964815887348;minecraft_0d37eb6c-9cb7-4799-8e16-964815887348;minecraft_3878e7a1-a5b2-4dc8-920d-81ae5ec22ca8;minecraft_e5e25c86-2cb8-40d9-904d-259a02a214cc;test_Clover;test_/little-inferno-free-download/;test_little-inferno;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000005008;beamdog_Clover;humble_Clover;egg_Clover;itch_Clover;nwiiu_0005000010128600;generic_51153219359107850;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
