Kingdom Come Deliverance;Kingdom Come: Deliverance;Kingdom Come Deliverance;;videos\Kingdom Come Deliverance (2018).mp4;OK;images\Kingdom Come Deliverance (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Warhorse Studios;Deep Silver, Warhorse Studios;13/02/2018;"A first-person, open world, realistic RPG that will take you to the Medieval Europe in a time of upheaval and strife 
 
A humble, young blacksmith loses everything to war. As he tries to fulfill the dying wish of his father, Fate drags him into the thick of a conspiracy to save a kidnapped king and stop a bloody conflict. You will wander the world, fighting as a knight, lurking in the shadows as a rogue, or using the bard’s charm to persuade people to your cause. You will dive deep into a sweeping, epic, nonlinear story from Daniel Vávra, an award-winning designer from the Mafia series. Our unique, first-person combat system lets you wield sword or bow in both one-on-one skirmishes and large-scale battles. All of this – and more – brought to life beautifully with next-gen visuals delivered via CryEngine 3.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/379430/106515/7ebae3c59dd8f446e0baefcdf61ecc9278223ca1/1750521127/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1592317466;epic_Eel;steam_379430;gog_1719198803;xboxone_68553410;psn_CUSA07180_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002968;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003615;psn_CUSA09682_00;psn_CUSA07238_00;psn_CUSA15436_00;psn_CUSA15610_00;humble_kingdomcome_deliverance_monthly_steam;xboxone_1703270586;humble_kingdomcome_deliverance_steam;epic_Eel;epic_EelStaging;psn_CUSA15643_00;winstore_9p3t7hvkm6d0;test_CUSA07238_00;humble_kingdomcome_deliverance_royaledition_steam;itch_ec0b94a956c2e4d6e1ab7d619b6c4841cca2548b1eddd8d9d496716d;origin_eb894e992bd7618ab370a1d5818ecc5f190e6cda;origin_78354ece048b85baeec5dd1125a91acefa16c34d9a255141a75f4366c6dd2274;test_d2bd69dde8686f30c91c2d4b3db26eccadd8acb1;test_c3155ce9cc9f37c9ace50d931fc79053220427e5;test_52321b9793dc50308443a2f333fce19758960550;test_Eel;humble_kingdom_royaledition_steam;test_/kingdom-come-deliverance-free-pc-download/;test_kingdom-come-deliverance;playfire_kingdom-come-deliverance;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003615@gifting;humble_kingdomcome_deliverance_bundle_steam;test_epic_kingdomcomedeliverance;test_gfn_100573211;test_gfn_379430;fanatical_kingdom-come-deliverance;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-00