The Crew 2;The Crew 2;The Crew 2;;videos\The Crew 2 (2018).mp4;OK;images\The Crew 2 (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Ivory Tower;Ubisoft Entertainment;29/06/2018;The newest iteration in the revolutionary franchise, The Crew 2 captures the thrill of the American motorsports spirit in one of the most exhilarating open worlds ever created. Welcome to Motornation, a huge, varied, action-packed, and beautiful playground built for motorsports throughout the entire US of A. Enjoy unrestrained exploration on ground, sea, and sky. From coast to coast, street and pro racers, off-road explorers, and freestylers gather and compete in all kinds of disciplines. Join them in high-octane contests and share every glorious moment with the world.;Sport;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/646910/164182/1b7a390001745f277e47c337c0db40103b6cebab/1750566881/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1556554184;epic_Hermit;steam_646910;xboxone_504085184;xboxone_518619593;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002916;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002919;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002918;psn_NPWR14350_00;psn_CUSA08609_00;uplay_90c0ddf3-64c2-40d1-ac53-85ebeccd96eb;psn_CUSA08600_00;psn_CUSA08605_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002931;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002924;uplay_f852bab6-9e9f-4c53-9290-99c36c51452c;uplay_2855;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002925;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002932;psn_CUSA09665_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002927;epic_HermitTrial;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002934;epic_Hermit;humble_thecrew2_gold_emea_uplay;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002923;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002926;humble_thecrew2_standard_na_uplay;humble_thecrew2_gold_na_uplay;humble_thecrew2_standard_emea_uplay;humble_thecrew2_deluxe_na_uplay;humble_thecrew2_gold_latam_uplay;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002933;psn_CUSA11140_00;humble_thecrew2_deluxe_emea_uplay;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002929;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002928;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002930;humble_thecrew2_gold_ru_cn_uplay;humble_thecrew2_standard_ru_cn_uplay;humble_thecrew2_deluxe_ru_cn_uplay;psn_CUSA11226_00;psn_CUSA11132_00;humble_thecre