The Messenger;The Messenger;The Messenger;;videos\The Messenger (2018).mp4;OK;images\The Messenger (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Sabotage;Devolver Digital;30/08/2018;"As a demon army besieges his village, a young ninja ventures through a cursed world, to deliver a scroll paramount to his clan's survival.
Leveraging players expectations as a core game design ingredient, The Messenger is first presented as an 8-bit action platformer with a simple story, that unravels into an epic time traveling tale, eventually revealing itself as a 16-bit Metroidvania game packed with replay value and deadpan humor.";Adventure, Indie, Platform, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/764790/139163/eedaf87f5b7b3028cfafc0795c7e3651a86cb240/1750581127/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1534427206;epic_Jay;steam_764790;gog_1433116924;psn_CUSA15268_00;psn_CUSA15271_00;amazon_1cb34067-6b1b-4610-9dd2-e06988f69a3b;humble_1cb34067-6b1b-4610-9dd2-e06988f69a3b;twitch_1cb34067-6b1b-4610-9dd2-e06988f69a3b;epic_Jay;xboxone_1991539413;3ds_1cb34067-6b1b-4610-9dd2-e06988f69a3b;winstore_9nnfbw3ngv9k;nswitch_0100DC300AC78000;humble_themessenger_steam;humble_themessenger_us_switch;humble_themessenger_bundle_steam;humble_themessenger;xboxone_1962688125;epic_NotReallyJay;generic_51295401009910635;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Sid Meier's Civilization VI;Sid Meier's Civilization VI;Sid Meier's Civilization VI;;videos\Sid Meiers Civilization VI (2016).mp4;OK;images\Sid Meiers Civilization VI (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Firaxis Games;2K Games, Aspyr Media;20/10/2016;"Civilization is a turn-based strategy game in which you attempt to build an empire to stand the test of time. Become Ruler of the World by establishing and leading a civilization from the Stone Age to the Information Age. Wage war, conduct diplomacy, advance your culture, and go head-to-head with history’s greatest leaders as you attempt to build the greatest civilization the world has ever known.

Civilization VI offers new ways to engage with your world: cities now physically expand across the map, active research in technology and culture unlocks new potential, and competing leaders will pursue their own agendas based on their historical traits as you race for one of five ways to achieve victory in the game.";Strategy, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/289070/76617/1f43ec5aa4bd687389eb29886a2539cc984530e9/1750500626/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1476737061;epic_Kinglet;steam_289070;steam_537570;humble_civilization6_eu_monthly_steam;humble_civilization6_row_monthly_steam;humble_civilization6_br_monthly_steam;humble_civilization6_eu_bundle_steam;psn_CUSA15322_00;psn_CUSA15381_00;xboxone_1989106096;humble_civilization6_rucis_monthly_steam;humble_civilization6_row_bundle_steam;humble_civilization6_asia_monthly_steam;nswitch_010044500C182000;humble_civilization6_row_steam;humble_civilization6_rucis_bundle_steam;humble_civilization6_digitaldeluxe_row_steam;humble_civilization6_digitaldeluxe_eu_steam;humble_civilization6_platinum_row_steam;humble_civilization6_eu_steam;humble_civilization6_gold_eu_steam;humble_civilization6_gold_row_steam;humble_civilization6_platinum_eu_steam;humble_civilization6_in_monthly_steam;humble_civilization6_asia_bundle_steam;humble_civilization6_in_bundle_steam;humble_civilization6_eu_aspyr_steam;humble_civilization6_digitaldeluxe_row_aspyr_steam;humble_civilization6_br_bundle_steam;itch_ff022ca89ecbcbe9d6352d4b8d025483fbdb5d93fc3f60e1caeb24a4;origin_e313335447e5ace4223e82bb03799cac02a926b3;origin_1ced556e09bed84dd741272ef1004b4eedea10a09ff29ade03f2739181727162;humble_civilization6_digitaldeluxe_eu_aspyr_steam;humble_civilization6_row_aspyr_steam;epic_Kinglet;humble_civilization6_digitaldeluxe_asia_steam;snes_53696;test_Kinglet;test_289070;test_sid-meier-s-civilization-vi;playfire_sid-meier-s-civilization-vi;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000007256;humble_Kinglet;humble_civilization6_row_2kmegahits_bundle_steam;