Unreal Tournament;Unreal Tournament;Unreal Tournament;;;OK;images\Unreal Tournament (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Epic Games;Epic Games;01/05/2016;"Unreal Tournament is a first-person shooter video game developed by Epic Games. It was to be the ninth installment in the Unreal franchise, and the first main entry in the series since Unreal Tournament 3 (2007). The game utilizes Epic's Unreal Engine 4 and was to be released for free on Microsoft Windows, OS X, and Linux.

Unreal Tournament's development is crowdsourced and open to contribution from anyone. Epic Games has been using forums for discussions and Twitch livestreams for regular updates. The source code of the game is published on GitHub.";Shooter;;;epic_UnrealTournamentDev;epic_UnrealTournamentDev;epic_Zen_4.14;epic_InfiltratorDemo_4.22;epic_UnrealTournamentPublicTest;epic_UnrealTournamentDevPlaytest;ps2_SLES-50074;epic_UnrealTournamentEditor;epic_UnrealTournamentEditorPublicTest;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000008660;beamdog_UnrealTournamentDev;humble_UnrealTournamentDev;egg_UnrealTournamentDev;ps2_Unreal Tournament;generic_51295418915358934;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Rebel Galaxy;Rebel Galaxy;Rebel Galaxy;;videos\Rebel Galaxy (2015).mp4;OK;images\Rebel Galaxy (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store, GOG, Steam;Double Damage Games;Double Damage Games;20/10/2015;Rebel Galaxy is an action-packed, swashbuckling space opera. You’ll battle pirates, explore anomalies, befriend aliens, scavenge battle wreckage, mine asteroids, and discover artifacts. Choose your path as a roguish do-gooder, crafty space-trader or power-hungry privateer - or maybe a little of each! Buy larger and more powerful craft with your hard-earned credits, and outfit them with a variety of wicked weapons and defenses. Set in a galaxy of fantastic sights, and secrets to be found, Rebel Galaxy is above all a space epic of adventure, exploration, and combat.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/290300/43186/ea106a4155fc86888ead4428ca9bebf5e3951c52/1750500989/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447378125;epic_Weaver, gog_1435582019, steam_290300;steam_290300;gog_1435582019;xboxone_126264108;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002166;psn_CUSA02586_00;psn_CUSA02381_00;epic_Weaver;psn_CUSA06668_00;psvita_CUSA02381_00;humble_rebelgalaxy_steam;test_CUSA02586_00;test_CUSA02381_00;psx_Rebel Galaxy;test_Weaver;test_/rebel-galaxy-free-download/;test_rebel-galaxy;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002166@subscription;fanatical_rebel-galaxy;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000006449;beamdog_Weaver;humble_Weaver;egg_Weaver;itch_Weaver;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002166@xgp_vault_game;generic_51154105680330054;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
World War Z;World War Z;World War Z;;;OK;images\World War Z (2019).webp;;Epic Games Store;Saber Interactive;Paramount Digital Entertainment, Focus Entertainment;16/04/2019;"Humanity is on the brink of extinction. From New York to Moscow and Jerusalem, the undead apocalypse continues to spread. As the end looms, a hardened few bands together to defeat the horde and outlive the dead.

World War Z is a heart-pounding co-op third-person shooter for up to 4 players featuring swarms of hundreds of zombies. Based on the Paramount Pictures film, World War Z focuses on fast-paced gameplay while exploring new storylines from around the world.";Adventure, Shooter;;;epic_Wombat;epic_Wombat;xboxone_940594756;psn_CUSA14046_00;psn_CUSA13930_00;epic_WombatPress;epic_WombatDevelopment;epic_WombatTrial;humble_worldwarz_biohazardbundle_epic_keyless;humble_worldwarz_epic;humble_worldwarz_epic_keyless;xboxone_1811697311;humble_worldwarz_gotyedition_epic_keyless;humble_worldwarz_gotyedition_builttosurvive_bundle_epic_keyless;humble_worldwarz_gotyedition_bundle_keyless_epic;generic_51295433219235083;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Gamedec;Gamedec;Gamedec;;videos\Gamedec (2021).mp4;OK;images\Gamedec (2021).webp;;Epic Games Store;Anshar Studios;Anshar Publishing;16/09/2021;Gamedec is an adaptive cyberpunk RPG. As a private detective, it’s your job to solve crimes inside virtual worlds. What decisions will you make in a world where child slavery is a F2P game, where murder over a game-clan dispute is an every-day reality? Who will you become in the XXII century?;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/917720/500662/48156060c5bebb2d4125d230396bc06c2f1b42f5/1750595922/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1708698972;epic_a01150ee6deb406c92dd2b2445186163;steam_917720;gog_1921398290;discord_fa63024e-bd9b-4107-9271-121a30ffb0be;gog_1326749904;epic_a01150ee6deb406c92dd2b2445186163;humble_gamedec_storefront_steam_p8rsq;humble_gamedec;humble_gamedec_choice_steam;psn_PPSA12363_00;generic_52522866326050554;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Five Nights at Freddy's Into the Pit;Five Nights at Freddy's: Into the Pit;Five Nights at Freddy's Into the Pit;;videos\Five Nights at Freddys Into the Pit (2024).mp4;OK;images\Five Nights at Freddys Into the Pit (2024).webp;;Epic Games Store;Mega Cat Studios;Mega Cat Studios;07/08/2024;"Jump into the pit and immerse yourself in a new chapter in the Five Nights at Freddy’s universe. Oswald wishes his town, and his life, weren’t so boring. That all changes when he explores the ball pit in a rundown pizzeria and finds himself in the past. However, Oswald’s deepest desire will have an unexpected cost…

Survive five nights of terror in this chilling adventure game. Travel between time periods, gather clues, and outrun the threat relentlessly pursuing you. Move swiftly and stay hidden, and you may just survive. But be careful—it’s not just your own life that’s on the line. Oswald’s father and children from the past could all meet their end if you don’t save them.";Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2638370/737287/bd0d416f957fcc97aac7570f96b8d1c7cd792fb0/1750817777/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1723065416;epic_a0fbc3eb950341e290ae20a7d02cc501;steam_2638370;xboxone_1835944487;epic_a0fbc3eb950341e290ae20a7d02cc501;generic_57248431181653962;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Chessarama;Chessarama;Chessarama;;videos\Chessarama (2023).mp4;OK;images\Chessarama (2023).webp;;Epic Games Store;Minimol Games;Minimol Games, Hawthorn Games;05/12/2023;Chessarama is a collection of chess-inspired puzzle and strategy games that use chess pieces and their established move sets, then reimagines their goals and themes. Solve challenges, unlock collectibles, and compete against each other on the leaderboards. Welcome to Chessarama!;Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS), Indie, Puzzle, Tactical, Card & Board Game;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1831830/635703/b0ef03b2636de023dda6ded18ac31c1fcc37470d/1751036306/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1701661036;epic_a1292bca78514801bc03571e9247909d;steam_1831830;xboxone_1751868147;epic_a1292bca78514801bc03571e9247909d;generic_55481609142422612;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Kerbal Space Program;Kerbal Space Program;Kerbal Space Program;;videos\Kerbal Space Program (2015).mp4;OK;images\Kerbal Space Program (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store, GOG, Steam;Squad;Private Division;27/04/2015;In Kerbal Space Program, take charge of the space program for the alien race known as the Kerbals. You have access to an array of parts to assemble fully-functional spacecraft that flies (or doesn’t) based on realistic aerodynamic and orbital physics. Launch your Kerbal crew into orbit and beyond (while keeping them alive) to explore moons and planets in the Kerbol solar system, constructing bases and space stations to expand the reach of your expedition.;Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/220200/171271/78c61bd83ebdcf9bfd985dc8dd77db6c4e272a9d/1750481505/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1530546317;epic_a1e2ce30defe4a9187ebc14fc9d2bd8b, gog_1429864849, steam_220200;steam_220200;gog_1429864849;xboxone_632819091;steam_231410;steam_steam_220200;psn_CUSA04780_00;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_row_monthly_steam;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_steam;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_rucis_monthly_steam;itch_8edc336a36d98d71b16df2ee6bb60c407ea69415bf6243334678d2e1;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xLZXJiYWwgU3BhY2UgUHJvZ3JhbSBbRml0R2lybCBSZXBhY2td;origin_b0130308000556b18f4ffaeb581b4e55db7958d3;origin_6cd087338da533a270b65b6eb73ad8cb6ef8fc5aec30e586667b4b2ed65563b7;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_fightforjustice_steam;test_220200;test_/kerbal-space-program-free-download/;test_kerbal-space-program;test_4bf4590139086d5c8b98b0192761216d59175aa4;test_173e46af17692e4f81583d2a8468a2297d4592d7;test_5ec84517240b5dccad9868752d7c72320bf521bc;test_935447eae78dba8e027e4e226f98b7585e6bb922;test_afaef9ea4b2a242fc691fce794c33b3598710f94;test_1cc413c6543b55dc412ff168ecf39f538a2d96c0;test_e4ad81383a542c5cd504501e51955a5ff60b7f1f;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_bundle_steam;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_standwithukraine_row_bundle_steam;humble_kerbalspaceprogram_standwithukra