Doodle Devil Dark Side;Doodle Devil: Dark Side;Doodle Devil Dark Side;;;OK;images\Doodle Devil Dark Side (2025).webp;;Epic Games Store;JoyBits;JoyBits;19/08/2025;"The Power of Destruction is in Your Hands!

While Doodle God was creating light, life, and balance, Doodle Devil was quietly crafting chaos, temptation, and sin.

Step into the shadows in this wickedly addictive puzzle game where you mix and match elements not to build, but to corrupt. The same clever mechanics and creative exploration that made Doodle God a worldwide hit return - only now, every combination leads you deeper into the darker side of existence.

Discover the Seven Deadly Sins. Create demons, monsters, and the horrors of war. Spread disease, greed, and despair across a crumbling world. From zombie apocalypses to nuclear catastrophes, your imagination is the only limit to destruction.

With every tap, you shape a universe of evil, unlocking twisted new elements, dark humor, and morally questionable outcomes. But remember - being bad has never been so much fun.";Indie, Puzzle, Simulator;;;epic_b75f769b59e14d48b57d4fb773f33446;epic_b75f769b59e14d48b57d4fb773f33446;epic_521bf8fc16894f61b85a89335eae5e6d;generic_59367756883378227;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
