Pillars of Eternity - Definitive Edition;Pillars of Eternity - Definitive Edition;Pillars of Eternity - Definitive Edition;;videos\Pillars of Eternity - Definitive Edition (2015).mp4;OK;images\Pillars of Eternity - Definitive Edition (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store;Obsidian Entertainment;Paradox Interactive, Obsidian Entertainment;26/03/2015;"Prepare to be enchanted by a world where the choices you make and the paths you choose shape your destiny. Recapture the deep sense of exploration, the joy of a pulsating adventure, and the thrill of leading your own band of companions across a new fantasy realm and into the depths of monster-infested dungeons in search of lost treasures and ancient mysteries. 
 
