The Fall;The Fall;The Fall;;videos\The Fall (2014).mp4;OK;images\The Fall (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store;Over The Moon;Over The Moon;30/05/2014;"The Fall is a side-scrolling adventure game with platforming and combat elements. Your character is an AI controlling a combat suit whose occupant is unresponsive and presumably dead or seriously injured. You have crash landed on an unknown planet for unknown reasons and must seek medical attention for your 'pilot'.

The bulk of the gameplay resolves around completing a series of object-matching puzzles in the style of classic adventure games, interspersed with occasional platforming/jumping puzzles and combat sequences.";Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle, Shooter, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/290770/38018/c31aedb1b8ba75f52002d38c1300ea3552e93563/1751271475/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447376723;epic_daac7fe46e3647cb80530411d7ec1dc5;steam_290770;gog_1425568340;xboxone_10027721;psn_CUSA02649_00;psn_CUSA02031_00;humble_thefall;humble_thefall_wiiu_nintendo;humble_thefall_yogscast2017_steam;humble_thefall_steam;nwiiu_00050000101B2800;epic_daac7fe46e3647cb80530411d7ec1dc5;beamdog_daac7fe46e3647cb80530411d7ec1dc5;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000003007;generic_51295397157832760;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Breakout Recharged;Breakout: Recharged;Breakout Recharged;;videos\Breakout Recharged (2022).mp4;OK;images\Breakout Recharged (2022).webp;;Epic Games Store;Nickervision Studios;Atari, Inc.;10/02/2022;The grandfather of brick-breaking games is back with some of the toughest challenges yet! Breakout: Recharged steps up the excitement with a fresh coat of paint, exciting power-ups, and another original soundtrack from award-winning video game composer Megan McDuffee. Breakout: Recharged will forever change what you expect from a brick-breaking title. The endless arcade mode and 50 challenge levels will push you to the limit of your skills. Don’t fret, however, as this wouldn’t be a Recharged title without game-changing powerups. Expect the aid of rail guns, homing missiles, and explosives to join the traditional multi-ball. You’ll need every tool in the arsenal and razor-sharp reflexes to climb the global leaderboards.;Puzzle, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1714190/433014/cbf52f83b3a0e4ab8786c638675f5b0325d99c94/1751022845/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1643035669;epic_daec2330d8114107ac5e953dca5eb8e8;steam_1714190;xboxone_1857840975;epic_daec2330d8114107ac5e953dca5eb8e8;psn_PPSA05906_00;psn_PPSA05905_00;psn_CUSA31474_00;gog_1340291710;psn_CUSA31473_00;humble_breakout_recharged_bundle_steam;test_592569-breakout-recharged;generic_55118038092946756;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
