Aven Colony;Aven Colony;Aven Colony;;videos\Aven Colony (2017).mp4;OK;images\Aven Colony (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Mothership Entertainment;Team17;25/07/2017;"Aven Colony is a city-building and management sim that tells the story of humanity’s first settlement of an extrasolar world. Land on exotic Aven Prime, where you must construct and maintain the infrastructure and ensure the well-being of your citizens, all while dealing with the often harsh realities of an exotic alien world.

On top of this, you’ll face the greatest challenge of all — keeping your people happy. How will you feed your people? Will you be able to provide them with enough jobs, entertainment, retail outlets, and other services while protecting them from the planet’s many dangers? What social policies will you enact to influence your people? The future of the colony rests on your decisions.";Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/484900/115454/366e734ce763f3b950167484b8b569534a6313d7/1750536627/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1501237196;epic_dc07b9ead8214591b8df6d2546d2a0e3;steam_484900;xboxone_1042452848;gog_1824175646;psn_CUSA08055_00;psn_CUSA08138_00;humble_avencolony_row_steam;itch_f1090e0680bd48cab4b7ef4f4746dd42388ac413ced92616960b9ec8;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xBdmVuIENvbG9ueSBbRml0R2lybCBSZXBhY2td;origin_ea8884c11387ad165bd1d159ea80de470744cd56;origin_696a8294da2f426873ce122896ade6550521e43a6f20970df5f9fd5509f084f2;itch_78462;test_/aven-colony-free-download/;test_aven-colony;humble_avencolony;humble_avencolony_row_choice_steam;humble_avencolony_latam_choice_steam;humble_avencolony_asia_choice_steam;humble_avencolony_africa_me_choice_steam;humble_avencolony_rucis_choice_steam;humble_avencolony_bundle_steam;epic_dc07b9ead8214591b8df6d2546d2a0e3;test_gfn_102054311;test_gfn_484900;test_100198211;test_gfn_100198211;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000001138;beamdog_dc07b9ead8214591b8df6d2546d2a0e3;test_dc07b9ead8214591b8df6d2546d2a0e3;humble_dc07b9ead8214591b8df6d2546d2a0e3;egg_dc07b9ead8214591b8df6d2546d2a0e3;itch_dc07b9ead8214591b8df6d2546d2a0e3;generic_51141455192164330;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Shadowrun Returns;Shadowrun Returns;Shadowrun Returns;;videos\Shadowrun Returns (2013).mp4;OK;images\Shadowrun Returns (2013).webp;;Epic Games Store, GOG, Steam;Harebrained Schemes;Harebrained Schemes;25/07/2013;"The year is 2054. Magic has returned to the world, awakening powerful creatures of myth and legend. Technology merges with flesh and consciousness. Elves, trolls, orks and dwarves walk among us, while ruthless corporations bleed the world dry. You are a shadowrunner – a mercenary living on the fringes of society, in the shadows of massive corporate arcologies, surviving day-by-day on skill and instinct alone. When the powerful or the desperate need a job done, you get it done… by any means necessary. 
 
 
 
The unique cyberpunk-meets-fantasy world of Shadowrun has gained a huge cult following since its creation nearly 25 years ago. Now, creator Jordan Weisman returns to the world of Shadowrun, modernizing this classic game setting as a single player, turn-based tactical RPG. 
 
 
 
With the Shadowrun Returns Editor, everyone is empowered to create and share their own stories and campaigns with the Steam Workshop community. You can even explore the entire Shadowrun Returns Seattle campaign in the Editor directly – see how it was built and borrow as much as you need to jump-start your own creations! No advanced coding or art skills are required to create content using the SRR Editor.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/234650/11385/fe4bdcf98d46bb017204b8b2dff11f695ba91575/1750496597/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447357826;epic_dc29cb42f32e4a17af1d68c715fa459c, gog_1207660413, steam_234650;steam_234650;gog_1207660413;humble_shadowrunreturns;humble_shadowrunreturns_bundle_steam;humble_shadowrunreturns_carepackage_steam;humble_shadowrunreturns_steam;humble_shadowrunreturns_deluxe_steam;humble_shadowrunreturns_paradox_steam;totalwar_shadowrunreturns_steam;d2d_shadowrunreturns_steam;humble_shadowrunreturns_deluxe_paradox_keys_restricted_steam;epic_dc29cb42f32e4a17af1d68c715fa459c;test_/shadowrun-returns-free-download/;test_shadowrun-returns;playfire_shadowrun-returns;test_dc29cb42f32e4a17af1d68c715fa459c;fanatical_shadowrun-returns;test_steam_shadowrunreturns;test_epic_shadowrunreturns;test_gfn_234650;test_gfn_100892711;xboxone_1953391836;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000007080;beamdog_dc29cb42f32e4a17af1d68c715fa459c;humble_dc29cb42f32e4a17af1d68c715fa459c;egg_dc29cb42f32e4a17af1d68c715fa459c;psn_PPSA04121_00;psn_CUSA28614_00;psn_CUSA28615_00;test_gfn_100223111;psn_PPSA04120_00;xboxone_1813959723;itch_dc29cb42f32e4a17af1d68c715fa459c;generic_51154182198455080;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
