The Long Dark;The Long Dark;The Long Dark;;videos\The Long Dark (2017).mp4;OK;images\The Long Dark (2017).webp;;Epic Games Store;Hinterland Studio Inc.;Hinterland Studio Inc.;01/08/2017;"Welcome to The Long Dark, the innovative exploration-survival experience Wired magazine calls ""the pinnacle of an entire genre"". The game is a thoughtful, exploration-survival experience that challenges solo players to think for themselves as they explore an expansive frozen wilderness in the aftermath of a geomagnetic disaster. There are no zombies but only you, the cold, and all the threats Mother Nature can muster.";Adventure, Strategy, Indie, Shooter, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/305620/1426103121/6cb2741806173c1f06602c3b510613f7170cf92e/1764959491/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1765217090;epic_ed93b18355a84230938c705121c63661;steam_305620;gog_1447763046;xboxone_690285705;psn_CUSA09690_00;psn_CUSA08624_00;humble_thelongdark_monthly_steam;test_CUSA08624_00;humble_thelongdark_steam;humble_thelongdark_gift;discord_58151ab7-5fcd-426f-84d4-ae38337b0f6e;test_305620;epic_ed93b18355a84230938c705121c63661;test_/the-long-dark-free-download/;test_the-long-dark;test_ed93b18355a84230938c705121c63661;test_steam_thelongdark;test_gfn_305620;nuuvem_3fdd2742f2e234f149817cbc58e1f768ea245b63;humble_thelongdark_standwithukraine_bundle_steam;test_100104511;test_gfn_100104511;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000005043;beamdog_ed93b18355a84230938c705121c63661;humble_ed93b18355a84230938c705121c63661;egg_ed93b18355a84230938c705121c63661;epic_87441b64c6d746b7a7c90017c227dd0c;psn_PPSA30659_00;psn_PPSA30658_00;generic_51295400441275501;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Mothergunship;Mothergunship;Mothergunship;;videos\Mothergunship (2018).mp4;OK;images\Mothergunship (2018).webp;;Epic Games Store;Grip Digital, Terrible Posture Games;Grip Digital;17/07/2018;Our mission is clear, our determination strong, and our guns are very, very big. MOTHERGUNSHIP is a bullet-hell FPS hybrid facing you, Earth’s last hope, against the fleets of data-hoarding robotic alien invaders. Take the fight to the enemy, craft gun monstrosities that no reasonable person could ever lift, and experience randomized mayhem as you battle your way to the heart of the fleet to destroy the MOTHERGUNSHIP!;Indie, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/574090/170808/d2866cb58961bc92d6abdd2905d40c2d0b197fd1/1750552387/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1530208631;epic_ee5c6a659d0f478fba0049fa44429a1f;steam_574090;xboxone_199170438;xboxone_1015377306;psn_CUSA10579_00;psn_CUSA10581_00;humble_mothergunship_monthly_steam;humble_mothergunship_steam;itch_e3cc0b45d3bfec529d28cb56301df40eaf24005739fd355d3e43f25a;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xNT1RIRVJHVU5TSElQIFtGaXRHaXJsIFJlcGFja10=;origin_4fcd586afe90cbcd457845951c2ab7b631a67a41;origin_d45f40d7144d5b91226690a32b89a80b38123f4c92f9e320bbe0a1b44b44bad1;test_/mothergunship-free-download/;test_mothergunship;gog_1749107974;epic_ee5c6a659d0f478fba0049fa44429a1f;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000005360;beamdog_ee5c6a659d0f478fba0049fa44429a1f;test_ee5c6a659d0f478fba0049fa44429a1f;humble_ee5c6a659d0f478fba0049fa44429a1f;egg_ee5c6a659d0f478fba0049fa44429a1f;itch_ee5c6a659d0f478fba0049fa44429a1f;test_574090;generic_51153305470884966;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Asteroids Recharged;Asteroids: Recharged;Asteroids Recharged;;videos\Asteroids Recharged (2021).mp4;OK;images\Asteroids Recharged (2021).webp;;Epic Games Store;SneakyBox;Atari, Inc.;14/12/2021;"The original space shooter warps to the modern era! Asteroids: Recharged has been reimagined for modern gameplay, with vibrant visuals, powerful new abilities, and another original soundtrack from award-winning video game composer Megan McDuffee.

Asteroids: Recharged creates a familiar, but revitalized and modern challenge to both old school and new high score chasers. And 30 unique and creative challenge levels take the space shooting game play into new territory, complete with local and global leaderboards.";Shooter, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1700890/419028/47ef0283df34a0438011b343e64e645fbd338a61/1750727019/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1637692550;epic_ee63838c6c394ce587ec0613c41161a6;steam_1700890;epic_ee63838c6c394ce587ec0613c41161a6;psn_PPSA05552_00;xboxone_1946604107;psn_CUSA30832_00;psn_CUSA30833_00;psn_PPSA05551_00;gog_1651421166;humble_asteroids_recharged_bundle_steam;generic_55011644363136522;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Mortal Shell Tech Beta;Mortal Shell Tech Beta;Mortal Shell Tech Beta;;videos\Mortal Shell Tech Beta (2020).mp4;OK;images\Mortal Shell Tech Beta (2020).webp;;Epic Games Store;Cold Symmetry;Playstack;18/08/2020;"Mortal Shell is a ruthless and deep action-RPG that tests your sanity and resilience in a shattered world. Your adversaries spare no mercy, with survival demanding superior awareness, precision and instincts. Possess lost warriors, track down hidden sanctums of the devout, and face formidable foes.

""Awakening as an empty vessel, you will enter into a shattered and twisted world where the remains of humanity wither and rot. Implored to do the bidding of the mysterious “Dark Father”, you must traverse this tattered landscape and track down hidden sanctums of devout followers. There, in Mortal Shell’s most hallowed grounds, you must overcome formidable foes and harvest the sacred glands. You won’t be truly alone when the dead litter your path: Scattered across this land are the remnant anima of lost warriors who can be inhabited to gain their unique abilities and knowledge of weapons. The Dark Father is desperate for you to complete your task — but to what end?

Discover “Shells” to Suit Your Playstyle - The lost remains of defeated warriors are yours to unearth. Awaken these Mortal Shells, occupy their bodies and significantly widen your understanding of different forms of combat. Inhabit a Shell that best fits your style and utilizes their own unique mastery of skills and weapon
upgrades.

Iron Sharpens Iron - Combat is strategic and deliberate. Survival demands superior awareness, precision and instincts. You must commit your sword only when an opportunity opens. Calculate your parries to unleash devastating counterblows.

Non-linear Campaign - Draw your own path across marsh-infested lowlands, through a gargantuan cathedral of obsidian rock, and into an ancient crypt frozen into the crest of a mountain.

Deep Upgrade Paths - The stronger your connection to each Mortal Shell grows, the better you can harness their innate talents. Craft unique upgrades, sharpen your blade with acid, and study dark arcane abilities that imbue your attacks with supernatural devastation.

Face Haunting Foes - Your path is guarded by desperate adversaries, devoted to inscrutable gods. Behold creatures both pitiable and grotesque, but do not let fear halt your journey. Muster your courage and face them down.

Developed by AAA Veterans - Mortal Shell has been developed by a coalition of seasoned veterans with an unbridled passion for the soulslike genre.""";Role-playing (RPG), Indie;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1110910/478582/062b53873b9747df0eeddc4dc13c93baf91e4910/1750620557/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1657529311;epic_f0ac8218ef7d4b5aabec153e3f193db6;steam_1110910;gog_1586537281;epic_SpinelDummy;epic_bed774d589a54b4d81643c59f6b7be1a;epic_75ed4104bf1d418592fced1341cc5fed;epic_0055e45ce7654c55aade646467349e83;xboxone_1679589975;psn_CUSA20133_00;psn_CUSA16364_00;epic_f0ac8218ef7d4b5aabec153e3f193db6;psn_CUSA24600_00;epic_2997a8c7680a4d049233aac47bd9a147;test_/mortal-shell-free-download/;test_mortal-shell;playfire_mortal-shell;psn_PPSA02867_00;psn_PPSA02868_00;psn_PPSA02904_00;humble_mortalshell_bundle_epic_keyless;humble_mortalshell_epic_keyless;itch_0055e45ce7654c55aade646467349e83;epic_e8a9426c08b94430b637c56bbab826bf;humble_mortalshell_bundle_steam;generic_53262622047882032;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Lysfanga The Time Shift Warrior;Lysfanga: The Time Shift Warrior;Lysfanga The Time Shift Warrior;;videos\Lysfanga The Time Shift Warrior (2024).mp4;OK;images\Lysfanga The Time Shift Warrior (2024).webp;;Epic Games Store;Sand Door Studio;Quantic Dream, Fabloo Games;13/02/2024;Your Kingdom’s fate relies on you… you… and you. Rewind time to create clones of your past-selves, and fight with an army of your own. Become legion and triumph over hordes of monsters to rescue Antala in this Hack'N'Slash game with a tactical twist.;Strategy, Indie, Puzzle, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2161620/662147/c39e78c7a597db42c10fe691bcdce0698e57c135/1751083823/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1707912261;epic_f3208566bd004bbfb1a7a4d40fbf8ea4;steam_2161620;epic_f3208566bd004bbfb1a7a4d40fbf8ea4;gog_1436524406;generic_56581382751735769;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Never Alone (Kisima Ingitchuna);Never Alone (Kisima Ingitchuna);Never Alone;;videos\Never Alone (Kisima Ingitchuna) (2014).mp4;OK;images\Never Alone (Kisima Ingitchuna) (2014).webp;;Epic Games Store, itch.io;Upper One Games;E-Line Media;18/11/2014;"Never Alone (Kisima Ingitchuna) is an atmospheric puzzle platformer and the first game to be developed in collaboration with the Iñupiat, an Alaska Native people, drawn from a traditional story that has been shared across the generations. Nearly 40 Alaska Native elders, storytellers and community members contributed to the development of the game. 
 
It features two characters, and it can be played in single-player mode or play cooperatively with a friend as you trek through frozen tundra, leap across treacherous ice floes, swim through underwater caverns and face enemies both strange and familiar. 
 
You'll explore awe-inspiring environments, perform heroic deeds and meet legendary characters from Iñupiaq stories — all narrated by a master storyteller in the spoken Iñupiaq language.";Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/295790/32731/6242a2531dee20b797f3738e47eb5ab377b58718/1751262773/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447370885;epic_f38de9fa4c6d43eabac080942cb394a1;steam_295790;gog_1446112277;xboxone_910593568;psn_CUSA01394_00;psn_CUSA01305_00;psn_CUSA01603_00;humble_neveralone;psn_CUSA03264_00;humble_neveralone_plusfoxtalesdlc_steam;psvita_CUSA01305_00;nwiiu_00050000101CCF00;humble_neveralone_steam;humble_never_alone_arctic_collection_steam;test_CUSA01394_00;test_CUSA01305_00;nwiiu_00050000101CE800;test_never-alone-kisima-ingitchuna;humble_neveralone_bundle_steam;epic_f38de9fa4c6d43eabac080942cb394a1;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000005641;beamdog_itchuna);test_itchuna);humble_itchuna);egg_itchuna);epic_itchuna);itch_f38de9fa4c6d43eabac080942cb394a1;generic_51153339066509705;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
