Carmageddon TDR 2000;Carmageddon TDR 2000;Carmageddon TDR 2000;;videos\Carmageddon TDR 2000 (2000).mp4;OK;images\Carmageddon TDR 2000 (2000).webp;;GOG;Torus Games;Xicat Interactive, Stainless Games Ltd., SCi Games;14/12/2000;"Carmageddon TDR 2000 has been designed from the ground up for Internet playing. Unique arenas and play modes, packed full of highly charged AI computer players, will add a whole new dimension for serious gamers.

