Neverwinter Nights Diamond;Neverwinter Nights Diamond;Neverwinter Nights Diamond;;;OK;images\Neverwinter Nights Diamond (2005).webp;;GOG;BioWare;Atari, Inc.;03/11/2005;"Experience one of the most popular role-playing adventures of our time, a journey that has thrilled millions. Inhabit dreamlike worlds of myth and mystery. Boundless lands of deadly creatures, foreboding omens and bold heroism.

This game puts you at the center of an epic tale of faith, war and betrayal, all the while staying true to the pen-and-paper role-playing tradition.
Neverwinter Nights - A world without limits!

The Diamond Edition includes the original Neverwinter Nights and three official expansion packs: Shadows of Undrentide, Hordes of the Underdark and Kingmaker.

A fast-paced RPG with an intuitive interface, suitable for new players and RPG veterans alike.

A classic RPG experience that will keep you entertained for over one hundred hours!";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;;;gog_1207658890;gog_1207658890;generic_51153339731185657;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Broken Sword Director's Cut;Broken Sword: Director's Cut;Broken Sword Director's Cut;;videos\Broken Sword Directors Cut (2008).mp4;OK;images\Broken Sword Directors Cut (2008).webp;;GOG;Revolution Software;Kalypso Media, Revolution Software;26/08/2008;"One of the all-time classic adventures, multi BAFTA-nominated ""Broken Sword: Director's Cut"" pitches sassy journalist Nico Collard, and intrepid American George Stobbart into a mysterious journey of intrigue and jeopardy. Guide George and Nico on their globe-spanning adventure, exploring exotic locations, solving ancient mysteries, and thwarting a dark conspiracy to reveal the secret truths of the Knights Templar.";Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/57640/26781/8d5987723c543ddc615bcf40f340e5fb0142cfdd/1751246388/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1479743091;gog_1207658900;steam_57640;gog_1207658900;humble_brokensword_directorscut;humble_brokenswordshadowofthetemplars;humble_brokensword_directorscut_trove;nds_YB7PN0;humble_androidbundle6_brokenswordshadowofthetemplarssteam;humble_brokensword_directorscut_steam;test_21127;beamdog_05cb8cde-ad7d-4203-9131-f46884cbf72d;minecraft_05cb8cde-ad7d-4203-9131-f46884cbf72d;minecraft_0daf41f3-7ae3-446e-b999-57921b369baa;minecraft_442e4e31-96d8-4b37-986a-6282329d14b2;minecraft_c4413b20-abf0-4923-bd03-9c9e70479efc;bethesda_06352443-0572-417f-a518-42910354e00d;nds_980fe656279ca03f33d2103468c3c136849b1a08;generic_51141994675053003;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Tyrian 2000;Tyrian 2000;Tyrian 2000;;;OK;images\Tyrian 2000 (1999).webp;;GOG;Eclipse Software;XSIV Games;30/11/1999;Tyrian 2000 is an updated rerelease of the original Tyrian. Tyrian is an action killing, smashing, shoot'em'all arcade game. Your goal is to kill as many enemies as possible and finish the level, buy more weapons and then kill many more enemies. Your battle ship can be improved over time and you can buy new weapons currently available. Your ship supports front guns, rear guns and side slots for the most deadly weapons.;Shooter, Arcade;;;gog_1207658901;gog_1207658901;ngameboy_6784;ngameboy_Tyrian 2000;ngameboy_3303251459;jaguar_25805655;test_25805655;generic_51295416355398085;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
XIII;XIII;XIII;;videos\XIII (2003).mp4;OK;images\XIII (2003).webp;;GOG;Ubisoft Paris;Ubisoft Entertainment, Feral Interactive;09/10/2003;XIII is a cel-shaded first-person shooter based on the popular Belgian cult comic created by Jean Van Hamme and illustrated by William Vance. The game is loosely based on the first five comics. The player unravels clues, trying to solve a conspiracy set in an environment that breathes a comic book ambiance. Footsteps and shots are visualized in text and actions: for example, headshots are shown in a series of still images. Aside from that, the game has all the typical FPS elements: both stealth and action, more than fifteen weapons (shotguns, crossbows, rifles, ...), interaction with environmental objects and plenty of enemies in levels spread all over the world. During the game, the player can learn a number of skills such as silent walking, lockpicking and dual weapons handling.;Puzzle, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1170760/286651/b5e8c6be3d2c39abdeb499917d642d9f23dd542a/1751198498/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1591904746;gog_1207658920;gog_1207658920;ncube_GX3E41;ps2_ZBD117AM1F;ps2_SLUS-20677;ps2_SLES-51244;steam_1170760;humble_xiii_classic_bundle_steam;generic_51295434535278292;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Alone in the Dark The Trilogy 123;Alone in the Dark: The Trilogy 123;Alone in the Dark The Trilogy 123;;;OK;images\Alone in the Dark The Trilogy 123 (1992).webp;;GOG;;;02/01/1992;"A suspicious suicide. A chilling curse. A malevolent power. Finally, a wicked dark secret. This is Derceto, a legendary Louisiana mansion where, against your better judgment, you're drawn into a world of shadows to explore the darker side of Jeremy Hartwood's imagination.<br>
<br>
Despite a paralyzing sense of personal danger, your quest for truth drives you to investigate the old house. But, you didn't know that, by entering Derceto, you'll be plunged into the daily nightmare that was Jeremy Hartwood's life. You weren't prepared for the torturous howls that resound from deep within its halls. You didn’t foresee the shadowy corridors that seemingly have no end. You couldn't anticipate the brooding, gloom-filled rooms, the pervasive weight of dread, the heavy sense of evil that gills the atmosphere and the very house itself.<br>
<br>
Had you known, you might have refused this task. But alas, you accepted, and now you must make your way through this spine-tingling adventure alone... and in the dark.The grand-daddy of survival horror genre
A memorable soundtrack, excellent voice acting, and a thrilling story will keep you hooked for hours
Inspired by H.P. Lovecraft's universe, where ancient evils of unimaginary power play with human lives
Includes Jack in the Dark bonus adventure";;;;gog_1207658923;gog_1207658923;generic_51623041474177960;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Dragonsphere;Dragonsphere;Dragonsphere;;videos\Dragonsphere (1994).mp4;OK;images\Dragonsphere (1994).webp;;GOG;MPS Labs;Retroism, MicroProse Software, Inc., Nightdive Studios;02/01/1994;Newly-crowned King of Callahach! It's been twenty years since your father saved the world by entrapping the evil Sorcerer Sanwe. Now the spell is waning. Sanwe's malevolent force will soon consume the land, and only you can stop him!;Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click, Quiz/Trivia;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/327940/26338/acdb0499ed8a2885e3676e3bc33d67fba9f0b61a/1751264732/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447364215;gog_1207658927;steam_327940;gog_1207658927;test_dragonsphere;test_46125517;jaguar_360317;jaguar_1547717724454799;generic_51152795097887404;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Syndicate Plus;Syndicate Plus;Syndicate Plus;;;OK;images\Syndicate Plus (1993).webp;;GOG;Bullfrog Productions;Electronic Arts;06/06/1993;"In the dark and twisted cities of tomorrow, corporate syndicates compete for global dominance. But the boardroom deals and corporate takeovers of the future look very different from today: they are lead by marketing directors who manage teams of half-men, half-machine cyborgs with no conscience and plenty of guns. 

You are an ambitious marketing director in the Syndicate, hand-picked to lead a team of cyborg mercenaries. You work in the problem-solving department and you are damn good at ""taking care"" of problems. Some might say that violence is not the answer but you know better. There here are hardly any problems that you can't solve with a well-placed bullet. Collateral damage in the local population and infrastructure during the “negotiations” is, as always, acceptable. After all, what would you expect form the dystopian futuristic world run by mega-corporations? 

Syndicate is Bullfrog’s masterpiece of a game in which you aren’t saving the world or protecting innocents. You just make sure that your employers get what they want. At your disposal are four cyborg agents, an impressive arsenal of weapons and gadgets, and a massive selection of cybernetic upgrades. You are free to unleash this power on a highly interactive map where you can blow up buildings, steal cars, light trees on fire, or just shoot stuff. Produced by Peter Molyneux himself, Syndicate is the essence of cyberpunk and, with its great music, stylized visuals, and mind-blowing atmosphere, it has earned its place among the best games of all time. Make sure to check out the game that secured Bullfrog's place in game development hall of fame.";Strategy, Real Time Strategy (RTS), Tactical;;;gog_1207658992;gog_1207658992;jaguar_Syndicate Plus;jaguar_1607341;test_syndicate-plus;jaguar_205744589;test_205744589;jaguar_13807289970036097;generic_51154308310747531;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Deus Ex GOTY Edition;Deus Ex GOTY Edition;Deus Ex GOTY Edition;;;OK;images\Deus Ex GOTY Edition (2000).webp;;GOG;Ion Storm;Square Enix;22/06/2000;"The year is 2052 and the world is a dangerous and chaotic place. Terrorists operate openly - killing thousands; drugs, disease and pollution kill even more. The world's economies are close to collapse and the gap between the insanely wealthy and the desperately poor grows ever wider.

The Game of the Year edition contains the latest game updates and a software development kit, a separate soundtrack CD, and a page from a fictional newspaper featured prominently in Deus Ex titled The Midnight Sun, which recounts recent events in the game's world.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Shooter;;no_section;gog_1207658995;steam_6910;gog_1207658995;humble_deusex_goty_steam;humble_deusex_thefall_plusgoty_steam_1;test_/deus-ex-game-of-the-year-edition-free-download/;fanatical_deus-ex-game-of-the-year-edition;humble_deusex_goty_eidos_steam;generic_51152762713120465;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Thief Gold;Thief Gold;Thief Gold;;;OK;images\Thief Gold (1998).webp;;GOG;Looking Glass Studios;Square Enix;30/11/1998;"Having received training from an enigmatic organization known as the Keepers, Garrett leaves the order and goes back to the life of a thief on the streets of the City. Once you enter the underworld you have to deal with all the consequences - you are not the only one out there looking for decent loot. Hide in the shadows of the dark, savage city. Sneak into old ruins, haunted cathedrals and mansions of the rich. Incapacitate your enemies quietly or in an open fight. This unique sneak-em-up game provides you with a range of means to achieve your goal. Remember though - secrecy is your best friend. 
 
Thief Gold is a first-person perspective stealth game. It was the first game to use light and sound gameplay mechanics – different surfaces cause varying noise (for example carpets are quiet and ceramic tiles are very loud). You can use sound to your advantage - it’s not only your main source of information on how close your enemies are but you can use it to distract them, for example by throwing objects. With unscripted levels, and objectives and paths altered based on difficulty settings, Thief Gold can give you hours of non-repetitive gameplay. 
 
This extended edition includes all of the missions from the first release, as well as three new missions adapted to the original storyline, with full voice acting and new graphics. It can still be considered the first game in the Thief series.";Adventure, Simulator;;no_section;gog_1207658997;steam_211600;gog_1207658997;humble_thiefgold_steam;totalwar_thiefgold_steam;d2d_thiefgold_steam;test_thief-gold;playfire_thief-gold;pce_1635;test_1635;zx_1635;amiga_1635;test_gfn_211600;test_211600;generic_51295406402063704;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Thief 2 The Metal Age;Thief 2: The Metal Age;Thief 2 The Metal Age;;;OK;images\Thief 2 The Metal Age (2000).webp;;GOG;Looking Glass Studios;Square Enix, Eidos Interactive, Eidos Montréal;23/03/2000;The ultimate thief is back! Tread softly as you make your way through 15 new complex, non-linear levels full of loot to steal and guards to outsmart. Improved enemy AI, new gadgets and a riveting story will draw you into the world of Thief II: The Metal Age, a place of powerful new technologies, fanatical religions and corruption.;Adventure, Shooter, Simulator;;no_section;gog_1207659001;steam_211740;gog_1207659001;humble_thief2_themetalage_steam;test_Thief 2: The Metal Age;test_4ff5cb90-7d7e-4032-82ad-2136789842e8;test_912c1ac6-6300-4e39-bf6f-5147ba98af8b;test_211740;generic_51295406386500558;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Treasure Adventure Game;Treasure Adventure Game;Treasure Adventure Game;;videos\Treasure Adventure Game (2011).mp4;OK;images\Treasure Adventure Game (2011).webp;;GOG;Robit Games;GOG.com;26/11/2011;Treasure Adventure Game is a freeware open-world, platform adventure game developed by Stephen Orlando. It includes a 1 hour original sound-track composed by Robert Ellis;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Platform;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/863940/163859/0ed526ccacafa230b8f4ec9c37064e5e04d34d09/1751155043/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1614897955;gog_1207659013;gog_1207659013;steam_863940;generic_51295413275532115;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Thief 3 Deadly Shadows;Thief 3: Deadly Shadows;Thief 3 Deadly Shadows;;;OK;images\Thief 3 Deadly Shadows (2004).webp;;GOG;Ion Storm;Square Enix, Eidos Interactive, Eidos Montréal;25/05/2004;"In the third instalment of the Thief series, master-thief Garrett is contacted by Keeper Artemus with a mission to steal two valuable artefacts. At the same time, Garrett learns about a prophecy: the coming of a Dark Age. He embarks upon a journey to unravel a mystery that threatens the existence of the order of Keepers. Is it possible that there is a traitor in their midst?

The stealth and thievery game, Thief: Deadly Shadows comes with a number of improvements over two previous parts. Released in 2004, it left behind the aging Dark Engine, using a heavily modified Unreal engine instead. Realistic lighting effects have been implemented: each character and object now casts its own shadow. A third person's view has been made available in addition to the standard first person perspective.

The stealth system that made Thief: The Dark Project and Thief 2: The Metal Age famous is still in place. You have to stick to the shadows and avoid making noise, as guards will react to anything suspicious. It is also the first game of the series that introduced free roaming. The City, divided into several unlockable districts, is yours to explore. You can interact with the city's inhabitants: pickpocket, steal, or even mug them for loot.";Adventure, Shooter, Simulator;;no_section;gog_1207659036;steam_6980;gog_1207659036;humble_thiefdeadlyshadows_steam;test_thief-deadly-shadows;playfire_thief-deadly-shadows;test_Thief: Deadly Shadows;test_1db127e4-5883-4a86-ae7a-590fe7bbd5c1;test_f1db184a-d696-449a-bd0b-853542c1f584;test_gfn_6980;test_6980;generic_51295406410750399;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Worlds of Ultima The Savage Empire;Worlds of Ultima: The Savage Empire;Worlds of Ultima The Savage Empire;;;OK;images\Worlds of Ultima The Savage Empire (1990).webp;;GOG;Origin Systems;Electronic Arts;30/12/1990;"Savage Empire is Origin's first ""Worlds of Ultima"" release. It was made using basically the same engine as Ultima VI but with slightly different graphics. The game contains all of the elements of the other Ultimas, as well as some extra features that add to the experience. You are able to interact with the environment in a realistic manner... picking branches from trees, digging clay from a riverbank etc. Savage Empire also has a lot more character interaction than the previous Ultimas. Characters will jump into conversations whenever they feel they have something pertinent to add.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;;;gog_1207659061;gog_1207659061;jaguar_Worlds of Ultima 1 - The Savage Empire;jaguar_26987451435357;generic_51295433607506794;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Legacy of Kain Soul Reaver 2;Legacy of Kain: Soul Reaver 2;Legacy of Kain Soul Reaver 2;;;OK;images\Legacy of Kain Soul Reaver 2 (2001).webp;;GOG;Crystal Dynamics;Eidos Interactive;30/10/2001;"Soul Reaver 2 picks up where Legacy of Kain: Soul Reaver left off, with Raziel having just plunged through the Chronoplast time portal in his relentless pursuit of Kain. Over the course of his quest for revenge, Raziel must unearth the mysteries of Nosgoth’s ancient races, expose the machinations behind the corruption of the Pillars, and the vampire genocide. Throughout the game, Raziel acquires numerous new abilities, weapon enhancements, and spells, all of which are critical to the completion of his epic adventure.

Soul Reaver is a third-person combat adventure filled with devious puzzles and kick-ass combat. Fly, swim, jump, and even travel from the material world to the spectral realm to overcome obstacles and conquer your enemies. With over 40 abilities to choose from, no two fights will ever be the same.";Adventure;;no_section;gog_1207659063;steam_224940;gog_1207659063;ps2_EKEYYFJS20;humble_legacyofkain_soulreaver2_steam;ps2_SLUS-20165;ps2_SLES-50196;ps2_SCPS-55013;ps2_2046;test_6f09289b4a55edc84b7f9b63cd0780750676796d;test_/legacy-of-kain-soul-reaver-2-free-download/;ps2_Legacy of Kain - Soul Reaver 2;test_Legacy Of Kain: Soul Reaver 2;test_96291e81-a0b7-4523-a294-e87f16d07c25;test_ac52c66f-bcf7-456e-b789-f592de856b64;humble_legacyofkain_soulreaver2_crystal_steam;generic_51153206572188037;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Deus Ex 2 Invisible War;Deus Ex 2: Invisible War;Deus Ex 2 Invisible War;;;OK;images\Deus Ex 2 Invisible War (2003).webp;;GOG;Ion Storm;Square Enix, Eidos Interactive, Eidos Montréal;02/12/2003;"Several religious and political factions see an opportunity to re-shape a worldwide government to their agendas. In this techno-nightmare, take part in the dark struggle to raise the world from its own ashes. 
 
This dynamic and innovative 1st person-action/adventure brings a level of reality unprecedented in a videogame. Biotech modifications allow players to see through walls, leap 40 feet into the air, regenerate critical body damage or render yourself radar invisible. Globe-hop to real world locations such as Seattle, Antarctica, and Cairo.";Role-playing (RPG), Shooter;;no_section;gog_1207659068;steam_6920;gog_1207659068;humble_deusex_invisiblewar_steam;test_deus-ex-invisible-war;playfire_deus-ex-invisible-war;test_Deus Ex: Invisible War;test_eba49413-a977-4c13-a2e0-a0e9bf52810f;test_e1d3c029-bfd4-4a21-9310-df2b78a10034;fanatical_deus-ex-invisible-war;test_d63a152e-2df8-4a8c-aa38-2fd7c5c611a6;humble_deusex_invisiblewar_eidos_steam;generic_51152762847937031;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Legacy of Kain Defiance (2003);Legacy of Kain: Defiance;Legacy of Kain Defiance;;;OK;images\Legacy of Kain Defiance (2003) (2003).webp;;GOG;Crystal Dynamics;Eidos Interactive;17/12/2003;"Swords, sorcery, souls, and buckets of blood await you in Legacy of Kain: Defiance.
<br><br>
Return to the corrupt world of Nosgoth, where the disfigured wraith Raziel pursues his creator, the vampire overlord Kain. Separated by their common enemies and time itself, the two anti-heroes must wage their own personal battles to discover what lies behind their destinies and defeat the vicious forces that seek to condemn their world to eternal damnation. While their foes plot and scheme, Kain and Raziel embark on a dark and twisted odyssey. In the end, only one of them may be left standing.
<br><br>
The final chapter in the epic Legacy of Kain series is a time-bending, dimension-crossing, action-adventure game featuring more fast-paced combat than ever before. Take control of two mighty and highly-evolved vampires, each with a vast arsenal of combat moves and elaborate combos to unlock during their journey. A world filled to the brim with gruesome monsters, conflict and intrigue lies before them.
<br><br>
Can you handle the combined power of this demonic duo?
<br><br>
<img src=""http://items.gog.com/defiance_ratings.png"">
