I Have No Mouth And I Must Scream;I Have No Mouth And I Must Scream;I Have No Mouth And I Must Scream;;videos\I Have No Mouth And I Must Scream (1995).mp4;OK;images\I Have No Mouth And I Must Scream (1995).webp;;GOG;The Dreamers Guild, Cyberdreams;Acclaim Entertainment, DotEmu, Nightdive Studios, Cyberdreams;31/10/1995;"I Have No Mouth, and I Must Scream is a point-and-click adventure game based upon Harlan Ellison's short story of the same title.
The game's story is set in a world where an evil computer named AM has destroyed all of humanity except for five people, whom he has been keeping alive and torturing for the past 109 years. Each survivor has a fatal flaw in their character, and in an attempt to crush their spirits, AM has constructed a metaphorical adventure for each that preys upon their weaknesses. To succeed in the game, the player must make choices to prove that humans are better than machines, because they have the ability to redeem themselves. Woven into the fabric of the story are ethical dilemmas dealing with issues such as insanity, rape, paranoia and genocide.";Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/245390/13463/f7f68d4a00d2e29f12a6a314bf68d5b420e74b1c/1750487172/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447358790;gog_1207659593;steam_245390;gog_1207659593;humble_ihavenomouthandimustscream_steam;egg_ihnm;gameuk_ihnm;amiga_ihnm;amiga_ihnm-de;amiga_ihnm-es;amiga_ihnm-demo;test_/i-have-no-mouth-and-i-must-scream-free-download/;test_b6bb4bbfb39fa64ddbd2396ffeeb0c5e008370e7;test_i-have-no-mouth-and-i-must-scream;test_72262132499663;test_de2d1dd74189e538e27d87d9d5418422ed34701b;amiga_ihnm-it;amiga_ihnm-1;jaguar_591969190414512475;jaguar_9698823215750922049647;humble_ihavenomouthandimustscream_new_steam;xboxone_2129720796;psn_CUSA53759_00;psn_PPSA28836_00;generic_51152989663811301;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Stargunner;Stargunner;Stargunner;;;OK;images\Stargunner (1996).webp;;GOG;Apogee Software;Apogee Software;19/11/1996;"In the far distant future, an epic war for survival takes place...

Deep within the Andromeda galaxy, the people of Zile grow restless and greedy. The Zilions secretly prepare for a massive strike against the nearby planet Ytima. Fearing such an attack, the Ytimians train an elite squad of ""Stargunners."" Their mission: To strike the planet Zile and cripple the Zilions’ three strongholds, where the Zilion war fleets await. If the Stargunners can surprise the Zilions on their own planet and wipe out their fleet, then good will triumph over evil once again.";Shooter, Arcade;;no_section;gog_1207659693;steam_358390;gog_1207659693;generic_51154263049919873;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Flight of the Amazon Queen;Flight of the Amazon Queen;Flight of the Amazon Queen;;videos\Flight of the Amazon Queen (1995).mp4;OK;images\Flight of the Amazon Queen (1995).webp;;GOG;iPhSoft, Interactive Binary Illusions;Renegade Software, iPhSoft, Interactive Binary Illusions;25/10/1995;Flight of the Amazon Queen follows a pilot for hire named Joe King who is hired to fly a famous actress to her next job, but ends up in a lightning storm and crashes deep in the Amazon Jungle. In the jungle, Joe uncovers a plot by a mad scientist to take over the world by creating an army of dinosaur women created from Amazon women.;Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/1105460/240396/dab6bb6dfa7dfe6915f8008ddf8e206c00b384a0/1751189304/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1619020863;gog_1207659723;gog_1207659723;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-684-20200408214058;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-684-20200408223931;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-684-20200408233931;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-684-20200409003932;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-684-20200409080600;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-727-20200411074355;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411082911;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411084254;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411094254;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411104254;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411114254;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411124255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411134255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411144255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411154255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411164255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411174256;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411184256;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411194256;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411204256;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-199-20200411214257;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-203-20200412223222;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-203-20200412230610;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-203-20200412232524;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-203-2020041223