Baldur's Gate: Enhanced Edition [gog_1207666353];Baldur's Gate: Enhanced Edition;Baldur's Gate: Enhanced Edition [gog_1207666353];;videos\Baldurs Gate Enhanced Edition (2013).mp4;OK;images\Baldurs Gate Enhanced Edition (2013).webp;;GOG;Overhaul Games;Atari, Inc., Beamdog;16/01/2013;Running on an upgraded and improved version of the Infinity Engine, Baldur's Gate: Enhanced Edition includes the entire Baldur's Gate adventure, the Tales of the Sword Coast expansion pack, and never-before-seen content including a new adventure and three new party members: the Calishite monk Rasaad yn Bashir, Neera the wild mage, and Dorn Il-Khan, the evil blackguard.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/228280/25521/80076622c821cbd99956d77a6a5d87a980b3684a/1750493806/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447363829;gog_1207666353;steam_228280;gog_1207666353;test_/baldurs-gate-enhanced-edition-free-download/;test_baldur-s-gate-enhanced-edition;playfire_baldur-s-gate-enhanced-edition;fanatical_baldurs-gate-enhanced-edition;test_e16d22e64d1ba9bbb350cf5060fcba4d8ea5fa1c;epic_2dfdd37919f542038d9fea69d8604f33;test_fc82a43065927ea598541f49cbd697db8f106595;humble_baldursgate_enhancededition_bundle_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.5d35cae7-39d1-4e53-ba92-36004c4a5211;test_41de998d3569224603c6148a358cbb0889243785;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.5d35cae7-39d1-4e53-ba92-36004c4a5211;humble_baldursgate_enhancededition_steam;epic_fe07cfbb58d0443e9561205f4644eb93;generic_51141465399503513;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Toonstruck;Toonstruck;Toonstruck;;videos\Toonstruck (1996).mp4;OK;images\Toonstruck (1996).webp;;GOG;Burst Studios;Virgin Interactive Entertainment (Europe) Ltd., Virgin Interactive Entertainment, Inc.;04/11/1996;"Toonstruck is an adventure game released in 1996 in which, although all the imagery is drawn and scanned into the game, the protagonist Drew Blanc (played and voiced by Christopher Lloyd) is an actual video-captured representation of the actor (the name is a pun, since the character has ""drawn a blank"" on coming up with a new idea for a character). Drew's sidekick, crudely named Flux Wildly, is a drawn character voiced by Dan Castellaneta. Toonstruck also features scan-line compressed FMV and was also one of the first video games to include stock music from APM Music, notably the classic ""Spooky Scherzo"" by Sam Fonteyn and ""Lonely Hearts Club A"" by David Bell.";Adventure, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/369830/79035/db11396ef174f0cb559955cc78b0cfb7b9a022df/1751277118/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1575507951;gog_1207666633;steam_369830;gog_1207666633;egg_toon;gameuk_toon;amiga_toon;amiga_toon-1;amiga_toon-de;test_/toonstruck-free-download/;amiga_toon-demo;test_12791247;amiga_toon-de-1;epic_6e066444830f448c9d7c41237b846b64;dotemu_Toonstruck;jaguar_12791249;generic_51295410293023242;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Mount & Blade;Mount & Blade;Mount & Blade;;videos\Mount Blade (2008).mp4;OK;images\Mount Blade (2008).webp;;GOG;Taleworlds;Paradox Interactive;16/09/2008;Mount & Blade is an immersive medieval action/tactics game taking place in a fictitious land named Calradia. Enriched with RPG elements, Mount & Blade offers a captivating environment, beautifully detailed with hundreds of castles, towns, and villages to explore.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Shooter, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/22100/1400/199bc4f277640cf88e8db7b67cacdbe24014fef2/1750484706/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447351527;gog_1207666893;steam_22100;gog_1207666893;humble_mountandblade_steam;test_22100;fanatical_mount-blade;generic_51153307202491647;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Grim Fandango Remastered;Grim Fandango Remastered;Grim Fandango Remastered;;videos\Grim Fandango Remastered (2015).mp4;OK;images\Grim Fandango Remastered (2015).webp;;GOG, Steam;Double Fine Productions;Double Fine Productions;26/01/2015;"Something's rotten in the land of the dead, and you're being played for a sucker. Meet Manny Calavera, travel agent at the Department of Death. He sells luxury packages to souls on their four-year journey to eternal rest. But there's trouble in paradise. Help Manny untangle himself from a conspiracy that threatens his very salvation.

One of the most acclaimed adventure games of all time is now back, better than ever. Grim Fandango's epic story of four years in the life (or death) of Manny Calavera, travel agent to the dead, has been remastered to look, sound, and control even better than when it won GameSpot's Game of the Year award upon its original launch. Grim Fandango still stands as a classic of the genre, with unforgettable characters and unique combination of film noir and Mexican folklore.";Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/316790/30310/72e95b68e3bdafa65af7272ddb80c2fbc83d9b5b/1751264067/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447367957;gog_1207667183, humble_grimfandango, steam_316790;steam_316790;gog_1207667183;psn_CUSA01858_00;psn_NPWR07722_00;psn_CUSA01319_00;humble_grimfandango;humble_grimfandango_steam;psvita_CUSA01319_00;humble_grimfandango_bundle_steam;test_CUSA01858_00;test_CUSA01319_00;totalwar_grimfandango_steam;d2d_grimfandango_steam;humble_psnindie2019_rebundle_bt1tier_playstation_0;humble_psnindie2019_bundle_bt1tier_playstation_0;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-764-20200411074355;beamdog_d3560900-c997-4a1b-84be-f097fba56997;minecraft_d3560900-c997-4a1b-84be-f097fba56997;minecraft_dee19096-5e73-418d-b84d-83a3f3697b22;minecraft_7b212645-7316-43dd-b525-ea4ed75dbe03;psx_Grim Fandango Remastered;itch_63060;xboxone_1755179727;test_/grim-fandango-remastered-free-download/;humble_grimfandangoremastered_bundle_steam;nswitch_0100B7900B024000;generic_51152935747419324;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Forgotten Realms The Archives - Collection Three;Forgotten Realms: The Archives - Collection Two;Forgotten Realms The Archives - Collection Three;;;OK;;;GOG;;;;"The Forgotten Realm Archives - Collection Two brings a healthy mix of “Gold Box” and nostalgia goodness to your PC, along with a combination of adventure builders, turn-based and real-time role-playing gameplay. Composed of RPG classics that premiered the Forgotten Realms to video gamers, The Forgotten Realm Archives - Collection Two contains the following titles: Pool of Radiance, Curse of the Azure Bonds, Hillsfar, Secret of the Silver Blades, Pools of Darkness, Gateway to the Savage Frontier, Treasures of the Savage Frontier, Forgotten Realms Unlimited Adventures.
<br><br><br>

<img src=""https://items.gog.com/hasbeen/main_art_pool_of_radiance_resized.jpg"" style=""margin: 5px 15px 0 0; float: left; width: 220px"">
<span style=""text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; display: block;"">Pool of Radiance</span>
Located on the northern shore of the Moonsea, the fabled city of Phlan has been overrun by monsters led by a mysterious leader. Your quest: uncover the identity of this evil force and rid Phlan of its scourge, restoring the city to its former glory. Along the way, you hope to find the legendary Pool of Radiance, said to glow with its own mystical power. Does it really give tremendous strength to the warrior who bathes in its magic waters? Or is that just an elfin myth? Before you meet the challenges ahead, you must create your characters and choose their races and battle skills. Then, set off on your glorious quest to drive out the monsters and let civilization reign once more!
<span style=""display: block; height: 20px""> </span>

<img src=""https://items.gog.com/hasbeen/fr08710234caba.jpg"" style=""margin: 5px 15px 0 0; float: left; width: 220px"">
<span style=""text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; display: block;"">Curse of the Azure Bonds</span>
After you saved the entire city of Phlan and located the Pool of Radiance, a simple trip to Tilverton should have been as easy as a noon-day stroll. But it wasn’t…
Ambushed, captured and knocked unconscious, you awake with no idea who attacked you or how you arrived in Tilverton. You only know that five azure-blue symbols are imprinted under the skin of your right arm. The mystical power of the azure symbols ensnares your will like metal bonds! And when the bonds glow, you must do as they command, No magic can dispel them, no prayers can remove them. Your only hope: search the world for members of the alliance who created the bonds and regain control of your own destiny. Only then can you be free of th";;;;gog_1209599383, gog_1597590091, gog_2048243655;gog_2048243655;generic_59157896912310335;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
