Hitman Absolution;Hitman: Absolution;Hitman Absolution;;videos\Hitman Absolution (2012).mp4;OK;images\Hitman Absolution (2012).webp;;GOG;IO Interactive;Square Enix, Feral Interactive;20/11/2012;"Hitman: Absolution follows the Original Assassin undertaking his most personal contract to date. Betrayed by the Agency and hunted by the police, Agent 47 finds himself pursuing redemption in a corrupt and twisted world. 
 
