Baba Is You;Baba Is You;Baba Is You;;videos\Baba Is You (2019).mp4;OK;images\Baba Is You (2019).webp;;Steam;hempuli;hempuli;13/03/2019;"Baba Is You is a puzzle game where you can change the rules by which you play. In every level, the rules themselves are present as blocks you can interact with; by manipulating them, you can change how the level works and cause surprising, unexpected interactions! With some simple block-pushing you can turn yourself into a rock, turn patches of grass into dangerously hot obstacles, and even change the goal you need to reach to something entirely different.";Strategy, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/736260/209884/a4399e94a570a08ed4332fb7e95b0182b8dd2ff1/1750576739/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1550681204;humble_babaisyou_OdtBg, steam_736260;steam_736260;humble_babaisyou_OdtBg;itch_366363;humble_babaisyou_storefront_steam_r06Z0;nswitch_01002CD00A51C000;humble_babaisyou_switch;humble_babaisyou_fightforjustice_steam;humble_babaisyou_fightforjustice_new_steam;humble_babaisyou_humblehealcovid19_steam;generic_51141460747983911;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Broken Age;Broken Age;Broken Age;;videos\Broken Age (2014).mp4;OK;images\Broken Age (2014).webp;;Steam;Double Fine Productions;Nordic Games Publishing, Double Fine Productions;28/01/2014;Broken Age is a point-and-click adventure telling the stories of a young boy and girl leading parallel lives. Vella Tartine has been chosen by her village to be sacrificed to a terrible monster — but she decides to fight back. Meanwhile, Shay Volta is living a solitary life on a spaceship under the care of a motherly computer, but he wants to break free to lead adventures and do good in the world. Adventures ensue.;Adventure, Indie, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/232790/35014/e2b1757cae46dd2dd8194757ffe46f1fe68b2899/1751249607/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447373622;humble_brokenage, steam_232790;steam_232790;gog_1207662943;xboxone_232457702;psn_CUSA01963_00;psn_CUSA01990_00;humble_brokenage;amazon_9504afc3-c0e2-478a-8dd7-03761f536363;humble_9504afc3-c0e2-478a-8dd7-03761f536363;twitch_9504afc3-c0e2-478a-8dd7-03761f536363;humble_brokenage_ouya;humble_doublefine_bundle_brokenagekeys;xboxone_1618263033;psvita_CUSA01990_00;humble_brokenage_steam;3ds_9504afc3-c0e2-478a-8dd7-03761f536363;test_CUSA01963_00;humble_brokenage_bundle_steam;test_CUSA01990_00;uplay_2179;humble_brokenage_gog;humble_psnindie2019_rebundle_btatier_playstation_3;humble_brokenage_conquer_covid19_steam;humble_psnindie2019_bundle_btatier_playstation_3;psx_Broken Age;humble_brokenage_fightforjustice_steam;humble_brokenage_doublefine20thanniversary_bundle_steam;test_/broken-age-free-download/;test_broken-age;playfire_broken-age;humble_brokenage_standwithukraine_bundle_steam;itch_61788;test_fd0b12324995c97fb96813c4c4e3e8e443162417;humble_brokenage_dayofthedevsletsgetdigital_bundle_steam;test_47764-broken-age;amazon_bd85cd04-7898-45b5-9db3-d393dfa3bc23;generic_51141994387076924;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Broken Sword 5 The Serpent's Curse;Broken Sword 5: The Serpent's Curse;Broken Sword 5 The Serpent's Curse;;videos\Broken Sword 5 The Serpents Curse (2013).mp4;OK;images\Broken Sword 5 The Serpents Curse (2013).webp;;Steam;Revolution Software;Deep Silver, Ravenscourt, Revolution Software;04/12/2013;Broken Sword 5: The Serpent's Curse is a classical point & click adventure. It abandons 3D graphics and direct control which were used in the two predecessors and returns to the style of the first two games. The only major technical differences are a higher resolution and that the characters are modelled instead of drawn. The game uses an intelligent mouse cursor: a right click on a hotspot results in looking at the item and a left click triggers an item-specific action. Of course this is the main ingredient of the puzzles: collecting items and using them on other items in order to solve problems. On some occasions there are also logic puzzles from a zoomed-in view on an object, e.g. connecting cables of an engine in order to repair the car's horn. Another important part of the game are conversations with the various characters, some of them known from previous instalments. During the course of the game the controlled character switches between George and Nico. A help function supports players who are stuck.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/262940/15581/578d77957632d20991cd0eaafb4e867c8e9435cc/1750498851/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1752409263;humble_brokensword5theserpentscurse, steam_262940;steam_262940;gog_1207660323;xboxone_364252200;psn_CUSA02681_00;psn_CUSA02500_00;humble_brokensword5theserpentscurse;humble_brokensword5theserpentscurse_bundle_steam;humble_brokensword5theserpentscurse_trove;humble_brokensword5theserpentscurse_steam;test_CUSA02681_00;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-561-20200411074355;test_2924;beamdog_4ebcb1d8-f0f0-4346-b68b-4512535cb8ed;minecraft_4ebcb1d8-f0f0-4346-b68b-4512535cb8ed;minecraft_39e7ad3a-74ff-40d1-8037-4630abd2a488;minecraft_12ec3843-a770-41d8-bb4b-00c5648cbc50;riot_1440805;test_/broken-sword-5-the-serpents-curse-free-pc-download/;fanatical_broken-sword-5-the-serpents-curse;test_5ba04-broken-sword-5-the-serpents-curse-fr;generic_51141994611834074;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Burly Men at Sea;Burly Men at Sea;Burly Men at Sea;;videos\Burly Men at Sea (2016).mp4;OK;images\Burly Men at Sea (2016).webp;;Steam;Brain&Brain;Plug In Digital, Brain&Brain;29/09/2016;Burly Men at Sea is a folktale about a trio of large, bearded fishermen who step away from the ordinary to seek adventure. Set in early 20th-century Scandinavia, the game's story branches through a series of encounters with creatures from folklore.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/403290/146981/656de0ccdda6ffa8a6959ee589b95a7c72236a88/1751277691/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1711318742;humble_burlymenatsea, steam_403290;steam_403290;psn_CUSA09549_00;psn_CUSA09109_00;humble_burlymenatsea;humble_burlymenatsea_earlybuild;humble_burlymenatsea_bundle_steam;humble_burlymenatsea_storefront_steam_JKU1u;psvita_CUSA09109_00;test_CUSA09109_00;itch_66678;test_CUSA09549_00;generic_51142001082016067;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Day of the Tentacle Remastered;Day of the Tentacle Remastered;Day of the Tentacle Remastered;;videos\Day of the Tentacle Remastered (2016).mp4;OK;images\Day of the Tentacle Remastered (2016).webp;;Steam;Double Fine Productions;Double Fine Productions;21/03/2016;"Originally released by LucasArts in 1993 as a sequel to Ron Gilbert’s ground breaking Maniac Mansion, Day of the Tentacle is a mind-bending, time travel, cartoon puzzle adventure game in which three unlikely friends work together to prevent an evil mutated purple tentacle from taking over the world!

Now, over twenty years later, Day of the Tentacle is back in a remastered edition that features all new hand-drawn, high resolution artwork, with remastered audio, music and sound effects (which the original 90s marketing blurb described as ""zany!"")

Players are able to switch back and forth between classic and remastered modes, and mix and match audio, graphics and user interface to their heart's desire. We’ve also included a concept art browser, and recorded a commentary track with the game’s original creators Tim Schafer, Dave Grossman, Larry Ahern, Peter Chan, Peter McConnell and Clint Bajakian.

Day of the Tentacle was Tim Schafer’s first game as co-project lead, and a much beloved cult classic! This special edition has been lovingly restored and remade with the care and attention that can only come from involving the game's original creators. It’s coming to Windows, OSX, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita early next year!";Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/388210/52042/e16d2c7395397b3c55a7e9851fda4bf66b7f5b41/1750523491/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1457573196;humble_dayofthetentacle, steam_388210;steam_388210;gog_1456922969;psn_CUSA01959_00;psn_CUSA01991_00;humble_dayofthetentacle;amazon_d96d188b-283a-44e1-8402-1fbf3f1f2d72;humble_dayofthetentacle_steam;psvita_CUSA01991_00;test_CUSA01991_00;test_CUSA01959_00;itch_e0b7418141e1519b645172b10e01691c4ce68b79a5917f8292f3a303;psvita_Day of the tentacle remastered;origin_847fb5ef37d43a882bbc039b90b3e97395ae2014;origin_149f94d696f8df432b8cf4eb7364a9f6a898f2ca0e5f36cde719ae988c6e9fdb;psx_Day of the Tentacle Remastered;humble_dayofthetentacle_bundle_steam;xboxone_2102421406;test_/day-of-the-tentacle-remastered-free-download/;test_day-of-the-tentacle-remastered;playfire_day-of-the-tentacle-remastered;humble_dayofthetentacleremastered_bundle_steam;itch_63056;generic_51152742697893332;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
FTL Faster than Light;FTL: Faster Than Light;FTL Faster than Light;;videos\FTL Faster than Light (2012).mp4;OK;images\FTL Faster than Light (2012).webp;;Steam;Subset Games;Subset Games;14/09/2012;"In FTL you experience the atmosphere of running a spaceship trying to save the galaxy. It's a dangerous mission, with every encounter presenting a unique challenge with multiple solutions. What will you do if a heavy missile barrage shuts down your shields? Reroute all power to the engines in an attempt to escape, power up additional weapons to blow your enemy out of the sky, or take the fight to them with a boarding party? This ""spaceship simulation roguelike-like"" allows you to take your ship and crew on an adventure through a randomly generated galaxy filled with glory and bitter defeat.";Role-playing (RPG), Strategy, Indie, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/212680/9010/3b8455f5c0716335bcf4719fcbe479b01da86a82/1750480987/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447356626;humble_ftlfasterthanlight_bundle, steam_212680;steam_212680;gog_1207659102;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003511;humble_ftlfasterthanlight_bundle;humble_ftlfasterthanlight;humble_hib9_ftlfasterthanlight_steam;humble_ftlgog;epic_Blowfish;humble_ftlsteam;xboxone_1900462811;winstore_9nwntzqw4g8g;humble_ftlfasterthanlight_fightforjustice_steam;test_212680;test_/ftl-faster-than-light-free-download/;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003511@subscription;test_epic_ftlfasterthanlight;test_gfn_100818211;test_gfn_212680;test_100299511;test_gfn_100299511;test_gfn_Blowfish;generic_51152847405747984;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Hacknet;Hacknet;Hacknet;;videos\Hacknet (2015).mp4;OK;images\Hacknet (2015).webp;;Steam;Team Fractal Alligator;Fellow Traveller;12/08/2015;"Hacknet is an immersive, terminal-based hacking simulator for PC. Dive down a rabbit hoIe as you follow the instructions of a recently deceased hacker, whose death may not have been the accident the media reports. Using old school command prompts and real hacking processes, you’ll solve the mystery with minimal hand-holding and a rich world full of secrets to explore.

Exploring the volatile nature of personal privacy, the prevalence of corporate greed, and the hidden powers of hackers on the internet, Hacknet delivers a true hacking simulation, while offering a support system that allows total beginners get a grasp of the real-world applications and commands found throughout the game.";Indie, Puzzle, Simulator;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/365450/39496/9a0fbabffd419ca5983102eb6d2621a00af58396/1750516645/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1532385499;humble_hacknet, steam_365450;steam_365450;gog_1439474400;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002048;humble_hacknet;humble_hacknet_trove;amazon_f6e3da4d-62fd-475f-845a-6e708723de00;humble_f6e3da4d-62fd-475f-845a-6e708723de00;twitch_f6e3da4d-62fd-475f-845a-6e708723de00;humble_hacknet_bundle_steam;discord_449639683740270612;humble_hacknet_steam;3ds_f6e3da4d-62fd-475f-845a-6e708723de00;totalwar_hacknet_bundle_steam;d2d_hacknet_bundle_steam;humble_hacknet_australiafirerelief_bundle_steam;humble_hacknet_conquercovid19_steam;test_11707;test_Hacknet;test_365450;test_/hacknet-free-download/;playfire_hacknet;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002048@subscription;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0002132@subscription;itch_228313;test_steam_hacknet;test_gfn_365450;test_gfn_100228211;test_55ca9bb85f0df2e9ae62c85e94737b012f7c3ed6;test_3b17a9d0cbaf248fd2400e7c865c21b7d287c8c1;amazon_4749912f-59d7-4bd2-b759-03b35889db4a;generic_51152946557157061;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
