Super Time Force Ultra;Super Time Force Ultra;Super Time Force Ultra;;videos\Super Time Force Ultra (2014).mp4;OK;images\Super Time Force Ultra (2014).webp;;Steam;Capybara Games;Capybara Games;25/08/2014;Super Time Force Ultra is an action-packed platformer with a time-travelling twist! You’re in control of time itself, bending and stretching it to your advantage on the battlefield. Rewind time and choose when to jump back into the action, teaming-up with your past selves in a unique single-player co-op experience! Take control of up to 16 unique characters, and battle across 6 different time periods, from the long-ago past to the far-away future.;Adventure, Indie, Platform, Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/250700/24229/f02acf6323b482e917fb602910dd33e0d821e9aa/1751250038/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1463132372;humble_supertimeforceultra, steam_250700;steam_250700;gog_1207665553;psn_CUSA02013_00;psn_CUSA01938_00;humble_supertimeforceultra;psvita_CUSA01938_00;humble_supertimeforce_ultra_steam;psn_EP2003-PCSB00786_00-SUPERTIMEFORCEUL;test_CUSA02013_00;test_CUSA01938_00;humble_supertimeforceultra_fightforjustice_steam;test_super-time-force-ultra;humble_supertimeforceultra_dayofthedevsletsgetdigital_bundle_steam;generic_51154297796130336;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
