Journey;Journey;Journey;;videos\Journey (2012).mp4;OK;images\Journey (2012).webp;;Psn;ThatGameCompany;Sony Computer Entertainment, Annapurna Interactive;13/03/2012;"In Journey the player controls a robed figure in a vast desert, traveling towards a mountain in the distance. Other players on the same journey can be discovered, and two players can meet and assist each other, but they cannot communicate via speech or text and cannot see each other's names. The only form of communication between the two is a musical chime. This chime also transforms dull, stiff pieces of cloth found throughout the levels into vibrant red, affecting the game world and allowing the player to progress through the levels. The robed figure wears a trailing scarf, which when charged by approaching floating pieces of cloth, briefly allows the player to float through the air.

The developers sought to evoke in the player a sense of smallness and wonder, and to forge an emotional connection between them and the anonymous players they meet along the way. The music, composed by Austin Wintory, dynamically responds to the player's actions, building a single theme to represent the game's emotional arc throughout the story. Reviewers of the game praised the visual and auditory art as well as the sense of companionship created by playing with a stranger, calling it a moving and emotional experience. Journey won several ""game of the year"" awards and received several other awards and nominations, including a Best Score Soundtrack for Visual Media nomination for the 2013 Grammy Awards.";Adventure, Platform;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/638230/445304/488a13fed8afd15efbca108f2424ffa7accf823f/1750565278/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1646936227;psn_CUSA00470_00;psn_CUSA00470_00;psn_CUSA00694_00;epic_Lemur;psn_CUSA01982_00;psn_CUSA01036_00;psn_CUSA01983_00;psvita_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-KJOURNEYDEM00001;psvita_NPUA80275_00;psvita_CUSA00694_00;psn_EP9000-NPEA00288_00-KJOURNEYDEM00001;psn_EP9000-CUSA00470_00-JOURNEYPS4061115;test_CUSA00470_00;test_EP9000-NPEA00288_00-KJOURNEYDEM00001;vision_NPUA80275;psn_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-KJOURNEYDEM00001;psn_EP9000-NPEA00288_00-JOURNEYYYPRIVATE;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNYCUTOUT0;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNEYRETURN;origin_0d3703e1176df5bfc70b8c84437798dc702cf76c;origin_7e6eaea54b6330d1929d40fc6ded6ecd5e667a6c1be962a6da93b1e55c41b61f;steam_638230;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNYGUARDTP;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-JOURNEYYYPRIVATE;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-JOURNEYCONCEPTDT;discord_8aeaa311-9ee8-4d0c-9c66-ad636555186e;test_CUSA00694_00;psn_NPUA80275_00;vision_NPEA00288;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNYHEAD000;itch_755c17ecd585df978fc2f5adac0ac893c000f1fc7d413a8c44b9070e;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNYGUARDHD;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNYCREATRE;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNYANCESTR;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNEYWONDER;test_UP9000-NPUA80275_00-AVAJOURNYEARLYCP;epic_LemurDummy;c64_11835;test_/journey-free-download/;test_journey;playfire_journey;amiga_journey;amiga_journey-1;ps2_NPUA80275;psx_NPUA80275;psn_CUSA02833_00;psn_CUSA02816_00;psn_CUSA02832_00;psx_CUSA00470_00;humble_journey_row_steam;generic_51153161190567062
Uncharted The Nathan Drake Collection;Uncharted: The Nathan Drake Collection;Uncharted The Nathan Drake Collection;;;OK;images\Uncharted The Nathan Drake Collection (2015).webp;;Psn;Naughty Dog;Sony Computer Entertainment;07/10/2015;"Uncharted: The Nathan Drake Collection is a remastered compilation of the action-adventure shooter platform video games Drake's Fortune, Among Thieves, and Drake's Deception. Ported by Bluepoint Games, the collection was released exclusively for the PlayStation 4 on October 7, 2015 in Europe and October 9th, 2015 in North America.

The Nathan Drake Collection features the original three games in the Uncharted series with 1080p resolution, 60 frames per second, better lighting, textures and models. The collection also implements a ""Photo Mode"", a mode where the player can freeze the game at any moment to take personalized screenshots, derived from Naughty Dog's other remastered entry, The Last of Us Remastered, as well as new trophies. The ported games only include their respective single-player modes.

The pre-ordered version of The Nathan Drake Collection includes the ""Nathan Drake Pack"", which consists of single-player skins of iconic Nathan Drake outfits, as well as two weapons: the Golden AK-47 and Golden 92FS - 9mm. Pre-ordering the collection as a digital download through the PlayStation Store would also give an exclusive Uncharted: The Nathan Drake Collection PlayStation 4 dynamic theme.

Purchasing The Nathan Drake Collection, and owning a valid subscription to PlayStation Plus, before the expiry date of December 13, 2015 would grant the player exclusive access to the multiplayer beta of A Thief's End.";Adventure, Platform, Puzzle, Shooter;;;psn_CUSA02343_00;psn_CUSA02344_00;psn_CUSA02320_00;psn_CUSA02343_00;psn_CUSA02826_00;psn_CUSA01399_00;psn_CUSA01398_00;psvita_CUSA02320_00;test_CUSA02343_00;test_CUSA02320_00;psx_CUSA02344_00;psn_CUSA03270_00;psn_CUSA03262_00;psn_CUSA03331_00;generic_51295418017555787;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
