Clear the arena of enemies while racking up a big fat Combo with swift kills and well timed Bombs. If it all gets a bit too much you can use your Time Buffer to slow down the action and turn defeat into victory. Players can compete across seven different game modes with online high-score tables and Achievements in their pursuit of twin-stick perfection.";Indie, Shooter, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/107600/18440/83eff4a10434e860639414cb0e6729710ad9e591/1751250925/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447360906;steam_107600;steam_107600;generic_51295426632148798;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
