Grand Theft Auto San Andreas;Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas;Grand Theft Auto San Andreas;;;OK;images\Grand Theft Auto San Andreas (2005).webp;;Steam;Rockstar North;Take-Two Interactive, Rockstar Games;07/06/2005;Returning after his mother's murder to the semi-fictional city of Los Santos (based on Los Angeles), Carl Johnson, a former gang banger, must take back the streets for his family and friends by gaining respect and once again gaining control over the city. However, a story filled with plots, lies and corruption will lead him to trudge the entire state of San Andreas (based on California and Nevada) to get revenge.;Adventure, Shooter, Racing;;no_section;steam_12120;steam_12120;steam_12250;xboxone_35962435;xboxone_1805889020;psn_CUSA03541_00;psn_CUSA03506_00;xboxone_2008436942;steam_206270;xboxone_2130408740;ps2_7120;xboxone_1610681612;egg_18;riot_31;beamdog_18;riot_18;ps2_SLUS-20946;humble_gta_sanandreas_bundle_steam;ps2_SLES-51541;rockstar_18;vision_BLUS31584;humble_gta_sanandreas_de_steam;ps2_SLES-52541;ps2_SLES-52927;test_CUSA03506_00;humble_grandtheftauto_sanandreas_rockstarsocial;humble_gta_sanandreas_steam;vision_BLES02219;ps2_SLPM-65984;ps2_Grand Theft Auto - San Andreas;test_/grand-theft-auto-san-andreas-free-download/;test_grand-theft-auto-san-andreas;playfire_grand-theft-auto-san-andreas;xboxone_1414793400;beamdog_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20211027014142;rockstar_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20211027015527;beamdog_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20211027022834;rockstar_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20211027030013;winstore_3bf17de90ed5b16cd616c690229151c46145a042;ps2_Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas;test_d69c5b0cfd95f174444b9db4a11df34a6114d553;generic_51152930477101408;;;;;;;;;
Manhunt;Manhunt;Manhunt;;videos\Manhunt (2004).mp4;OK;images\Manhunt (2004).webp;;Steam;Rockstar North;Take-Two Interactive, Rockstar Games;20/04/2004;"Manhunt is a third-person stealth horror game. The game consists of twenty levels, and four bonus levels that can be unlocked; the levels are referred to as ""scenes"". Players survive the Scenes by dispatching enemy gang members known as ""Hunters"", occasionally with firearms but primarily by stealthily executing them in gruesome, over-the-top ways.

The player is rated at the end of each level, primarily dependent on the gruesomeness of the killings and the speed of completion, from one (unimpressive) to five (extremely competent) stars. Executions are preferred in order to gain a higher score, thus encouraging players to play as viscerally as possible. The game's locales are full of ""dark spots"" and shadows where the player can hide while being chased by the Hunters; hiding in these dark areas makes the player invisible to opponents.";Shooter, Tactical;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/12130/914/7d17608b928efd9a78554e22fe6ab4979923a460/1750484484/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447351212;steam_12130;steam_12130;psn_CUSA03512_00;psn_CUSA03545_00;ps2_CK6LMOZ36I;humble_manhunt_bundle_steam;ps2_SLES-52023;ps2_6108;test_CUSA03512_00;humble_manhunt_steam;ps2_SLUS-20827;test_/manhunt-free-download/;ps2_Manhunt;xboxone_1849239853;test_7d54168284c12859afbc6126dae929e344ce07fa;generic_51153251209217929;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Max Payne;Max Payne 3;Max Payne;;;OK;images\Max Payne (2001).webp;;Steam;Rockstar Vancouver, Rockstar New England, Rockstar Toronto, Rockstar London;Take-Two Interactive, Rockstar Games;01/06/2012;"Max Payne 3 is a third-person shooter in which the player assumes the role of its titular character, Max Payne. A new feature to the series, introduced in Max Payne 3, is the cover system, which allows players to gain a tactical advantage, and avoid taking damage from enemies. To progress through the linear story, players take on enemies throughout levels. The game features interactive cutscenes which transition seamlessly into continuing gameplay; there are no loading screens across gameplay and cutscenes.";Shooter;;no_section;steam_12140, steam_204100;steam_204100;humble_maxpayne3_bundle_steam;egg_10;riot_40;beamdog_10;riot_10;humble_maxpayne3_rockstarpass_steam;humble_maxpayne3_de_bundle_steam;rockstar_10;psvita_NPUB30902_00;psn_EP1004-NPEB01037_00-MAXPAYNE3DIGITAL;psn_UP1004-NPUB30902_00-MAXPAYNE3DIGITAL;humble_maxpayne3_steam;humble_maxpayne3_de_steam;humble_maxpayne3_complete_rockstarsocial;origin_0a4af2820753812bbf7ea8927f7b7a0ac5c7f9c16b29efd7fb062d3b483b780f;origin_2fd766c77d2fff1359414bfbebbc23238204a74e;discord_43b7e3d8-b487-4daf-a49f-dbc6cd2936b2;test_/max-payne-3-free-download/;rockstar_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-5-20211027030013;xboxone_1689362557;xboxone_1414793323;humble_maxpayne3_standwithukraine_bundle_rgl;generic_51153262012618402;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Max Payne 2 The Fall of Max Payne;Max Payne 2: The Fall of Max Payne;Max Payne 2 The Fall of Max Payne;;;OK;images\Max Payne 2 The Fall of Max Payne (2003).webp;;Steam;Remedy Entertainment;Rockstar Games;14/10/2003;Max Payne 2 is a third-person shooter, in which the player assumes the role of Max Payne, but also plays as Mona Sax in a few levels. Initially, the player's weapon is a 9mm pistol. As they progress, players access other weapons including other handguns, shotguns, submachine guns, assault rifles, sniper rifles, and hand-thrown weapons. To move the game along, the player is told what the next objective is through Max's internal monologue, in which Max iterates what his next steps should be.;Shooter;;no_section;steam_12150;steam_12150;steam_12260;steam_210410;steam_210430;humble_maxpayne2_bundle_steam;ps2_SLES-51954;ps2_3547;humble_maxpayne2_steam;steam_202900;ps2_SLUS-20814;test_cd9e94fa6731ad025c341dbd4e73a03804ef1531;ps2_Max Payne 2 - The Fall of Max Payne;test_/max-payne-2-the-fall-of-max-payne-free-download/;pce_7790;test_7790;zx_7790;amiga_7790;xboxone_1943256869;xboxone_1414793291;ps2_SLES-52256;ps2_SLES-52338;ps2_SLES-52336;ps2_SLES-52337;test_a312acf45e3ba739a8064cb3cdc191ba388af9da;generic_51153261964430733;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
