Select from over 100 playable characters including Harry Potter, Ron Weasley and Hermione Granger. Experience the wonder of Hogwarts: attend lessons, mix potions, fly on broomsticks, and complete tasks to collect LEGO studs and relive the adventures like never before with tongue-in-cheek humor and creative customization unique to LEGO videogames.";Adventure, Platform, Puzzle;;no_section;steam_204120, steam_21130;steam_21130;gog_1423058817;uplay_124;humble_lego_harrypotter_bundle_steam;origin_OFB-EAST:109545709;psp_4OBI3VIBQW;psp_9ZGCTZIKXA;psp_4B0ILBFFRD;psp_4RSORDZCVM;nds_BLHPN0;nwii_R25EWR;humble_lego_harrypotter_steam;nds_BLHEN0;nwii_26753;psp_ULES-01351;nds_LEGO Harry Potter - Years 1-4;psx_LEGO Harry Potter: Years 1-4;psp_ULUS-10500;psn_BLUS30437_00;nwii_236b808a2859da422324895c8a3c2bf2424fc2e4;test_/lego-harry-potter-years-1-4-free-download/;psp_LEGO Harry Potter - Years 1-4;nwii_LEGO Harry Potter: Years 1-4;nwii_Lego Harry Potter Years 1-4 [English][WII-Scrubber][USA][WwW.ZoNaTorrent.CoM];test_21130;nwii_R25PWR;psp_LEGO Harry Potter: Years 1-4;test_LEGO Harry Potter Years 1-4;atari_LEGO Harry Potter Years 1-4;nwii_LEGO Harry Potter - Years 1-4;generic_51153209577991787;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Sins of a Solar Empire Rebellion;Sins of a Solar Empire: Rebellion;Sins of a Solar Empire Rebellion;;videos\Sins of a Solar Empire Rebellion (2012).mp4;OK;images\Sins of a Solar Empire Rebellion (2012).webp;;Steam;Stardock, Ironclad Games;Stardock;12/06/2012;"The Next Installment to the Award-Winning RTS. 
 
While many were hopeful that diplomacy would finally end the war, differing opinions on what should be done, along with the depleted power of the controlling factions, has led to a splintering of the groups involved. 
 
The loyalist members of the Trader Emergency Coalition adopt a policy of isolation, focusing on enhanced defenses to ride out the rest of the war. Those who rebel against the coalition take on a purely militant view, coming to the opinion that the only way to bring peace is by ultimately crushing all who oppose them - especially xenos. 
 
For the first time in their history, the war creates a schism in the Advent Unity. The loyalists seek to continue their policy of revenge against the Traders, and to assimilate all others to the Unity’s influence. However, others amongst the Advent suspect that a corrupting influence from within has diverted the Unity from its proper destiny. 
 
The divide created in the Vasari Empire is less pronounced, but just as severe to their people. With the Vasari now practically frantic to move on to new space, the loyalist faction abandons cooperation and decides to take the resources they need by any means necessary. Having accepted the need to work together, the rebel faction feels that their best chance for survival is to work with the other races and bring them along to flee the approaching enemy. 
 
Take the battle for galactic supremacy to its ultimate level in Sins of a Solar Empire: Rebellion – a standalone RT4X game that combines the tactics of real-time strategy with the depth of the 4X genre (eXplore, eXpand, eXploit, eXterminate).";Strategy, Indie, Simulator, Real Time Strategy (RTS);;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/204880/7250/6d8b3001bcc2224bbadf91b30ffc8bb5303e2960/1750492823/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1683215410;steam_204880;steam_204880;kartridge_204880;amazon_204880;gg_204880;gmg_204880;humble_sinsofasolarempire_rebellion_freegame_steam;humble_sinsofasolarempire_rebellion_steam;humble_sinsofasolarempire_rebellion_bundle_steam;humble_storefront_sinsofasolarempire_rebellion_steam;steam_205670;discord_a191247e-3af0-4f78-86d9-5f8fa42fca78;test_204880;test_/sins-of-a-solar-empire-rebellion-free-download/;test_sins-of-a-solar-empire-rebellion;playfire_sins-of-a-solar-empire-rebellion;gog_1448030136;test_gfn_100318811;xboxone_2120931003;generic_51154203184485063;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
