Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition;Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition;Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition;;;OK;images\Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition (2025).webp;;Steam;Tarsier Studios;Bandai Namco Entertainment;24/06/2025;"Little Nightmares is a puzzle-platform horror adventure game developed by Tarsier Studios and published by Bandai Namco Entertainment. Set in a mysterious world, Little Nightmares follows the journey of Six, a hungry little girl who must escape the Maw, an iron vessel inhabited by monstrous, twisted beings.

The Enhanced Edition improves upon the original release by supporting 4K resolution at 60 FPS and enhancing visual effects, including RTX reflections, improved water effects, additional particles, and volumetric lighting.

It also offers players the option to choose between Quality Mode or Performance Mode, allowing them to prioritize either visual fidelity or frame rate based on their preferences.";Adventure, Platform, Puzzle;;no_section;steam_2149010;steam_2149010;xboxone_1936213191;xboxone_1935490407;generic_58915395283299013;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
