100 Orange Juice;100 Orange Juice;100 Orange Juice;;videos\100 Orange Juice (2009).mp4;OK;images\100 Orange Juice (2009).webp;;Steam;Orange_Juice;Fruitbat Factory, Orange_Juice;15/08/2009;"100% Orange Juice is a goal-oriented boardgame played by OrangeJuice's all-star cast including characters from Acceleration of Suguri, Flying Red Barrel: A Diary of Little Aviator, Sora, and QP Shooting.

This is a world where dogs, people and machines fly through the air. In that world, a small patch of darkness was born. Infinitesimal at first, it gradually began to envelope everything...

A youth named Kai, led by the mysterious life form known as Marie Poppo, begins a journey that will span worlds. The black, bottomless darkness of desire slowly eats away at both Kai and the world itself...

Let Marie Poppo lead you into a mysterious world to play. Grab your deck of cards and let the games begin!";Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS), Indie, Card & Board Game;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/282800/1400253690/5d91082bc4616fbdc0242c5ff228d85adee2abc4/1767097226/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1767272429;steam_282800;steam_282800;humble_100_orangejuice;humble_100_orangejuice_steam;steam_steam_282800;test_/100-orange-juice-free-download/;test_100-orange-juice;playfire_100-orange-juice;fanatical_100-orange-juice;humble_100orangejuice_bundle_steam;test_282800;test_sashagame_26;generic_51141226780161571;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
