Dark Sector;Dark Sector;Dark Sector;;videos\Dark Sector (2009).mp4;OK;images\Dark Sector (2009).webp;;Steam;Digital Extremes;D3 Publisher, Aspyr Media, Zoo Corporation, Noviy Disk, ND Games;24/03/2009;Dark Sector thrusts players into the role of Hayden Tenno, a covert operative sent on a dangerous mission into Lasria, an Eastern European city on the brink of ruin that hides a deadly Cold War secret. In the midst of this mission, Hayden is attacked by an unknown enemy and infected by the Technocyte Virus, a brutal bio-weapon that twists its victims into mindless killing machines. Surviving this attack, Hayden finds that the Technocyte virus has granted him powerful, inhuman abilities unlike anything he has ever seen. Now, he must evolve with his powers, survive and become a hero.;Shooter;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/29900/1729/1fff19116f68b4db7eda07c11eb29a0d87552608/1750484965/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447351734;steam_29900;steam_29900;psn_BLUS30116_00;generic_51152737838706848;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Day of Defeat;Day of Defeat;Day of Defeat;;;OK;images\Day of Defeat (2003).webp;;Steam;Valve;Activision, Valve;01/05/2003;Enlist in an intense brand of Axis vs. Allied teamplay set in the WWII European Theatre of Operations. Players assume the role of light/assault/heavy infantry, sniper or machine-gunner class, each with a unique arsenal of historical weaponry at their disposal. Missions are based on key historical operations. And, as war rages, players must work together with their squad to accomplish a variety of mission-specific objectives.;Shooter;;no_section;steam_30;steam_30;test_30;winstore_774734de7f073a88b1544c1989588635c84d6921;generic_51152742599165373;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Adr1ft;Adr1ft;Adr1ft;;videos\Adr1ft (2016).mp4;OK;images\Adr1ft (2016).webp;;Steam;Three One Zero;505 Games;28/03/2016;Adr1ft is an immersive First Person Experience (FPX) that tells the story of an astronaut in peril. Floating silently amongst the wreckage of a destroyed space station with no memory and a severely damaged EVA suit slowly leaking oxygen, the only survivor struggles to determine the cause of the catastrophic event that took the lives of everyone on board. The player fights to stay alive by exploring the wreckage for precious resources, and overcomes the challenges of an unforgiving environment to repair the damaged EEV and safely return home.;Adventure, Indie, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/300060/52314/f2b9b8a6bd7e17909c4a64a3b5b6a3327bff6c0c/1751262631/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1467226027;steam_300060;steam_300060;psn_CUSA02519_00;psn_CUSA02572_00;humble_adr1ft_steam;test_CUSA02572_00;itch_ADR1FT [FitGirl Repack];itch_274eddef7a4d2c05ef54bd2b90ab19785b3e24ebf483bebca2e5da54;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xBRFIxRlQgW0ZpdEdpcmwgUmVwYWNrXQ==;epic_ADR1FT [FitGirl Repack];winstore_ADR1FT [FitGirl Repack];origin_13d3fc8c4557c9ab6116964b4faad753ecf080ed;origin_50027bf11a94e8f31b5f9f552d4d643902bfd3b4c2f5885d26a99db713af61a4;origin_76ebe992364f5597d6da0570fe73bad9ec0a36ffd066b6d51501e14dcbbdba9b;origin_6342e47bf464a3100b240963ae295d6cc8ec11aae05aef4f19594d67aa33d0cf;discord_fb890797-2d58-4d01-90d6-e994ace464e7;psx_ADR1FT;steam_steam_300060;test_sashagame_340;generic_51141385399406979;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
