Planet of the Eyes;Planet of the Eyes;Planet of the Eyes;;videos\Planet of the Eyes (2015).mp4;OK;images\Planet of the Eyes (2015).webp;;Steam;Cococucumber;Cococucumber;24/08/2015;Planet of the Eyes is an action-puzzle platformer with a retro sci-fi inspired aesthetic and a mystery-driven storyline. At the outset of the game, the player - an exploration robot - starts his search for the source of a pulsing signal on the planet. Along the way, the robot negotiates multiple dangers, solves environment-based puzzles, and uncovers the truth about the Planet of the Eyes through the audiologs of a surviving crew member. The fate of both these survivors and the planet itself will hang in the balance as the player contemplates a destiny that was meant to be unavoidable.;Adventure, Indie, Platform, Puzzle;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/350970/119985/d67ac7df3e3d4f227ea9bcae0c0218c364d0ff0b/1751281738/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1503938692;steam_350970;steam_350970;xboxone_650235919;psn_CUSA07531_00;psn_CUSA09870_00;humble_planetoftheeyes_steam;test_CUSA07531_00;humble_planetoftheeyes_fightforjustice_steam;generic_51153497063445309;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
