Dragon's Dogma Dark Arisen;Dragon's Dogma: Dark Arisen;Dragon's Dogma Dark Arisen;;videos\Dragons Dogma Dark Arisen (2016).mp4;OK;images\Dragons Dogma Dark Arisen (2016).webp;;Steam;Capcom;Capcom;15/01/2016;"Dragon’s Dogma: Dark Arisen contains all the content from the original Dragon’s Dogma plus the additional content from its sequel, including the Bitterblack Isle area, filled with challenging new enemies and quests, and additional high level weapons and armour sets. Along with its stunningly high resolution graphics and full Steam platform support, this is the ultimate franchise experience for PC players. 
 
Set in a huge open world, Dragon’s Dogma: Dark Arisen presents a rewarding action combat experience. Players embark on an epic adventure in a rich, living world with three AI companions, known as Pawns. These partners fight independently, demonstrating prowess and ability that they have developed based on traits learnt from each player. PC users can share these Pawns online and reap rewards of treasure, tips and strategy hints for taking down the terrifying enemies. Pawns can also be borrowed when specific skills are needed to complete various challenging quests.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/367500/50247/8c40fa32e91ab28da90d6ae2236905630c8c9624/1750517658/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1452876592;steam_367500;steam_367500;gog_1242384383;xboxone_849613404;psn_CUSA07340_00;psn_CUSA07385_00;psn_CUSA09431_00;psn_CUSA07316_00;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_monthly_row_steam;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_monthly_ru_steam;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_row_steam;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_monthly_br_steam;test_EP0102-NPEB01268_00-DDDA000000000000;nswitch_010032C00AC58000;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_row_preorder_steam;humble_dragonsdogmadarkarisen_row_bundle_steam;humble_dragonsdogmadarkarisen_asia_bundle_steam;humble_dragonsdogmadarkarisen_rucis_bundle_steam;humble_dragonsdogmadarkarisen_br_bundle_steam;discord_20318268-37c3-4492-bbfd-98795400e4a5;vision_BLES01794;test_/dragons-dogma-dark-arisen-free-download/;vision_NPUB31117;nuuvem_8e097cdaa56a27f2206d29d6ce9d50ffa3bc9251;humble_dragonsdogmadarkarisen_capcomsummer2022bundle_row_bundle_steam;humble_dragonsdogmadarkarisen_latam_bundle_steam;humble_dragonsdogmadarkarisen_apac_bundle_steam;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_br_steam;nuuvem_678f3bbd73fa534dd089634d69bf0083bfff6df7;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_capcomsummer2024_na_bundle_steam;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_capcomsummer2024_latam_bundle_steam;humble_dragonsdogma_darkarisen_capcomsummer2024_row_bundle_steam;hum