Devil May Cry HD Collection;Devil May Cry HD Collection;Devil May Cry HD Collection;;videos\Devil May Cry HD Collection (2018).mp4;OK;images\Devil May Cry HD Collection (2018).webp;;Steam;Capcom;Capcom;13/03/2018;"The popular stylish action games Devil May Cry, Devil May Cry 2, and Devil May Cry 3 Special Edition return in one collection!

As Dante, the ultimate devil hunter, you'll join forces with appealing characters such as Trish, Lady, and Lucia and enjoy incredible action for the first time in blistering 60fps. 

Devil May Cry: The first appearance of Dante, the ultimate devil hunter! With the blood of a legendary demon warrior flowing through his veins, Dante takes on the king of the underworld, Mundus. 

Devil May Cry 2: Dance with the devil. Set decades after the first game, this sequel adds moves like the wall run and Rain Storm, bringing Dante's action to the next level of stylishness. The bonus mode Bloody Palace also makes its debut.  

Devil May Cry 3 Special Edition: This prequel to the first Devil May Cry introduces Vergil, Dante's twin brother. Customize your game style by selecting from various styles to level up and gain new moves and abilities.";Adventure, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/631510/146385/7d07d2ebe2ed3aff95901f1e78d5b35e692e97d2/1750564352/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1518545015;steam_631510;steam_631510;xboxone_528369592;psn_CUSA09263_00;psn_CUSA09407_00;psn_CUSA09261_00;amazon_c24336e8-b8e2-4537-bf1b-9f6cc6cee40a;twitch_c24336e8-b8e2-4537-bf1b-9f6cc6cee40a;humble_devilmaycry_hdcollection_ps3;test_CUSA09263_00;humble_c24336e8-b8e2-4537-bf1b-9f6cc6cee40a;psn_UP0102-NPUB30988_00-DMCCHDDIGITAL000;humble_devilmaycryhdcollection_row_steam;3ds_c24336e8-b8e2-4537-bf1b-9f6cc6cee40a;test_UP0102-NPUB30988_00-DMCCHDDIGITAL000;vision_BLES01228;itch_e290c4513d98c253fcf1eebd5bbb714542cc375e32510c8b5bb674f7;origin_21c23608491316e1de22c53a8279b78514e08fc5;origin_a62fd721fde2e8f995f4676b40ebcb6f3b01f69a133b80b3a336f3d586971de3;discord_0161fc72-4e5c-4449-83e6-0d6db438440c;psx_Devil May Cry HD Collection;psn_NPUB30988_00;test_/devil-may-cry-hd-collection-free-download/;test_devil-may-cry-hd-collection;humble_devilmaycryhdcollection_restricted_steam;humble_devilmaycryhdcollection_row_bundle_steam;humble_devilmaycryhdcollection_latam_bundle_steam;humble_devilmaycryhdcollection_restricted_bundle_steam;test_c62e4561be7417ea28ae82ca5cbba578ad3bfe68;gog_1351925727;humble_devilmaycry_hdcollection_specialedition_row_bundle_steam;humble_devilmaycry_hdcollection_specialedition_na_bundle_steam;generic_51152763680502780;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
