Take the controls as Jedi-to-be Anakin Skywalker or any one of over 20 pod racers. These lightning-quick vehicles are capable of reaching simulated speeds of up to 600 miles per hour while skimming a mere 4 feet above the ground. Feel the full-force blast while avoiding hazards such as methane lakes, meteor showers, and the notorious Tusken Raiders. You can race alone or against a friend in split-screen mode on more than 21 courses that span over 8 different worlds. This level of customization adds excellent replay value.";Sport, Arcade;;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/808910/194823/da02bc8252d1721311a3ea5b529c0174fe6c695a/1750585927/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1542410784;steam_808910;gog_1288119483;steam_808910;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003397;n64_C53C1035;n64_494C667A;humble_starwars_episode1racer_steam;n64_E0F46629;n64_Star Wars Episode I: Racer;n64_Star Wars Episode I - Racer;n64_EDE47E8A;ngameboy_Star Wars Episode I - Racer;dc_Star Wars - Episode I - Racer;discord_46c5c147-2794-4946-a83a-75a700026d8c;discord_4150a698-efe6-4cb8-baea-c4bf4cc76f74;test_970723877722259cc3e7596d59ba7402fb68305e;test_108aac62d48948908135a2bec5bc069f169164e3;test_dc503e18ddbe2dfa7a711183e85cfab279c56680;n64_dc503e18ddbe2dfa7a711183e85cfab279c56680;test_9a82ca7c72b64437ccf995ad75cd9d26555b7c63;psn_CUSA18198_00;psn_CUSA18211_00;n64_Star Wars - Episode 1 - Racer;test_eb3f6b7918b9608a0b767c9d56b127e606a7ac89;test_b2089737e122cf346775edbcfcdaa020d9d0cad5;test_16686d94d4892065747eddeb1289a45a1759986b;xboxone_1883232264;test_91f19c3ce12f355fd9f7d4b7d8cc3a781b858f55;test_3542d5597c8a56ea8f5c63bceae97a24c4c08d58;ngameboy_51487522013187;humble_starwars_episode1racer_switch;test_8d55c76dbefcfcfb3c38ce17c924ef04accf7c8d;nswitch_0100BD100FFBE000;test_c7554adec4bcb07ae45ca77588b4f04e38d6d9c6;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003397@subscription;dc_Star Wars Episode I Racer;ngameboy_Star Wars Episode I - Racer GBC;test_2c92fed5e3b6be0edc454d542c61871665a6be0e;dc_Star Wars Episode I - Racer;psn_CUSA267