Two of the authors are the comics artist Régis Loisel and Philippe Ulrich.

This 3D puzzle-platformer was developed by Eko Software and published in 2001 by Cryo Interactive, the team behind the Game Boy Color edition of the game.

Also, Loisel created an animated series of 8 episodes in 2005 (VHS/DVD) based on this title.";Platform, Puzzle, Adventure; - CRYO;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbKg3-ey05Y;igdb_95440;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
