2004 - Myst 4 - Revelation;Myst 4 - Revelation;Myst 4 - Revelation;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - CYAN WORLDS\2004 - Myst 4 - Revelation;;OK;images\2004 - Myst 4 - Revelation.jpg;2004;Warez;Ubisoft Montreal;Cyan Worlds;30/09/2004;"Myst IV: Revelation is the fourth installment in the Myst computer game series, developed and published by Ubisoft. Like Myst III: Exile, Revelation combines pre-rendered graphics with digital video, but also features real-time 3D effects for added realism.

The plot of Revelation ties up loose ends from the original Myst. The player is summoned by Atrus, a man who creates links to other worlds known as Ages by writing special linking books. Almost twenty years earlier, Atrus' two sons nearly destroyed all of his linking books and were imprisoned; Atrus now wishes to see if his sons' imprisonment has reformed them. The player ends up traveling to each brother's prison, in an effort to recover Atrus' daughter Yeesha from the brothers' plot.";Point-and-click, Puzzle, Adventure; - CYAN WORLDS;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eI1IxdAoSbw;igdb_798;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2004 - Uru, Complete Chronicles;Uru, Complete Chronicles;Uru, Complete Chronicles;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - CYAN WORLDS\2004 - Uru, Complete Chronicles;;OK;images\2004 - Uru Complete Chronicles.jpg;2004;Warez;Cyan Worlds;Cyan Worlds;07/07/2004;The critically acclaimed adventure of Uru: Ages Beyond Myst returns with this special collection that contains more Uru than ever before. Already the deepest Myst adventure to date, Uru is significantly expanded with the addition of To D'ni and The Path of the Shell, expansion packs that will take Uru beyond your imagination.;Puzzle, Adventure; - CYAN WORLDS;;igdb_16202;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2005 - Myst 5 - End of Ages;Myst 5 - End of Ages;Myst 5 - End of Ages;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - CYAN WORLDS\2005 - Myst 5 - End of Ages;;OK;images\2005 - Myst 5 - End of Ages.jpg;2005;Warez;Cyan Worlds, Beenox;;20/09/2005;"Myst V: End of Ages is a 2005 adventure video game, and the fifth and final installment in the Myst series. As in previous games in the series, End of Ages's gameplay consists of navigating worlds known as ""Ages"" via the use of special books and items which act as portals. On each Age, the player solves puzzles and discovers story clues hidden in the Ages or written down in diaries and journals. The player's actions in the game decide the fate of the ancient D'ni civilization.";Puzzle, Strategy, Adventure; - CYAN WORLDS;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8l-4l4Ga2QU;igdb_8475;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
