Rookie One responds to a distress call coming from a ship in the nebula. Once there, he discovers an Imperial presence. As the story progresses, it becomes clear that the Empire is somehow responsible for at least some of the more recent disappearances.";Shooter, Arcade; - STAR WARS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/456540/55182/0a364da7972fbe50944bbba6af3608743e2f9888/1751288010/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1462237638;gog_1429011813, gog_1429104954, gog_1429105182;gog_1429105182;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003196;psx_Star Wars - Rebel Assault II - The Hidden Empire;psx_Star Wars - Rebel Assault II;test_3373020792451039695;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003196@subscription;psx_Star Wars: Rebel Assault 2 - The Hidden Empire;psn_PPSA07366_00;psn_CUSA33312_00;psn_CUSA33313_00;psn_PPSA07367_00;psn_PPSA07526_00;psn_CUSA33568_00;generic_51154260089320776;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
