1999 - Star Wars Episode 1 Racer (Steam);Star Wars Episode 1 Racer;Star Wars Episode 1 Racer;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\1999 - Star Wars Episode 1 Racer (Steam);;OK;images\1999 - Star Wars Episode 1 Racer (Steam).jpg;1999;Steam;LucasArts;Aspyr Media, Nintendo, LucasArts, Gradiente;18/05/1999;"Star Wars: Episode 1 - Racer lets you participate in the famous pod race sequence that was the critical highlight of the film Star Wars: Episode I, The Phantom Menace back in 1999.

Take the controls as Jedi-to-be Anakin Skywalker or any one of over 20 pod racers. These lightning-quick vehicles are capable of reaching simulated speeds of up to 600 miles per hour while skimming a mere 4 feet above the ground. Feel the full-force blast while avoiding hazards such as methane lakes, meteor showers, and the notorious Tusken Raiders. You can race alone or against a friend in split-screen mode on more than 21 courses that span over 8 different worlds. This level of customization adds excellent replay value.";Racing; - STAR WARS;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QfmBfJzt_io;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
1999 - Star Wars, X-Wing Alliance (Steam);Star Wars, X-Wing Alliance;Star Wars, X-Wing Alliance;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\1999 - Star Wars, X-Wing Alliance (Steam);videos\Star Wars X-Wing Alliance (1999).mp4;OK;images\Star Wars X-Wing Alliance (1999).webp;1999;Steam;Totally Games;LucasArts;28/02/1999;"The conflict is escalating...

A neutral family fights for its business - and its survival - and is swept up in the struggle against the encroaching Empire. You must defy the strong-arm tactics of a rival family who will stop at nothing to destroy your trading company. Ultimately, you will join the Rebel Alliance for a series of covert assignments and uncover information about the Empire's second Death Star project. The finale? You'll find yourself at the controls of the legendary Millennium Falcon , flying against the massive Imperial fleet in the Battle of Endor. Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance puts you right in the middle of the epic Star Wars conflict - and takes space combat excitement to new heights.";Shooter, Simulator; - STAR WARS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/361670/35001/7d228404eb9d6303c4ec427ce27ba1975adcb46c/1750515957/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447373611;steam_361670;steam_361670;gog_1421404763;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003339;humble_starwars_xwingalliance_trove;humble_starwars_xwingalliance_steam;totalwar_starwars_xwingalliance_steam;d2d_starwars_xwingalliance_steam;test_169;test_361670;test_star-wars-x-wing-alliance;playfire_star-wars-x-wing-alliance;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003339@subscription;generic_51154261156609599;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2001 - Star Wars Battle For Naboo;Star Wars Battle For Naboo;Star Wars Battle For Naboo;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2001 - Star Wars Battle For Naboo;;OK;images\2001 - Star Wars Battle For Naboo.jpg;2001;Warez;Factor 5, LucasArts;LucasArts, THQ, Gradiente;18/12/2000;"Attention defenders of Naboo! The Trade Federation must be stopped! Storm through more than 15 missions over land, sea and space as your freedom fighters rally against the droid armies. Take control of 7 vehicles: the Naboo starfighter, Gian speeder, and new craft like the heavy STAP, Trade Federation gunboat and more.

More than 15 missions: escape from Theed, search & destroy, sabotage, reconnaissance, convoy. Battle against Trade Federation droid starfighters, AATs, destroyer droids, battle droids.
Change vehicles mid-mission through specially designated hangars.";Shooter; - STAR WARS;;igdb_156;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2001 - Star Wars Galactic Battlegrounds Saga (Steam);Star Wars Galactic Battlegrounds Saga;Star Wars Galactic Battlegrounds Saga;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2001 - Star Wars Galactic Battlegrounds Saga (Steam);videos\Star Wars Galactic Battlegrounds Saga (2001).mp4;OK;images\Star Wars Galactic Battlegrounds Saga (2001).webp;2001;Steam;LucasArts;LucasArts;09/11/2001;"Lead the great armies of the Star Wars™ Episode II: Attack of the Clones saga in intense real-time strategy clashes. Enter the fray as the Galactic Empire, Rebel Alliance, Wookies, Trade Federation, Gungans or Royal Naboo to determine the course of the Galactic Civil War. 
 
Expand the battlefield with the Clone Campaigns addon. Choose to play as the breakaway Confederacy of Independent Systems or the Galactic Republic in 14 missions based on characters, vehicles and locations from Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones.";Strategy; - STAR WARS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/356500/53273/ea995b6cce7b8c8588ef54b52bdc1a66f04ba7dd/1750514377/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1456855178;gog_1393141574, steam_356500;steam_356500;gog_1421404646;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003353;humble_starwars_galacticbattlegroundssaga_steam;totalwar_starwars_galacticbattlegroundssaga_steam;d2d_starwars_galacticbattlegroundssaga_steam;test_356500;test_/star-wars-galactic-battlegrounds-saga-free-download/;test_star-wars-galactic-battlegrounds-saga;playfire_star-wars-galactic-battlegrounds-saga;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003353@subscription;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003353@gifting;humble_starwarstmgalacticbattlegroundssaga_bundle_steam;generic_51154259545347498;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2001 - Star Wars Starfighter (Steam);Star Wars Starfighter;Star Wars Starfighter;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2001 - Star Wars Starfighter (Steam);videos\Star Wars Starfighter (2002).mp4;OK;images\Star Wars Starfighter (2002).webp;2001;Steam;LucasArts;Disney Interactive, LucasArts;22/01/2002;"Join three heroic starfighter pilots in harrowing deep space and planetary missions to save the planet of Naboo. Star Wars Starfighter allows you to fly through a unique chapter of the Star Wars universe, piloting 20 realistic and accurately rendered 3D starships amidst a variety of 14 environments set in air and space.

Takeoff on an epic journey that begins on the lush paradise planet of Naboo and continues through the climactic assault on the Droid Control Ship inspired by the motion picture Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace. Take on the roles of rookie Naboo pilot Rhys Dallows, mercenary Vana Sage, and alien pirate Nym as they join together in an unlikely alliance against an unexpected assault on a peaceful planet. As you fly to the aid of Naboo, you'll test your battle skills against more than 50 vehicles, including Trade Federation drop ships, battle tanks, Droid starfighters and never before seen craft such as the deadly Protector, Scarab, and Dagger.";Shooter, Simulator; - STAR WARS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/32350/57343/88ef3341ace516539d9a47a0e84aa363c9773ebe/1750485025/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1462232556;steam_32350;steam_32350;gog_1421404999;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003369;humble_starwars_starfighter_steam;ps2_SLES-50165;ps2_SLUS-20044;test_32350;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003369@subscription;ps2_Star Wars - Starfighter;ps2_13998;generic_51154260330982657;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2002 - Star Wars Jedi Knight II - Jedi Outcast (Steam);Star Wars Jedi Knight II - Jedi Outcast;Star Wars Jedi Knight II - Jedi Outcast;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2002 - Star Wars Jedi Knight II - Jedi Outcast (Steam);videos\STAR WARS Jedi Knight II - Jedi Outcast (2002).mp4;OK;images\STAR WARS Jedi Knight II - Jedi Outcast (2002).webp;2002;Steam;Vicarious Visions, Westlake Interactive, Raven Software;Activision, LucasArts, Aspyr Media, CyberFront;26/03/2002;"In the tradition of the highly acclaimed Star Wars: Jedi Knight series, Star Wars: Jedi Knight 2, Jedi Outcast features rebel agent Kyle Katarn in exhilarating first-person action. Several years have passed since Kyle avenged his father's death and saved the Valley of the Jedi from Jerec and his band of Dark Jedi. Allowing his Force powers to languish for fear of falling to the dark side, Kyle entrusted his lightsaber to Luke Skywalker, vowing never to use it again. But when a new and menacing threat to the galaxy emerges, Kyle knows he must reclaim his past in order to save his future.

Explore breathtaking Star Wars locales such as Cloud City, the Jedi Academy on Yavin 4, Nar Shaddaa, and the smugglers' moon. Multiplayer options include deathmatch, saber-only deathmatch, and team capture the flag.";Adventure, Shooter; - STAR WARS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/6030/57346/8e90bc8405f77a346cfb36c60330a784ee16e028/1750483725/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1462236510;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.8320bb7e-a254-4a71-82e2-d5c29cd6a687, steam_6030;steam_6030;gog_1428935917;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003319;humble_starwars_jediknight2_jedioutcast_steam;psn_CUSA16655_00;psn_CUSA16624_00;ncube_GJKD52;humble_starwars_jediknight2_jedioutcast_aspyr_steam;test_CUSA16624_00;nswitch_0100BB500EACA000;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-1028-20200411074355;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411082911;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411084254;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411094254;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411104254;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411114254;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411124255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411134255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411144255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411154255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411164255;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411174256;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411184256;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411194256;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411204256;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-444-20200411214257;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-453-20200412223222;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-453-20200412230610;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-453-20200412232524;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-453-20200412233527;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-453-20200413001054;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-447-20200413155503;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-447-20200413162205;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-447-20200413164548;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-447-20200413172205;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-439-20200413173540;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-439-20200413183155;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-435-202004131900