2004 - Star Wars Battlefront (Steam);Star Wars Battlefront;Star Wars Battlefront;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2004 - Star Wars Battlefront (Steam);;OK;images\2004 - Star Wars Battlefront (Steam).jpg;2004;Steam;Pandemic Studios;Aspyr Media, LucasArts;17/09/2004;Star Wars: Battlefront is the first in the Star Wars: Battlefront series and is a third/first-person shooter video game based around battles featured in the Star Wars movies. It was developed by Pandemic Studios and LucasArts, and released on September 20, 2004 for Xbox (playable on Xbox 360), PlayStation 2, and PC, the same day as the release of the Star Wars Trilogy (DVD) set. Players can either play Star Wars: Battlefront online, or offline with up to 4 players (on consoles).;Shooter; - STAR WARS;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P2KCjFATtBw;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2005 - Star Wars Battlefront II Classic (Steam);Star Wars Battlefront II Classic;Star Wars Battlefront II Classic;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2005 - Star Wars Battlefront II Classic (Steam);;OK;images\2005 - Star Wars Battlefront II Classic (Steam).jpg;2005;Steam;Pandemic Studios, Savage Entertainment;LucasArts, Activision, Electronic Arts;31/10/2005;"Star Wars: Battlefront II is the sequel to Star Wars: Battlefront. It is a high-selling Star Wars video game following the many adventures of several characters. The two games are very similar, as both revolve around troopers from various factions fighting in different locales. Battlefront II, however, includes elements and missions from Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith, as well as enhanced aspects of gameplay including space combat and the ability to play as Jedi characters or other heroes.

With brand new space combat, playable Jedi characters, and over 16 all new battlefronts, Star Wars Battlefront II gives you more ways than ever before to play the classic Star Wars battles any way you want.";Shooter; - STAR WARS;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ilwPny3tvOE;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2005 - Star Wars Knights Of The Old Republic (Steam);Star Wars Knights Of The Old Republic;Star Wars Knights Of The Old Republic;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2005 - Star Wars Knights Of The Old Republic (Steam);videos\Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic (2003).mp4;OK;images\Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic (2003).webp;2005;Steam;BioWare;Activision, LucasArts, Aspyr Media;19/11/2003;"Choose Your Path! Set 4,000 years before the Galactic Empire, you are the last hope for the Jedi Order and the Republic - can you master the ways of the Force to become their savior? Or will you fall to the dark side and achieve ultimate power? Hero, villain, peacekeeper, or chaos-bringer... you and your party will determine the fate of the galaxy!

Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic is a role-playing video game. Players will be able to create their own characters and be able to choose what gender, appearance, class, skills, attributes, and feats they have throughout the game - no two characters will be the same!";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure; - STAR WARS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/32370/67706/67e888c01cfec7cd9a28aa4658f9cb16dee9a4fd/1750485028/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1470704824;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.7fc09019-f0f1-4500-9db7-224a5bc0f9d6, epic_a673c1ba29b446df909cbdeffa3a53e9, steam_32370;steam_32370;gog_1207666283;xboxone_561072219;xboxone_92932164;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003163;humble_starwars_kotor_steam;humble_starwars_kotor_aspyr_steam;totalwar_starwars_kotor_steam;d2d_starwars_kotor_steam;test_32370;test_/star-wars-knights-of-the-old-republic-free-download/;test_star-wars-knights-of-the-old-republic;playfire_star-wars-knights-of-the-old-republic;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003163@subscription;xboxone_1112934452;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003163@gifting;humble_starwarstm-knightsoftheoldrepublictm_us_switch;test_gfn_32370;fanatical_star-wars-knights-of-the-old-republic;humble_starwarstm_knightsoftheoldrepublictm_bundle_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.7fc09019-f0f1-4500-9db7-224a5bc0f9d6;humble_starwarstmknightsoftheoldrepublic_bundle_steam;epic_d6e92b7f6bee4744b3711700f7c8cb5e;epic_a673c1ba29b446df909cbdeffa3a53e9;generic_51154259850067439;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2005 - Star Wars Republic Commando (Amazon);Star Wars Republic Commando;Star Wars Republic Commando;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2005 - Star Wars Republic Commando (Amazon);videos\STAR WARS Republic Commando (2005).mp4;OK;images\STAR WARS Republic Commando (2005).webp;2005;Amazon;LucasArts;Activision, Electronic Arts, LucasArts, Aspyr Media;17/02/2005;"Chaos has erupted throughout the galaxy. As a leader of an elite squad of Republic Commandos, your mission is to infiltrate, dominate, and ultimately, annihalate the enemy. Your squad will follow your orders and your lead, working together as a team-instinctively, intelligently, instantly. You are their leader. They are your weapon.

Star Wars: Republic Commando is a tactical first-person shooter video game, set in the Star Wars universe. It was developed by LucasArts using the Unreal Engine, and published for the Xbox and Microsoft Windows in 2005. The game features both single-player and multiplayer game modes. In the story, set in the Star Wars Legends expanded universe, players assume the role of RC-1138 (""Boss""), an elite clone trooper, known as ""clone commando"", and the leader of the special ops unit Delta Squad, consisting of three fellow clone commandos with distinctive personalities and character traits: RC-1262 (""Scorch""), RC-1140 (""Fixer""), and RC-1207 (""Sev""). The story follows Delta Squad as they complete increasingly difficult missions throughout the Clone Wars and learn to bond as a team.

Republic Commando received generally favorable reviews at release. Many critics praised the story and combat, but criticized the short length and average multiplayer. In the years since its release, it has come to be considered one of the best Star Wars games ever made, and has gained a cult following.

An enhanced port of the game by Aspyr is set to release for the Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4 on April 6, 2021. As reported by Jordan Ramée of GameSpot, ""Handled by Aspyr Media, Star Wars: Republic Commando Remastered brings the original 2005 Xbox and PC game to PS4 and Switch with enhanced HD graphics and modernized controls, though the multiplayer is absent. Otherwise, it's the same game. And though the flaws in its gameplay are only more noticeable now 16 years later, this remaster manages to still deliver a compelling story of four specialized commandos engaging in a variety of combat missions across the Clone Wars."".";Adventure, Shooter, Tactical; - STAR WARS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/6000/67875/c3380099438a7479832bc44dd83307b70b3e762a/1750483700/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1476312642;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.334f1d96-0646-4e9b-9613-8747be0c7505;steam_6000;gog_1421405135;xboxone_398211151;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003315;humble_starwars_republiccommando_steam;test_6000;test_/star-wars-republic-commando-free-download/;test_star-wars-republic-commando;playfire_star-wars-republic-commando;xboxone_1112934459;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003315@subscription;psn_CUSA19234_00;psn_CUSA19302_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003315@gifting;xboxone_88641736;psn_CUSA26747_00;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.334f1d96-0646-4e9b-9613-8747be0c7505;test_029ae317eee28ae6bbb9fe3cdeedce35e4f0a6d2;test_65c0ac147cf30e81a3848803924e6af6b64e4409;test_7ad60003a81d2b5cf7426f4bb09cbb86a5fa69af;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.334f1d96-0646-4e9b-9613-8747be0c7505;psn_CUSA26748_00;humble_starwarstmrepubliccommando_bundle_steam;generic_51154260117679564;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2006 - Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic II - The Sith Lords (Steam);Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic II - The Sith Lords;Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic II - The Sith Lords;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ - STAR WARS\2006 - Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic II - The Sith Lords (Steam);videos\Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic II - The Sith Lords (2004).mp4;OK;images\Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic II - The Sith Lords (2004).webp;2006;Steam;Obsidian Entertainment;Activision, LucasArts, Aspyr Media;08/02/2005;Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords is a sequel to the blockbuster RPG Star Wars Knights of the Old Republic. Players continue to enjoy the title's emotionally compelling and story-driven theme, additions to features such as new characters, classes, locations and force powers as well as a deeper look into the founding lore.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS); - STAR WARS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/208580/57520/8f45165566ab17d6d63930cb44ed33fe36d7cd8f/1750493199/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1461792094;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.bc8c2cf6-ded7-42fb-91d9-d0865af9e57a, epic_9d79db3ce278424f933be491637c9a57, steam_208580;steam_208580;gog_1421404581;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003162;xboxone_321401884;humble_starwars_kotor2_thesithlords_steam;humble_starwars_kotor2_thesithlords_aspyr_steam;totalwar_starwars_kotor2_thesithlords_steam;d2d_starwars_kotor2_thesithlords_steam;test_208580;test_/star-wars-knights-of-the-old-republic-2-the-sith-lords-free-download/;xboxone_1112934458;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003162@subscription;fanatical_star-wars-knights-of-the-old-republic-ii-the-sith-lords;humble_starwarstmknightsoftheoldrepublictmii_thesithlordstm_bundle_steam;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.bc8c2cf6-ded7-42fb-91d9-d0865af9e57a;humble_starwarstm_knightsoftheoldrepublicii_thesithlords_bundle_steam;epic_9d79db3ce278424f933be491637c9a57;epic_9fc24aaba6a6454c977a3fc17427e5f5;generic_511542