A Plague Tale Requiem;A Plague Tale Requiem;A Plague Tale Requiem;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\A PLAGUE TALE\A Plague Tale Requiem;;OK;images\A Plague Tale Requiem.jpg;;Warez;Asobo Studio;Focus Entertainment;18/10/2022;A Plague Tale: Requiem is an action-adventure game similar to its predecessor. The player assumes control of Amicia and must face against both soldiers from the French Inquisition and hordes of rats that are spreading the black plague. The gameplay is largely similar to the first game, though the combat system is significantly expanded. The game features a progression system in which the player will be awarded additional skills and abilities. Stealth players will unlock skills that allow them to sneak around more efficiently, while those who prefer a more lethal approach will unlock additional combat skills. Locations are also larger, giving players additional options to progress.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;A PLAGUE TALE;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K6trXEz1YvM;igdb_152242;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2018 - Age of Empires Definitive Edition;Age of Empires Definitive Edition;Age of Empires Definitive Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\AGE OF EMPIRE\2018 - Age of Empires Definitive Edition;;OK;images\2018 - Age of Empires Definitive Edition.jpg;2018;Warez;Tantalus Media, Forgotten Empires LLC;Microsoft Studios;20/02/2018;Age of Empires, the pivotal RTS that launched a 20-year legacy returns in definitive form for Windows 10 PCs. Bringing together all of the officially released content with modernized gameplay, all-new visuals and a host of other new features, Age of Empires: Definitive Edition is the complete RTS package. Engage in over 40 hours of updated campaign content with new narration and pacing, jump online in up to 8-player battles with new competitive features and modes, experience 4K HD visuals with overhauled animations, get creative with the scenario builder and share your creations with easy mod support. There’s never been a better time to jump in to Age of Empires. Welcome back to history.;Real Time Strategy (RTS), Simulator, Strategy, Adventure;AGE OF EMPIRE;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g5GwKbk2ihA;igdb_37059;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2019 - Age of Empires II Definitive Edition;Age of Empires II Definitive Edition;Age of Empires II Definitive Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\AGE OF EMPIRE\2019 - Age of Empires II Definitive Edition;;OK;images\2019 - Age of Empires II Definitive Edition.jpg;2019;Warez;World's Edge;Xbox Game Studios;14/11/2019;Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition celebrates the 20th anniversary of one of the most popular strategy games ever with stunning 4K Ultra HD graphics, a new and fully remastered soundtrack, and brand-new content, “The Last Khans” with 3 new campaigns and 4 new civilizations.;Real Time Strategy (RTS), Strategy;AGE OF EMPIRE;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZOgBVR21pWg;igdb_55056;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
