2009 - Anno 1404 Gold Edition;Anno 1404 Gold Edition;Anno 1404 Gold Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ANNO\2009 - Anno 1404 Gold Edition;;OK;images\2009 - Anno 1404 Gold Edition.jpg;2009;Warez;Blue Byte;Ubisoft Entertainment;08/12/2010;For the first time have the critically acclaimed and best selling strategy game Anno 1404 and its tremendous add-on Anno 1404 Venice in only one pack. Anno 1404 and its add-on are an award winning combination of construction, economy, discovery, diplomacy & combat. Raise monumental metropolis and develop an idealized historical empire in the Orient and the Venice of the Renaissance. The game also offers multiplayer support, allowing you to share this experience with your friends.;Simulator, Strategy;ANNO;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lyhY1E4pJbY;igdb_27913;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2011 - Anno 2070;Anno 2070;Anno 2070;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ANNO\2011 - Anno 2070;;OK;images\2011 - Anno 2070.jpg;2011;Warez;Related Designs, Blue Byte;Ubisoft Entertainment;17/11/2011;Anno 2070 is a city-building and economic simulation game, with real-time strategy elements. It is the 5th game of the Anno series. It was released on 17 November 2011, and was co-developed by the German studios Related Designs and Ubisoft Blue Byte, and published by Ubisoft. Anno 2070 requires Uplay to operate.;Real Time Strategy (RTS), Simulator, Strategy;ANNO;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6ONqSVh_EfM;igdb_2959;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2015 - Anno 2205;Anno 2205;Anno 2205;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ANNO\2015 - Anno 2205;;OK;images\2015 - Anno 2205.jpg;2015;Warez;Blue Byte;Ubisoft Entertainment;02/11/2015;"In Anno 2205, you join humankind‘s next step into the future with the promise to build a better tomorrow. You conquer Earth, establishing rich, bustling cities and grand industrial complexes, but to secure the prosperity of your people, you must travel into space.

A scientific breakthrough in fusion energy promises to revolutionise all aspects of society. The necessary isotope, helium-3, can only be found in harvestable quantities on the Moon. Venture into space and settle on the Moon in the thrilling race for resource and power.

Anno’s masterful economic gameplay is back and taking strategic city-building simulation to new heights, launching into space!";Real Time Strategy (RTS), Simulator, Strategy;ANNO;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ur4yDtPHtfk;igdb_11205;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2019 - Anno 1800 Deluxe Edition;Anno 1800 Deluxe Edition;Anno 1800 Deluxe Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ANNO\2019 - Anno 1800 Deluxe Edition;;OK;images\2019 - Anno 1800 Deluxe Edition.jpg;2019;Warez;Ubisoft Blue Byte;Ubisoft Entertainment;16/04/2019;"Anno 1800: Deluxe Edition includes:

