2010 - Assassin's Creed Brotherhood (Uplay);Assassin's Creed Brotherhood;Assassin's Creed Brotherhood;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2010 - Assassin's Creed Brotherhood (Uplay);;OK;images\2010 - Assassins Creed Brotherhood (Uplay).jpg;2010;Uplay;Ubisoft Montreal;Ubisoft Entertainment;16/11/2010;"Live and breathe as Ezio, a legendary Master Assassin, in his enduring struggle against the powerful Templar Order. He must journey into Italy’s greatest city, Rome, center of power, greed and corruption to strike at the heart of the enemy.
Defeating the corrupt tyrants entrenched there will require not only strength, but leadership, as Ezio commands an entire Brotherhood who will rally to his side. Only by working together can the Assassins defeat their mortal enemies.
And for the first time, introducing a never-before-seen multiplayer layer that allows you to choose from a wide range of unique characters, each with their own signature weapons and assassination techniques, and match your skills against other players from around the world.
It’s time to join the Brotherhood.";Puzzle, Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zzNs4-kRLaE;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2011 - Assassin's Creed Revelations;Assassin's Creed Revelations;Assassin's Creed Revelations;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2011 - Assassin's Creed Revelations;;OK;images\2011 - Assassins Creed Revelations.jpg;2011;Warez;Ubisoft Montreal;Ubisoft Entertainment;14/11/2011;"Assassin's Creed Revelations presents the most immersive experience available in the series to date and the culmination of Ezio's adventure. In Assassin's Creed Revelations, master assassin Ezio Auditore walks in the footsteps of his legendary mentor, Altair, on a journey of discovery and revelation. It is a perilous path - one that will take Ezio to Constantinople, the heart of the Ottoman Empire, where a growing army of Templars threatens to destabilize the region.

In addition to Ezio's award-winning story, the acclaimed online multiplayer experience from Assassin's Creed Brotherhood returns; refined and expanded, with more modes, more maps and more characters that allow players to test their assassin skills against others from around the world. The latest chapter in the Assassin's Creed saga also includes revolutionary gameplay, allowing players to manipulate the construct of Desmond's memories and the Animus to decipher the mysteries of his past and gain insight into the future.";Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4K39UWxdm0U;igdb_537;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
