2012 - Assassin's Creed Liberation HD (Uplay);Assassin's Creed Liberation HD;Assassin's Creed Liberation HD;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2012 - Assassin's Creed Liberation HD (Uplay);;OK;images\2012 - Assassins Creed Liberation HD (Uplay).jpg;2012;Uplay;Ubisoft Sofia;Ubisoft Entertainment;15/01/2014;"Assassin’s Creed: Liberation HD is an action‑adventure stealth game set in 18th‑century New Orleans and surrounding territories, starring Aveline de Grandpré as she navigates colonial politics, slavery, and hidden conspiracies. Play through single‑player missions that blend stealth, parkour, and assassinations while upgrading gear and abilities.
This HD re-release updates visuals, audio, AI, and facial animations to align with Assassin’s Creed III, adds extra single‑player missions, and removes Vita‑specific touch episodes and multiplayer features.
On July 11, 2022, Assassin's Creed: Liberation HD was removed from purchase on Steam. Furthermore, it was announced that all DLC and online features would subsequently be inaccessible to players after September 1, 2022.";Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E-qVn6WlWyg;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2013 - Assassin's Creed IV Black Flag;Assassin's Creed IV Black Flag;Assassin's Creed IV Black Flag;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2013 - Assassin's Creed IV Black Flag;;OK;images\2013 - Assassins Creed IV Black Flag.jpg;2013;Warez;Ubisoft Montreal;Ubisoft Entertainment;29/10/2013;Assassin’s Creed IV Black Flag begins in 1715, when pirates established a lawless republic in the Caribbean and ruled the land and seas. These outlaws paralyzed navies, halted international trade, and plundered vast fortunes. They threatened the power structures that ruled Europe, inspired the imaginations of millions, and left a legacy that still endures.;Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Z9wnzlw9hA;igdb_1970;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2014 - Assassin's Creed Freedom Cry;Assassin's Creed Freedom Cry;Assassin's Creed Freedom Cry;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2014 - Assassin's Creed Freedom Cry;;OK;images\2014 - Assassins Creed Freedom Cry.jpg;2014;Warez;Ubisoft Québec, Ubisoft Montreal;;17/12/2013;Born a slave, Adewale found freedom as a pirate aboard Edward Kenway’s ship, the Jackdaw. 15 years later, Adewale has become a trained Assassin who finds himself shipwrecked in Saint-Domingue without weapons or crew. He now has to acquire a ship and gather his own crew to free the slaves and avenge them. Over 3 hours of new single-player gameplay!;Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Gu3ifv-7Ck;igdb_3775;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2014 - Assassin's Creed Rogue;Assassin's Creed Rogue;Assassin's Creed Rogue;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2014 - Assassin's Creed Rogue;;OK;images\2014 - Assassins Creed Rogue.jpg;2014;Warez;Ubisoft Sofia;Ubisoft Entertainment;11/11/2014;Assassin's Creed Rogue is a 2014 action-adventure video game developed by Ubisoft Sofia and published by Ubisoft. It is the seventh major installment in the Assassin's Creed series, and is set between 2012's Assassin's Creed III and 2013's Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag. It also has ties to Assassin's Creed Unity, which was released on the same day as Rogue. It is the last Assassin's Creed game to be developed for the seventh generation of consoles, being released for PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 in November 2014 and for Windows in March 2015.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HaEp7s7ws-A;igdb_7570;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2014 - Assassin's Creed Unity (Uplay);Assassin's Creed Unity;Assassin's Creed Unity;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2014 - Assassin's Creed Unity (Uplay);;OK;images\2014 - Assassins Creed Unity (Uplay).jpg;2014;Uplay;Ubisoft Montreal;Ubisoft Entertainment;11/11/2014;"Assassin’s Creed Unity is an action-adventure game set in Paris during the French Revolution. The player controls Arno Dorian, an Assassin who seeks to uncover the forces behind the political unrest. The game introduces new weapons, including the Phantom Blade, a modified Hidden Blade with ranged capabilities.
Gameplay emphasizes stealth, parkour, and close combat, featuring updated free-running mechanics and a revised fighting system. The open-world setting recreates 18th-century Paris and includes historical events such as the storming of the Bastille and the execution of King Louis XVI. Unity also includes a cooperative multiplayer mode supporting up to four players.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lrq37TNN0FU;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2015 - Assassin's Creed Chronicles China (Uplay);Assassin's Creed Chronicles China;Assassin's Creed Chronicles China;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2015 - Assassin's Creed Chronicles China (Uplay);;OK;images\2015 - Assassins Creed Chronicles China (Uplay).jpg;2015;Uplay;Climax Studios;Ubisoft Entertainment;21/04/2015;"Chronicles: China takes place after the film Assassin's Creed: Embers. It features the Chinese assassin Shao Jun in 1526. After being trained by legendary Italian assassin Ezio Auditore da Firenze, Shao Jun returns to her homeland to exact vengeance against the Templar group Eight Tigers, who wiped out the Chinese brotherhood. Shao Jun's quest took her through Macau, Nan'an, the Forbidden City and the Great Wall, as she killed the Tigers one by one and finally assassinating the final target, Zhang Yong. Years later, Shao Jun, who became an Assassin Mentor and had rebuilt the brotherhood, plotted the assassination of Jiajing Emperor by sending him an elixir of life.

Chronicles: China was originally announced in September 2014 as part of the season pass for Assassin's Creed Unity. It was released on April 21, 2015, in North America and April 22, 2015, in other territories, on Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One. Chronicles: China is the first title in the franchise to utilize Epic Games' Unreal Engine 3.";Platform, Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3pwy6-Sj5CA;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2015 - Assassin's Creed Syndicate;Assassin's Creed Syndicate;Assassin's Creed Syndicate;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2015 - Assassin's Creed Syndicate;;OK;images\2015 - Assassins Creed Syndicate.jpg;2015;Warez;Ubisoft Québec;Ubisoft Entertainment;23/10/2015;"London, 1868. The Industrial Revolution unleashes an incredible age of invention, transforming the lives of millions with technologies once thought impossible. Opportunities created during this period have people rushing to London to engage in this new world, a world no longer controlled by kings, emperors, politicians, or religion, but by a new common denominator: money.

Not everyone is able to enjoy the benefits of this boom, however. Despite fueling the engine of the British Empire, workers’ lives are little more than legalized slavery while the top few percent profit from their labor. Living poor and dying young, the lower class unite in protest as a new kind of family, gangs, who turn to a life in the underworld in their struggle to survive. A struggle, until watchful Assassins come to their side and re-ignite an age-old conflict involving London’s leaders that will echo throughout modern history, from the underground up.

Introducing Jacob Frye, who with the help of his twin sister Evie, will change the fate of millions in Assassin’s Creed Syndicate. Rise to rally and lead the underworld to break the corrupt stranglehold on London in a visceral adventure filled with action, intrigue, and brutal combat.";Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IoUOS1DDTI4;igdb_8263;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2016 - Assassin's Creed Chronicles India (Uplay);Assassin's Creed Chronicles India;Assassin's Creed Chronicles India;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2016 - Assassin's Creed Chronicles India (Uplay);;OK;images\2016 - Assassins Creed Chronicles India (Uplay).jpg;2016;Uplay;Climax Studios;Ubisoft Entertainment;12/01/2016;Chronicles: India will feature Indian assassin Arbaaz Mir in 1841, while the Sikh Empire was at war with the East India Company. When a Master Templar arrives with a mysterious item that used to belong to the Assassin Order, Mir must discover why he has come, steal back the item, and protect his friends and his lover.;Platform, Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2hTDuTpvTqs;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2016 - Assassin's Creed Chronicles Russia (Uplay);Assassin's Creed Chronicles Russia;Assassin's Creed Chronicles Russia;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2016 - Assassin's Creed Chronicles Russia (Uplay);;OK;images\2016 - Assassins Creed Chronicles Russia (Uplay).jpg;2016;Uplay;Climax Studios;Ubisoft Entertainment;09/02/2016;Chronicles: Russia will feature the Russian assassin Nikolai Orelov in 1918, during the aftermath of the October Revolution. Orelov wants to leave with his family, but is required to perform one last mission for the Assassin Order: infiltrate the house where the Tsar's family is being held by the Bolsheviks, and steal an artifact that has been fought over by Assassins and Templars for centuries. Along the way, he witnesses the massacre of the Tsar Nicholas II's children, but manages to save the princess, Anastasia. He must escape the Templars while protecting the artifact and Anastasia;Platform, Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=idosIQPtXdw;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2017 - Assassin's Creed Origins (Uplay);Assassin's Creed Origins;Assassin's Creed Origins;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2017 - Assassin's Creed Origins (Uplay);;OK;images\2017 - Assassins Creed Origins (Uplay).jpg;2017;Uplay;Ubisoft Montreal;Ubisoft Entertainment;26/10/2017;"Assassin’s Creed Origins is an action-adventure game set in ancient Egypt at the end of the Ptolemaic era. The story follows Bayek, a Medjay tasked with protecting the people, as personal tragedy draws him into a wider conflict that leads to the origins of the Assassin Brotherhood.

The game features a large open-world recreation of Egypt, including cities, deserts, and the Nile, with an increased emphasis on exploration. Gameplay combines stealth, melee and ranged combat, and role-playing elements such as character leveling, skill trees, and gear progression.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gczocLl14_U;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2018 - Assassin's Creed, Odyssey (Epic Games Store,Uplay);Assassin's Creed, Odyssey;Assassin's Creed, Odyssey;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\ASSASIN'S CREED\2018 - Assassin's Creed, Odyssey (Epic Games Store,Uplay);videos\Assassins Creed Odyssey (2018).mp4;OK;images\Assassins Creed Odyssey (2018).webp;2018;Epic Games Store, Uplay;Ubisoft Québec;Ubisoft Entertainment;05/10/2018;Write your own epic odyssey and become a legendary Spartan hero in Assassin's Creed Odyssey, an inspiring adventure where you must forge your destiny and define your own path in a world on the brink of tearing itself apart. Influence how history unfolds as you experience a rich and ever-changing world shaped by your decisions.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;ASSASIN'S CREED;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/812140/188292/a8c55a69aa88fdeafbbeeff69b4c525d6d2bd091/1750586000/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1538496199;epic_Clary;xboxone_964818375;steam_812140;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003014;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003012;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003016;psn_NPWR13822_00;psn_CUSA09303_00;uplay_7d3950e6-41ce-43e3-976b-f893b246c31e;psn_CUSA12042_00;psn_CUSA09311_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003029;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003036;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003024;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003032;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003030;psn_CUSA12041_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003027;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003018;psn_CUSA09344_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003037;epic_Clary;uplay_5059;uplay_5404;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003013;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003025;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003034;psvita_CUSA09311_00;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003042;steam_857152;steam_857151;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003028;test_CUSA09303_00;humble_assassinscreed_odyssey_deluxe_emea_uplay;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003048;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003019;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003044;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0003038;test_CUSA09311_00;humble_assassinscreed_odyssey_gold_na_uplay;humble_assassinscreed_odyssey_standard_na_uplay;humble_assassinscreed_odyssey_gold_emea_uplay;humble_assassinscr