Bridge Constructor Studio;Bridge Constructor Studio;Bridge Constructor Studio;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\BRIDGE CONSTRUCTOR\Bridge Constructor Studio;;OK;images\Bridge Constructor Studio.jpg;;Warez;ClockStone Studios;Headup Games;12/12/2024;"Test your construction expertise with dozens of distinct bridge-building puzzles across varied biomes. Seven different vehicles and multiple construction materials (wood, steel, cables, concrete pillars, and roadways) ensure each puzzle is a fresh and varied challenge.

With no budget restrictions or material limits, you are free to experiment and design without constraints. For an extra challenge, earn a special award by keeping costs within a set budget while ensuring your bridge holds up under pressure!

Design and play your very own bridge-building scenarios! Choose from five biomes, seven vehicles, and a variety of obstacles and checkpoints to design your own challenges. Up to 40 custom levels can be saved per player profile.

Mixed Reality (Quest 3 Exclusive): View your creations in the real world with Mixed Reality! Seamlessly switch between VR and Passthrough modes to experience the game in a whole new way.";Puzzle, Simulator, Strategy, Indie;BRIDGE CONSTRUCTOR;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5vdKOOBaee8;igdb_325559;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
