Homeworld Deserts of Kharak (Epic Games Store);Homeworld Deserts of Kharak;Homeworld Deserts of Kharak;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\HOMEWORLD\Homeworld Deserts of Kharak (Epic Games Store);videos\Homeworld Deserts of Kharak (2016).mp4;OK;images\Homeworld Deserts of Kharak (2016).webp;;Epic Games Store;Blackbird Interactive;Gearbox Software;20/01/2016;"Before you can find your Homeworld, you must first unlock the secrets of the desert.

Blackbird Interactive and Gearbox Software invite you to visit the deserts of Kharak in this new Homeworld story, where danger lurks behind every dune. Homeworld: Deserts of Kharak is set for release on January 20th on Windows PC.

The planet is dying, but deep in the southern sands of Kharak, an anomaly has been discovered. Could Kharak’s salvation lie in the desert? Led by chief science officer Rachel S’jet, the Coalition of the Northern Kiithid sends an expedition deep within enemy-controlled territory to investigate the finding, which could forever alter the fate of humanity.";Strategy;HOMEWORLD;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/281610/51838/c8a085ec4255c5c843df150fd1ff0cc23f349d31/1750489036/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1454954500;epic_c9b51edbca4d496cb39c6871f510620b;steam_281610;gog_2115713947;humble_homeworld_desertsofkharak_steam;discord_cdb833a9-c87e-4450-bdc7-c92e3a6db4c5;test_/homeworld-deserts-of-kharak-free-download/;test_homeworld-deserts-of-kharak;playfire_homeworld-deserts-of-kharak;humble_homeworld_desertsofkharak_bundle_steam;epic_c9b51edbca4d496cb39c6871f510620b;generic_51152976973420722;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Homeworld Remastered Collection (Epic Games Store);Homeworld Remastered Collection;Homeworld Remastered Collection;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\HOMEWORLD\Homeworld Remastered Collection (Epic Games Store);videos\Homeworld Remastered Collection (2015).mp4;OK;images\Homeworld Remastered Collection (2015).webp;;Epic Games Store;Gearbox Software;Gearbox Publishing;25/02/2015;"Homeworld Remastered Collection updates and introduces the landmark space strategy games to modern audiences. The collection includes Homeworld and Homeworld 2, painstakingly remastered by Gearbox in cooperation with key members of the original development team and members of the series’ passionate fan community. As a free bonus, this collection also includes the original versions of Homeworld and Homeworld 2 with compatibility updates, preserving the purest form of the original releases. Anyone who purchases Homeworld Remastered Collection will also receive free access to the Homeworld Remastered Steam Multiplayer Beta when the collection releases on February 25, 2015. 
 
The Homeworld series has a long legacy and is regarded by many as one of the best strategy series of all time. Following its release in 1999 by publisher Sierra and developer Relic Entertainment, Homeworld received several Game of the Year awards and redefined the RTS genre. Its sequel, Homeworld 2, launched in 2003, and was similarly praised by critics for its innovative controls and changes to multiplayer. Brian Martel, Gearbox Software's Chief Creative Officer, has great love and respect for Relic's brilliant, fun and innovative franchise and personally spearheaded Gearbox Software’s acquisition of Homeworld from THQ in 2013.";Strategy;HOMEWORLD;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/244160/51703/7bdaf4627680302109cf4f33ecafd7a7592137f7/1751248583/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1454704943;epic_dcfccf8d965a4f2281dddf9fead042de;steam_244160;gog_2114871440;humble_homeworld_remasteredcollection_steam;humble_homeworld_remasteredcollection_aspyr_steam;itch_51ed07b9b90a90864bbbf229c01d35bb8d87e9c16270381f1a2d5a79;origin_93604d4d32d4f065a5be084d80a1031f9745ec5c;origin_fb5b7af54f8d03cf095a5a809a8f9b97aaa841d4defb48bd8913037677d4d144;test_244160;test_/homeworld-remastered-collection-free-download/;fanatical_homeworld-remastered-collection;humble_homeworldremasteredcollection_bundle_steam;epic_dcfccf8d965a4f2281dddf9fead042de;generic_51152977037111735;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
