1989 - Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade (Amazon);Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade;Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\INDIANA JONES\1989 - Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade (Amazon);;OK;images\Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade (1991).webp;1989;Amazon;Taito, Software Creations;;31/12/1991;Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade is a video game for the NES based on the 1989 action and adventure movie of the same name. In the game, the player controls protagonist Indiana Jones, going through levels taken directly from the film, albeit with a shortened and simplified plot.;Adventure;INDIANA JONES;;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.7205721a-e8b0-4c7b-8bb2-ff22c4362baf;sms_CAWTHSI2OK;sms_SW67Y9W7UO;sms_KZ7WG2FLSI;segag_1529841982105;segag_195819773717251;nes_Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade;segag_Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade;sms_Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade;ngameboy_Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade;egg_indy3-vga;gameuk_indy3-vga;amiga_indy3-vga;amiga_indy3-fm;beamdog_a890ab1d-78a4-4f83-9ae7-0249e8de0843;minecraft_a890ab1d-78a4-4f83-9ae7-0249e8de0843;amiga_indy3-vga-it;amiga_indy3-steam-win;amiga_indy3-ega;amiga_indy3-ega-amiga;amiga_indy3-ega-st;amiga_indy3-ega-mac;nes_Indiana_jones_and_the_last_crusade;test_32310;amiga_indy3-ega-amiga-fr;amiga_indy3-vga-de;amiga_indy3-steam;amiga_indy3-fm-1;c64_1529841982105;nes_25064931035549615;nes_200519448284389265;ngameboy_783279094860155;test_195819639496659;jaguar_1529824156313;amiga_indy3-ega-amiga-de;ngameboy_Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade GB;jaguar_1529841982105;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.7205721a-e8b0-4c7b-8bb2-ff22c4362baf;test_924c233fec2ca44d0a4cecfcb42b862d63d5b34f;sms_Indiana Jones & The Last Crusade;nes_Indiana Jones & the Last Crusade;amiga_indy3-fm-2;amiga_indy3-vga-2;amiga_indy3-ega-st-1;amiga_indy3-vga-3;amiga_indy3-vga-it-1;twitch_amzn1.adg.product.7205721a-e8b0-4c7b-8bb2-ff22c4362baf;jaguar_25666190313138057595;test_9f3becf67f450089c930237d9da08d1d851e216a;test_21543d3fa1d8b9f7a9ed9eafa87bd98e1290b3f5;generic_51973334834937079
1992 - Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis (Amazon);Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis;Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\INDIANA JONES\1992 - Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis (Amazon);videos\Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis (1992).mp4;OK;images\Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis (1992).webp;1992;Amazon;LucasArts;Disney Interactive, U.S. Gold, LucasArts;01/06/1992;"A point-and-click adventure game by LucasArts originally released in 1992. Almost a year later, it was reissued on CD-ROM as an enhanced ""talkie"" edition with full voice acting and digitized sound effects. In 2009, this version was also released as an unlockable extra of the Wii action game Indiana Jones and the Staff of Kings, and as a digitally distributed Steam title. The seventh game to use the script language SCUMM, Fate of Atlantis has the player explore environments and interact with objects and characters by using commands constructed with predetermined verbs. It features three unique paths to select, influencing story development, gameplay and puzzles.";Adventure, Puzzle, Point-and-click;INDIANA JONES;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/6010/96899/c9985a75cec4da9dd35d501d7c11b9c22cce70d1/1751245948/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1491238597;amazon_88612dcd-7348-4588-89eb-ef41d873de11;steam_6010;gog_1207666293;humble_indianajones_andthefateofatlantis_trove;discord_492162663976140810;egg_atlantis;gameuk_atlantis;amiga_atlantis;test_184;amiga_atlantis-steam;amiga_atlantis-1;amiga_atlantis-fm;amiga_atlantis-it;amiga_atlantis-mac;amiga_atlantis-amiga;test_6010;amiga_atlantis-fm-1;c64_24477471477653;test_a20ca5dfadfea28f540ce1321866362f029ea18e;test_3133116349144521;test_0a5a77ea5f14e5da261a2c880ac7f73e70cfdedc;jaguar_1529840668565;amiga_atlantis-steam-win;amazon_88612dcd-7348-4588-89eb-ef41d873de11;twitch_88612dcd-7348-4588-89eb-ef41d873de11;test_2c667a1f84356a028813ff15fff65ba54c96fcd3;test_7fa2b22f054b1486a5ba0d959f837caa551738e2;amiga_atlantis-de;dotemu_20843c68c446f43c689c46460a1ef898bf54c741;amiga_atlantis-fr;test_17bd7631100c0c7b09f8f26ce44032209f8112f6;jaguar_24477471477653;amiga_atlantis-amiga-2;amiga_atlantis-11;amiga_atlantis-9;amiga_atlantis-mac-1;amiga_atlantis-5;amiga_atlantis-fm-4;amiga_atlantis-steam-1;amiga_atlantis-fm-2;amiga_atlantis-steam-2;amiga_atlantis-8;amiga_atlantis-amiga-1;amiga_atlantis-fm-3;amiga_atlantis-7;amiga_atlantis-amiga-3;amiga_atlantis-amiga-4;amiga_atlantis-10;amiga_atlantis-6;amiga_atlantis-2;amiga_atlantis-4
1999 - Indiana Jones and the Infernal Machine;Indiana Jones and the Infernal Machine;Indiana Jones and the Infernal Machine;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\INDIANA JONES\1999 - Indiana Jones and the Infernal Machine;;OK;images\1999 - Indiana Jones and the Infernal Machine.jpg;1999;Warez;LucasArts;LucasArts, Gradiente;23/11/1999;"1947. The Nazis have been crushed, the Cold War has begun and Soviet agents are sniffing around the ruins of the fabled Tower of Babel. What are they up to? The CIA wants renowned archaeologist and adventurer Dr. Henry ""Indiana"" Jones, Jr. to find out. Grab your whip and fedora and join Indy in a globe-spanning race to unearth the mysterious ""Infernal Machine.""";Fighting, Adventure;INDIANA JONES;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IJ7Ba4Bz0II;igdb_188;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2003 - Indiana Jones and the Emperor’s Tomb;Indiana Jones and the Emperor’s Tomb;Indiana Jones and the Emperor’s Tomb;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\INDIANA JONES\2003 - Indiana Jones and the Emperor’s Tomb;;OK;images\2003 - Indiana Jones and the Emperors Tomb.jpg;2003;Warez;TransGaming Inc., The Collective;LucasArts, Aspyr Media;24/02/2003;"As Indiana Jones, you’ll travel to 1935 China to prevent a powerful artifact from falling into evil hands. This globe-spanning adventure pits you against evil Nazis and the Asian underworld. It’ll take more than just a trusty whip and pistol to avoid the perils of the Emperor’s Tomb.

Indy's latest adventure plays out in dramatic fashion thanks to new gameplay features such as brawling combat. This time, in addition to using his trademark whip and pistol, Indy can engage in fierce hand-to-hand combat against foes, many of whom are well-versed in martial arts. Improvised weapons such as shovels, chairs and table legs also can be used to fend off adversaries. The result is a more immersive and more Indy-like gameplay experience, set amidst spine-tingling movie-like action sequences, such as a rickshaw chase in Hong Kong and a spectacular battle atop moving gondolas in the South China Sea area.";Adventure;INDIANA JONES;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BPugG4Bq-S8;igdb_187;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2008 - LEGO Indiana Jones, The Original Adventures (Amazon);LEGO Indiana Jones, The Original Adventures;LEGO Indiana Jones, The Original Adventures;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\INDIANA JONES\2008 - LEGO Indiana Jones, The Original Adventures (Amazon);videos\LEGO Indiana Jones The Original Adventures (2008).mp4;OK;images\LEGO Indiana Jones The Original Adventures (2008).webp;2008;Amazon;Traveller's Tales, Robosoft Technologies;LucasArts, Feral Interactive;02/06/2008;Build, Battle and Brawl your way out of trouble! Play through all three classic Indiana Jones movies and relive your favorite Indy adventures in the tongue-in-cheek worlds of LEGO. Explore and Discover - Battle enemies, solve puzzles, and seek out the world's greatest treasures.;Adventure, Platform, Puzzle;INDIANA JONES;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/32330/93061/3d4ad0c0c1d23ab825602f6d0d626a73183a643c/1750485022/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1488848164;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.8a584db6-f8e5-4bfa-87a8-256a9d3506c4;steam_32330;gog_1194227151;xboxone_497646326;ps2_SLUS-21759;psp_PVDK4TI4QD;psp_H66XWO2ZDB;psp_AUE7JHESDQ;psp_0SWZ37BN04;nds_YLJEN0;ps2_20534;ps2_SLES-55133;nwii_RLIE64;psp_ULES-01086;nds_YLJPN0;nds_LEGO Indiana Jones - The Original Adventures;psx_LEGO Indiana Jones: The Original Adventures;psp_ULUS-10365;psp_LEGO Indiana Jones - The Original Adventures;psn_BLUS30141_00;ps2_LEGO Indiana Jones - The Original Adventures;psp_LEGO Indiana Jones The Original Adventures [USA];test_/lego-indiana-jones-the-original-adventures-free-download/;nwii_LEGO Indiana Jones: The Original Adventures;xboxone_1279330271;psp_LEGO Indiana Jones: The Original Adventures;amazon_amzn1.adg.product.8a584db6-f8e5-4bfa-87a8-256a9d3506c4;humble_legorindianajones_theoriginaladventures_bundle_steam;test_3e116d2a22e7462913f36186b0a639e837816056;nwii_RLIP64;nwii_LEGO Indiana Jones - The Original Adventures;generic_51153209670444152;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2010 - LEGO Indiana Jones 2, The Adventure Continues;LEGO Indiana Jones 2, The Adventure Continues;LEGO Indiana Jones 2, The Adventure Continues;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\INDIANA JONES\2010 - LEGO Indiana Jones 2, The Adventure Continues;;OK;images\2010 - LEGO Indiana Jones 2 The Adventure Continues.jpg;2010;Warez;Traveller's Tales, Feral Interactive;LucasArts, Feral Interactive;17/11/2009;"LEGO Indy is back in his biggest adventure yet. Battle through all four movies, including all-new levels from the original adventures and your favorite new moments from The Kingdom of the Crystal Skull... or in true LEGO fashion, get creative and build your own levels to play with friends!

New modes including two-player drop-in, drop-out split-screen gameplay lets you play together with your friends and family like never before.";Platform, Puzzle, Adventure;INDIANA JONES;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RoX4LnZaZD8;igdb_138;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2024 - Indiana Jones and the Great Circle;Indiana Jones and the Great Circle;Indiana Jones and the Great Circle;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\INDIANA JONES\2024 - Indiana Jones and the Great Circle;;OK;images\2024 - Indiana Jones and the Great Circle.jpg;2024;Warez;MachineGames;Bethesda Softworks;05/12/2024;Uncover one of history’s greatest mysteries in Indiana Jones and the Great Circle, a first-person, single-player adventure set between the events of Raiders of the Lost Ark and The Last Crusade. You’ll become the legendary archaeologist in this cinematic action-adventure game from MachineGames, the award-winning studio behind the recent Wolfenstein series, and executive produced by Hall of Fame game designer Todd Howard.;Puzzle, Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;INDIANA JONES;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1CCQg4JEidM;igdb_142415;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Just Cause;Just Cause;Just Cause;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\JUST CAUSE\Just Cause;;OK;images\Just Cause.jpg;;Warez;Avalanche Studios;Eidos Interactive;22/09/2006;The Agency needs you to topple the dictator of San Esperito. Incite a revolution, ally with drug cartels, or go it alone - Just Cause gives you the freedom to tackle your assignment however you want.;Shooter, Racing, Adventure;JUST CAUSE;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dgaz0xGhBJo;igdb_1042;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
