1987 - Metal Gear;Metal Gear;Metal Gear;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\METAL GEAR\1987 - Metal Gear;;OK;images\1987 - Metal Gear.jpg;1987;Warez;Konami;Ultra Games, Playtronic, Konami;22/12/1987;"The NES version of Metal Gear. It differs from the original MSX2 release in level layout and enemy differences, including an alternative final boss.
