2004 - Prince Of Persia, Warrior Within (Uplay);Prince Of Persia, Warrior Within;Prince Of Persia, Warrior Within;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\PRINCE OF PERSIA\2004 - Prince Of Persia, Warrior Within (Uplay);videos\Prince of Persia Warrior Within (2004).mp4;OK;images\Prince of Persia Warrior Within (2004).webp;2004;Uplay;Ubisoft Montreal;Ubisoft Entertainment;02/12/2004;"Prince of Persia: Warrior Within is a video game and sequel to Prince of Persia: The Sands of Time. It picks up where The Sands of Time left off, adding new features, specifically, options in combat. The Prince now has the ability to wield two weapons at a time as well as the ability to steal his enemies' weapons and throw them. The Prince's repertoire of combat moves has been expanded into varying strings that allow players to attack enemies with more complexity than was possible in the previous game. Warrior Within has a darker tone than its predecessor adding in the ability for the Prince to dispatch his enemies with various finishing moves. In addition to the rewind, slow-down, and speed-up powers from The Sands of Time, the Prince also has a new sand power: a circular ""wave"" of sand that knocks down all surrounding enemies as well as damaging them.";Adventure, Platform;PRINCE OF PERSIA;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/13500/993/50127dd8fa3d8debb14ba687b96b57e4933468d9/1751245956/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447351272;gog_1207659082;steam_13500;gog_1207659082;uplay_121;ps2_52TNLAK0YE;ps2_SCAJ-20154;ps2_17357;ncube_G2OE41;ps2_SLES-52822;ps2_SLUS-21022;vision_NPUB30388;humble_princeofpersia_warriorwithin_uplay;discord_2978cc54-11ad-4f9b-9614-f9764935f0ab;test_b30a1b473bb7adcbaadf8708698c53396708e1af;ncube_Prince of Persia: Warrior Within;vision_NPEB00389;ps2_Prince of Persia - Warrior Within;ncube_G2OP41;snes_17357;test_/prince-of-persia-warrior-within-free-download/;ncube_17357;ncube_Prince of Persia - Warrior Within;epic_3aa2b690c8804bd2988322bc5710d261;ps2_SLPM-66002;test_0521a5fa28bd7a9fba4139e2909df64ca8d35712;generic_51153515939385843;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2005 - Prince Of Persia, The Two Thrones (Uplay);Prince Of Persia, The Two Thrones;Prince Of Persia, The Two Thrones;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\PRINCE OF PERSIA\2005 - Prince Of Persia, The Two Thrones (Uplay);videos\Prince of Persia The Two Thrones (2005).mp4;OK;images\Prince of Persia The Two Thrones (2005).webp;2005;Uplay;Ubisoft Montreal, Ubisoft Casablanca;Ubisoft Entertainment;07/12/2005;I returned home expecting peace. Instead, I found my kingdom ravaged by war and my people enslaved. Now I am a fugitive, hunted by hostile armies and plagued by a curse that is gradually possessing my soul. A darker Prince resides in me now. And I must embrace his powers and skill if I want to restore peace to my land, my people, and my soul.;Adventure, Platform, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up;PRINCE OF PERSIA;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/13530/994/1057e440914b1e23cf7b147382e5fde2121c76fa/1751245956/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447351272;gog_1207659091;steam_13530;gog_1207659091;uplay_113;ps2_MR6OIYM6CQ;ps2_SLES-53777;ncube_GKME41;ps2_SLUS-21287;vision_NPUB30387;humble_princeofpersia_thetwothrones_uplay;discord_63c2e9e0-9ab2-4809-bdff-aab4ca15a44f;test_8db4e8aa9851220e105b7663714e5874e8dd14f7;ps2_21380;ncube_Prince of Persia: The Two Thrones;test_/prince-of-persia-the-two-thrones-free-download/;ps2_Prince of Persia - The Two Thrones;ncube_Prince of Persia - The Two Thrones;ngameboy_Prince of Persia - The Two Thrones;ncube_GKMP41;ps2_SLPM-66391;test_7d7fc89512d4577030c13c403876a5a8b9d8d97b;generic_51153515902311311;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2008 - Prince Of Persia (Uplay);Prince Of Persia;Prince Of Persia;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\PRINCE OF PERSIA\2008 - Prince Of Persia (Uplay);videos\Prince of Persia (2008).mp4;OK;images\Prince of Persia (2008).webp;2008;Uplay;Ubisoft Montreal;Ubisoft Entertainment;10/12/2008;"Prince of Persia is an action-adventure and platforming video game developed by Ubisoft Montreal and published by Ubisoft. It is part of the Prince of Persia franchise.
The game is set in ancient Persia, with a player-character whose name is not revealed in the game. He is accompanied by a woman named Elika, whom he met after a large sandstorm diverted him from his course and he ended up in a mysterious land. Players traverse many different environments using his acrobatic abilities to scale walls and even crawl on the ceilings. Throughout the journey, players combat various enemies as they attempt to cleanse the land of corruption.";Adventure, Platform, Puzzle;PRINCE OF PERSIA;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/19980/1308/012725a26025e70d3c07419e185427805ceb61c7/1751245962/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447351469;gog_1207659109;steam_19980;gog_1207659109;uplay_277;uplay_276;xboxone_2015071396;xboxone_331612077;xboxone_1062052319;humble_princeofpersia_uplay;psn_UP0001-NPUB30424_00-PRINCEOFP0BLURAY;test_3e71b596-3bdb-470d-9b64-392ae54b0799;discord_8ac4109d-41c8-49fa-9f91-00eec62cf9f1;vision_NPUB30424;vision_BLES00390;nwii_JCNE;xboxone_1431504908;xboxone_1480656997;uplay_e98da4a7-0145-4dc2-be09-efa7b36fefe2;generic_51153515599056091;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2010 - Prince Of Persia - The Forgotten Sands;Prince Of Persia - The Forgotten Sands;Prince Of Persia - The Forgotten Sands;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\PRINCE OF PERSIA\2010 - Prince Of Persia - The Forgotten Sands;;OK;images\2010 - Prince Of Persia - The Forgotten Sands.jpg;2010;Warez;Ubisoft Montreal, Ubisoft Singapore;Ubisoft Entertainment;18/05/2010;Prince of Persia: The Forgotten Sands is a multi-platform video game produced by Ubisoft which was released on May 18, 2010, in North America and on May 20 in Europe. The games mark a return to the storyline started by Prince of Persia: The Sands of Time. Prince of Persia: The Forgotten Sands is the title of four separate games with different storylines. The main game was developed for PlayStation 3, Xbox 360, and Microsoft Windows, while the other three are exclusives for the PlayStation Portable, Nintendo DS, and Wii.;Platform, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up, Adventure;PRINCE OF PERSIA;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KmMwCu7scHo;igdb_2468;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
