Resident Evil 2;Resident Evil 2;Resident Evil 2;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\RESIDENT EVIL\Resident Evil 2;;OK;images\Resident Evil 2.jpg;;Warez;Capcom Planning Room 2;Nintendo, Virgin Interactive Entertainment, Capcom;21/01/1998;"Resident Evil 2 is a sequel to the first Resident Evil title. Like the previous game in the series, Resident Evil 2 is a 3D action-adventure using three-dimensional polygon characters over two-dimensional pre-rendered backgrounds, with the action viewed through a variety of cinematic fixed camera angles in each room. Players can choose to play as one of two possible characters; each goes through the same initial scenario but with differences in the type of weaponry they find and the people they meet along the way.";Shooter, Puzzle, Adventure;RESIDENT EVIL;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NW7DmsRKrDA;igdb_880;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
