2007 - Stalker - Shadow Of Chornobyl Enhanced Edition;Stalker - Shadow Of Chornobyl Enhanced Edition;Stalker - Shadow Of Chornobyl Enhanced Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\S.T.A.L.K.E.R\2007 - Stalker - Shadow Of Chornobyl Enhanced Edition;;OK;images\2007 - Stalker - Shadow Of Chornobyl Enhanced Edition.jpg;2007;Warez;GSC Game World;GSC Game World;20/05/2025;S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Shadow of Chornobyl, the first chapter of the Legends of the Zone Trilogy, which started it all. Welcome to the former exclusion territory near the Chornobyl Nuclear Power Plant… the most dangerous place on Earth. Play as The Marked One, face sinister mysteries, radiation-soaked anomalous threats and moral dilemmas, as your decisions determine your destiny in this immersive dark sci-fi saga.;Shooter, Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;S.T.A.L.K.E.R;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PD2i3pQqorg;igdb_343442;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2008 - Stalker - Clear Sky Enhanced Edition;Stalker - Clear Sky Enhanced Edition;Stalker - Clear Sky Enhanced Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\S.T.A.L.K.E.R\2008 - Stalker - Clear Sky Enhanced Edition;;OK;images\2008 - Stalker - Clear Sky Enhanced Edition.jpg;2008;Warez;GSC Game World;GSC Game World;20/05/2025;S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Clear Sky is the prequel chapter of the Legends of the Zone Trilogy. With the ability to directly influence the balance of power through Faction Wars, step into the boots of Scar — a seasoned mercenary, able to somehow survive deadly Emissions. Make your way to the Chornobyl Nuclear Power Plant through radiation, anomalies, enemies, mutants, and conflict-raging Zone.;Shooter, Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;S.T.A.L.K.E.R;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DSP0v0YdAQ8;igdb_343443;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
