2002 - Serious Sam - The Second Encounter;Serious Sam - The Second Encounter;Serious Sam - The Second Encounter;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SERIOUS SAM\2002 - Serious Sam - The Second Encounter;;OK;images\2002 - Serious Sam - The Second Encounter.jpg;2002;Warez;Croteam;Gathering of Developers;24/01/2002;Serious Sam: The Second Encounter, the highly anticipated arcade action FPS sequel to the Serious Sam: The First Encounter, is a high-adrenaline arcade-action shooter heavily focused on frantic arcade-style single player action. In a world where cyberpunk meets fantasy-fiction and advanced technology is mixed with black magic and psycho-powers, Sam travels through the three beautiful worlds, confronting countless Mental's minions on his way to the Mental's base.;Shooter, Indie;SERIOUS SAM;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qvubmHrD0nQ;igdb_858;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
