2022 - Shadow Warrior 3;Shadow Warrior 3;Shadow Warrior 3;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SHADOW WARRIOR\2022 - Shadow Warrior 3;;OK;images\2022 - Shadow Warrior 3.jpg;2022;Warez;Flying Wild Hog;Devolver Digital;01/03/2022;Shadow Warrior 3 launches the offbeat first-person shooter series to the next level with a seamless blend of fast-paced gunplay, razor-sharp melee combat, and a spectacular free-running movement system.;Shooter, Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Arcade;SHADOW WARRIOR;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SUsIYpeR0rA;igdb_135655;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Shenmue 3 (Epic Games Store);Shenmue 3;Shenmue 3;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SHENMUE\Shenmue 3 (Epic Games Store);videos\Shenmue 3 (2019).mp4;OK;images\Shenmue 3 (2019).webp;;Epic Games Store;Ys Net;Deep Silver, Shibuya Productions, ININ Games;19/11/2019;Shenmue III is an action-adventure video game and the sequel to the 2001 game Shenmue II. It follows teenage martial artist Ryo Hazuki in his quest to find his father's killer in 1980s China. In 2015, Suzuki launched a Kickstarter crowdfunding campaign to help fund Shenmue III and the campaign met its initial target of $2 million USD in under eight hours. The campaign ended in July having raised over $6 million, becoming the most funded video game in Kickstarter history.;Adventure;SHENMUE;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/878670/326994/2ed90fbbc365e9b6e20cb773e80a0d696853980b/1751157549/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1605543227;epic_Pepper;steam_878670;epic_Pepper;epic_PepperDummy;epic_PepperDemo;psn_CUSA12257_00;psn_CUSA12289_00;psn_CUSA16480_00;psn_CUSA16491_00;test_CUSA12289_00;humble_shenmue3_standard_preorder_epic_keyless;humble_shenmue3_deluxe_release_epic_keyless;gog_1832790021;humble_shenmue3_deluxe_ww_steam;test_/shenmue-3-free-download/;test_shenmue-iii;playfire_shenmue-iii;humble_shenmue3;humble_shenmue3_choice_steam;humble_shenmue3_choice_epic_keyless;humble_shenmue3_ww_steam;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000007186;beamdog_Pepper;test_Pepper;humble_Pepper;egg_Pepper;itch_Pepper;humble_shenmue3_row_steam;fanatical_shenmue-iii;generic_51154186186071701;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Shenmue I & II;Shenmue I & II;Shenmue I & II;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SHENMUE\Shenmue I & II;;OK;images\Shenmue I II.jpg;;Warez;Sega AM2;Sega, Sega Games;21/08/2018;"""Originally released for the Dreamcast in 2000 and 2001, Shenmue I & II is an open world action adventure combining jujitsu combat, investigative sleuthing, RPG elements, and memorable mini-games. It pioneered many aspects of modern gaming, including open world city exploration, and was the game that coined the Quick Time Event (QTE). It was one of the first games with a persistent open world, where day cycles to night, weather changes, shops open and close and NPCs go about their business all on their own schedules. Its engrossing epic story and living world created a generation of passionate fans, and the game consistently makes the list of “greatest games of all time”.""";Role-playing (RPG), Hack and slash/Beat 'em up, Adventure;SHENMUE;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=juPGbtqe8mU;igdb_96391;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2003 - Silent Hill 2;Silent Hill 2;Silent Hill 2;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SILENT HILL\2003 - Silent Hill 2;;OK;images\2003 - Silent Hill 2.jpg;2003;Warez;Bloober Team;Konami;06/10/2024;Silent Hill 2 Remake is a ground-up reimagining of the 2001 psychological horror game. It follows James Sunderland as he searches for his deceased wife in the fog-shrouded town of Silent Hill. The remake features entirely rebuilt visuals in Unreal Engine 5, over-the-shoulder gameplay, reworked combat, and new voice acting.;Puzzle, Adventure;SILENT HILL;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8qPdInnvMzg;igdb_222341;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2003 - Silent Hill 3;Silent Hill 3;Silent Hill 3;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SILENT HILL\2003 - Silent Hill 3;;OK;images\2003 - Silent Hill 3.jpg;2003;Warez;Team Silent;Konami;23/05/2003;Silent Hill 3 is the third installment in the Silent Hill series. Like the previous entries, Silent Hill 3 is a survival horror combining action-based combat and puzzle-solving, but is somewhat more combat-oriented than the preceding installments. The main character is able to side-step and block some attacks, but in general shares with the other protagonists of the series their relative ineptitude in combat.;Puzzle, Adventure;SILENT HILL;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MLo2WtNN69Q;igdb_482;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2004 - Silent Hill 4 The Room;Silent Hill 4 The Room;Silent Hill 4 The Room;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SILENT HILL\2004 - Silent Hill 4 The Room;;OK;images\2004 - Silent Hill 4 The Room.jpg;2004;Warez;Team Silent;Konami;17/06/2004;Silent Hill 4: The Room is the fourth installment in the Silent Hill survival horror series. The game is similar to the past entries in terms of atmosphere, never letting the player know what's behind the next corner or down the street. Aside from the traditional third-person-view, there is now a first-person mode which is used to control the main character when he is in his apartment. Objects that can be interacted with are highlighted by eyeball icons. The previous games in the series have mostly been about exploring the town and solving puzzles, but this installment has much more combat involved. There are more enemies in a given area, spread in cramped spaces. The main character mostly uses a standard Silent Hill arsenal of weapons, such as the steel pipe, pistol and a golf club.;Adventure;SILENT HILL;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GW_is7yL6_U;igdb_483;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2009 - Silent Hill, Homecoming;Silent Hill, Homecoming;Silent Hill, Homecoming;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SILENT HILL\2009 - Silent Hill, Homecoming;;OK;images\2009 - Silent Hill Homecoming.jpg;2009;Warez;Double Helix Games;Konami;30/09/2008;Silent Hill: Homecoming is the sixth installment in the Silent Hill survival horror series. The gameplay is the same as it's previous entries, where the player searches for objects and uses weapons to defend against grotesque monsters while solving puzzles to advance further into the game. In terms of combat, the player is able to perform light and heavy attacks or mix them to perform combinations. For the first time in the series, the player may select responses when engaging in dialogue with other characters encountered in the game, which in turn may affect how the player sees the plot unfold.;Puzzle, Adventure;SILENT HILL;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=za2iYFR-FhI;igdb_485;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2024 - Silent Hill 2;Silent Hill 2;Silent Hill 2;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SILENT HILL\2024 - Silent Hill 2;;OK;images\2024 - Silent Hill 2.jpg;2024;Warez;Bloober Team;Konami;06/10/2024;Silent Hill 2 Remake is a ground-up reimagining of the 2001 psychological horror game. It follows James Sunderland as he searches for his deceased wife in the fog-shrouded town of Silent Hill. The remake features entirely rebuilt visuals in Unreal Engine 5, over-the-shoulder gameplay, reworked combat, and new voice acting.;Puzzle, Adventure;SILENT HILL;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8qPdInnvMzg;igdb_222341;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2025 - Silent Hill f;Silent Hill f;Silent Hill f;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SILENT HILL\2025 - Silent Hill f;;OK;images\2025 - Silent Hill f.jpg;2025;Warez;NeoBards Entertainment;Konami;23/09/2025;"Silent Hill f is a survival horror game published by Konami as part of the Silent Hill series.
It is set in rural Japan during the 1960s, marking a departure from the franchise’s traditional Western settings. The story is written by Ryukishi07 and focuses on psychological horror, social pressure, and transformation.";Puzzle, Adventure;SILENT HILL;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3r7QnKutko;igdb_222343;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
1992 - SimCity Classic;SimCity Classic;SimCity Classic;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SIMCITY\1992 - SimCity Classic;;OK;images\1992 - SimCity Classic.jpg;1992;Warez;Maxis;Maxis;31/12/1992;SimCity Classic was the later shared name for the enhanced rereleases of SimCity for Windows 3.x, OS/2 Warp and Macintosh, built around their window systems.;Simulator, Strategy;SIMCITY;;igdb_138320;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
1999 - SimCity 2000;SimCity 2000;SimCity 2000;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SIMCITY\1999 - SimCity 2000;;OK;images\1999 - SimCity 2000.jpg;1999;Warez;Maxis;Electronic Arts, Zoo Digital, DSI Games, Maxis;31/12/1993;"It has all the features, flexibility, art, animation, and power you need to create an environment of your dreams. Choose from a selection of bonus cities and scenarios to rule or ruin as you please. Build schools, libraries, hospitals, zoos, prisons, power plants, and much more... Lay down roads, railways, and highways. Explore the underground layer and build subways and utilities without compromising your aesthetics. Customize different buildings or design your own graphics sets from scratch.

This is the ultimate classic Maxis city-building and management simulation. If this game were any more realistic, it'd be illegal to turn it off!";Simulator, Strategy;SIMCITY;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rl5huQdshns;igdb_330;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2000 - SimCity 3000;SimCity 3000;SimCity 3000;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SIMCITY\2000 - SimCity 3000;;OK;images\2000 - SimCity 3000.jpg;2000;Warez;Maxis;Electronic Arts;16/05/2000;In 2000, SimCity 3000 was re-released under different names in different regions, such as SimCity 3000 Unlimited (in North America and Oceania), SimCity 3000 Deutschland (Germany), SimCity 3000 UK Edition (UK & Ireland) and SimCity 3000 World Edition (other countries), among others. This added, among other things, East Asian and European building sets, additional terrain colors and vegetation types, a snapshot feature, additional music, an improved version of the Building Architect Tool (a pseudo-3D design tool based on cubes), four additional disasters (such as locusts and space junk), additional landmarks (like the Seoul Tower and Helsinki Cathedral), new reward buildings, thirteen scenarios (along with an editor based on Microsoft Access) and a new FMV intro. Premade cities are also available, including (London and Liverpool for the UK), Berlin (with the Berlin Wall), Madison, Madrid, Moscow and Seoul. The game also includes city terrains based on the geography of real cities, including Hong Kong and Chicago. At the time of the game's release, EA launched a website for Simcity 3000 Unlimited which allowed users to exchange their creations.;Simulator, Strategy;SIMCITY;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oln7r1AQ4VU;igdb_28955;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2003 - SimCity 4;SimCity 4;SimCity 4;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SIMCITY\2003 - SimCity 4;;OK;images\2003 - SimCity 4.jpg;2003;Warez;Maxis;Electronic Arts, Aspyr Media;12/01/2003;"SimCity 4 is a city-building simultor. You are in the shoes of one or several mayors, and you are tasked with populating and managing your cities.When you have chosen a segment to place your city in, you will be able to chose between 3 game modes.

God mode: This mode lets you shape the overall landscapes as you desire
Mayor mode: In this mode you build and manage your own cities.
