1999 - System Shock 2 (Steam);System Shock 2;System Shock 2;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SYSTEM SHOCK\1999 - System Shock 2 (Steam);videos\System Shock 2 (1999).mp4;OK;images\System Shock 2 (1999).webp;1999;Steam;Irrational Games, Looking Glass Studios;Electronic Arts, Nightdive Studios;11/08/1999;"System Shock 2 is a first-person shooter action role-playing survival horror video game for Microsoft Windows, Apple OS X and Linux. The title was designed by Ken Levine and co-developed by Irrational Games and Looking Glass Studios. Originally intended to be a standalone title, its story was changed during production into a sequel to the 1994 PC game System Shock; the alterations were made when Electronic Arts—who owned the System Shock franchise rights—signed on as publisher. System Shock 2 was released on August 11, 1999, in North America.";Role-playing (RPG), Shooter;SYSTEM SHOCK;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/238210/11489/5163a1ac1c44a160e91d8911fbd60c020d604ac0/1751246660/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447357878;steam_238210;steam_238210;gog_1207659172;humble_systemshock2;amazon_40c4e716-bce6-4526-a4b1-cdb43d5f66b0;amazon_da725ca3-04b9-403d-a520-851b66322098;twitch_da725ca3-04b9-403d-a520-851b66322098;twitch_40c4e716-bce6-4526-a4b1-cdb43d5f66b0;humble_storefront_sytemshock2_steam;humble_retroshooter_weekly_systemshock2;humble_40c4e716-bce6-4526-a4b1-cdb43d5f66b0;humble_systemshock2_fightforjustice_steam;test_238210;test_/system-shock-2-free-download/;fanatical_system-shock-2;humble_systemshock2_turkeysyriaearthquakerelief_bundle_steam;amazon_e4f2f3e7-cc2c-478f-ac8d-720c05b6652d;generic_51154308794316583;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2015 - System Shock, Enhanced Edition (Steam);System Shock, Enhanced Edition;System Shock, Enhanced Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SYSTEM SHOCK\2015 - System Shock, Enhanced Edition (Steam);videos\System Shock Enhanced Edition (2015).mp4;OK;images\System Shock Enhanced Edition (2015).webp;2015;Steam;Looking Glass Studios;Nightdive Studios, Limited Run Games;22/09/2015;"Exactly twenty one years after its first release, System Shock is back! The Enhanced Edition adds a modern touch to this true classic gem, without taking anything from its unmistakable atmosphere. See for yourself that the game that has been called the benchmark for intelligent first-person gaming, has lost nothing of its ability to keep you on the edge of your seat.

You're a renowned hacker, the most notorious cyberspace thief in the corporate world. Caught during a risky break-in, you become indentured to Diego, a greedy Trioptium exec who bankrolls a rare cyberjack implant operation. After six months in a healing coma, you awaken to the twisted aftermath of a terrible disaster. Where are the surgeons? Why is the station in such disrepair? Slowly, the chilling realization that something is very wrong creeps over you.

Once a prime corporate research facility, Citadel now teems with mindless cyborgs, robots and terribly mutated beings, all programmed to serve SHODAN, a ruthless A.I. There's scarcely time to think before it unleashes the first terror...";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Puzzle, Shooter;SYSTEM SHOCK;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/410710/182864/d0c2973a445aa651b32b363791ec7eba7952938d/1750526923/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1536254441;steam_410710;steam_410710;gog_1439995156;humble_systemshock_enhancededition;humble_99d11652-3f58-42f6-8a57-34fb56419dd5;amazon_99d11652-3f58-42f6-8a57-34fb56419dd5;twitch_99d11652-3f58-42f6-8a57-34fb56419dd5;humble_systemshock_enhancededition_steam;3ds_99d11652-3f58-42f6-8a57-34fb56419dd5;humble_systemshock_enhancededition_fightforjustice_steam;test_/system-shock-enhanced-edition-free-download/;fanatical_system-shock-enhanced-edition;humble_systemshock_enhancededition_standwithukraine_bundle_steam;humble_systemshock_enhancededition_turkeysyriaearthquakerelief_bundle_steam;amazon_10ed628c-4e32-40b9-a1e7-a015f5faec31;generic_51154308860203760;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2023 - System Shock;System Shock;System Shock;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SYSTEM SHOCK\2023 - System Shock;;OK;images\2023 - System Shock.jpg;2023;Warez;Nightdive Studios;Prime Matter;30/05/2023;"After 22 years, cyberpunk cult classic System Shock is getting an update. A ""reimagined"" version of the 1994 Windows PC game is in the works at Night Dive Studios for PC and Xbox One, and it's a project that company founder Stephen Kick says he can hardly believe is really happening.";Shooter, Role-playing (RPG), Simulator, Adventure;SYSTEM SHOCK;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LowSorH4dgk;igdb_18375;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2025 - System Shock 2, 25th Anniversary Remaster;System Shock 2, 25th Anniversary Remaster;System Shock 2, 25th Anniversary Remaster;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SYSTEM SHOCK\2025 - System Shock 2, 25th Anniversary Remaster;;OK;images\2025 - System Shock 2 25th Anniversary Remaster.jpg;2025;Warez;Nightdive Studios;Nightdive Studios;26/06/2025;"The original System Shock 2 is a genre-defining experience that established innovative gameplay mechanics that are a staple of the FPS and RPG genre today. Delve through the corridors of the derelict ship Von Braun and immerse yourself in the story rich atmosphere and environments. Explore deck by deck and unravel the horrifying fate of the Von Braun and her crew.

System Shock 2: 25th Anniversary modernizes the 1999 sci-fi horror classic using Nightdive Studios’ proprietary KEX Engine for a definitive version of the game featuring Enhanced Characters, Weapon Models and Animations, Up to 144FPS performance with ultra-widescreen support, Optimized Controller support, 50 Achievements to unlock, Additional Mod Support and Quality of Life Improvements.";Shooter, Puzzle, Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;SYSTEM SHOCK;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iZnBIb6uQHo;igdb_143964;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
