2006 - The Elder Scrolls IV, Oblivion - Game of the Year Edition Deluxe (GOG);The Elder Scrolls IV, Oblivion - Game of the Year Edition Deluxe;The Elder Scrolls IV, Oblivion - Game of the Year Edition Deluxe;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\THE ELDER SCROLLS\2006 - The Elder Scrolls IV, Oblivion - Game of the Year Edition Deluxe (GOG);videos\The Elder Scrolls IV Oblivion - Game of the Year Edition Deluxe (2007).mp4;OK;images\The Elder Scrolls IV Oblivion - Game of the Year Edition Deluxe (2007).webp;2006;GOG;Bethesda Game Studios;Bethesda Softworks;11/09/2007;The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Game of the Year Edition presents one of the best RPGs of all time like never before. Step inside the most richly detailed and vibrant game-world ever created. With a powerful combination of freeform gameplay and unprecedented graphics, you can unravel the main quest at your own pace or explore the vast world and find your own challenges.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;THE ELDER SCROLLS;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/900883/2108/af8f35ae7dbc5cddf5acb4fee7399f51ed04e1f6/1751160477/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1593798301;gog_1458058109;gog_1458058109;humble_theelderscrolls4_oblivion_gotyde_steam;steam_900883;humble_theelderscrolls4_oblivion_gotyde_new_steam;generic_51295396597205909;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
