2009 - The Witcher 2 Assassins of Kings Enhanced Edition (GOG);The Witcher 2 Assassins of Kings Enhanced Edition;The Witcher 2 Assassins of Kings Enhanced Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\THE WITCHER\2009 - The Witcher 2 Assassins of Kings Enhanced Edition (GOG);videos\The Witcher 2 Assassins of Kings Enhanced Edition (2012).mp4;OK;images\The Witcher 2 Assassins of Kings Enhanced Edition (2012).webp;2009;GOG;CD Projekt RED;CD Projekt;17/04/2012;All existing owners of The Witcher 2 received free upgrades to the Enhanced Edition, and could pre-load the update starting 11 April 2012. All new copies on PC and Xbox 360 shipped with the additional content on board. The Witcher 2: Assassins of Kings - Enhanced Edition added over 10GB of new content, including four hours of gameplay, arena mode, new tutorial, 36 minutes of cinematics including a new intro created by Platige Image and an outro, as well as a host of fixes to gameplay and the interface.;Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;THE WITCHER;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/20920/5213/e4879711548fc540635e72ffd86fd6a594e36763/1750484663/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447354275;gog_1207658930;steam_20920;gog_1207658930;origin_OFB-EAST:46853;origin_OFB-EAST:49582;humble_thewitcher2_gog;origin_bce5b93fc2e501d434abbab8b81f348e0de8d1e2b5dbb7c48703826f952303db;origin_56b3123a2f2b7d2e98f883b8be6674701531c410;humble_thewitcher2_gog_keyless;origin_1207658930;origin_20920;test_20920;test_/the-witcher-2-assassins-of-kings-enhanced-edition-free-game-download/;test_gog_thewitcher2assassinsofkingsenhancededition;test_gfn_100363511;test_gfn_20920;test_7868f152a0bfbce5e0ffd6612f6b13390865c15f;test_905bce34e1bde783f745022b26acf35f513f7477;generic_51295405628290947;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2014 - The Witcher - Adventure Game;The Witcher - Adventure Game;The Witcher - Adventure Game;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\THE WITCHER\2014 - The Witcher - Adventure Game;;OK;images\2014 - The Witcher - Adventure Game.jpg;2014;Warez;Can Explode, CD Projekt RED;;27/11/2014;"The Witcher Adventure Game takes players on a journey across the world of The Witcher as they assume the roles of four distinct characters known from the books and video games: Geralt of Rivia, Triss Merigold, Yarpen Zigrin and Dandelion. Each character has unique skills and multiple ways of overcoming obstacles - the choice is yours: do you fight your way to victory, call on your charm, or try your hand at diplomacy?

A variety of quests invite players to hunt monsters, earn gold, and interact with the characters they meet in a web of alliances and treachery - a wild ride that starts as soon as you sit down to play. Players may assist one another from time to time, but make no mistake - there can be only one winner.";Role-playing (RPG), Strategy, Turn-based strategy (TBS), Quiz/Trivia, Adventure;THE WITCHER;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sY_C_vWi4a0;igdb_8765;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2015 - The Witcher 3, Wild Hunt (GOG);The Witcher 3, Wild Hunt;The Witcher 3, Wild Hunt;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\THE WITCHER\2015 - The Witcher 3, Wild Hunt (GOG);videos\The Witcher 3 Wild Hunt (2015).mp4;OK;images\The Witcher 3 Wild Hunt (2015).webp;2015;GOG;CD Projekt RED;Bandai Namco Entertainment, cdp.pl, WB Games, Spike Chunsoft;19/05/2015;"The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt is an open-world action role-playing game developed by CD Projekt Red.

Set in a dark fantasy world, the game follows Geralt of Rivia, a monster hunter searching for his adopted daughter, Ciri, while navigating political conflicts and supernatural threats. Gameplay features exploration, combat, character progression, and branching narratives shaped by player choices. Widely acclaimed for its writing, world-building, and depth, it is considered one of the most influential RPGs of its generation.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;THE WITCHER;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/292030/533367/ee1f58b16da1bccf359c9305bff8193a0f7926f3/1750502482/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1674829921;gog_1207664643;steam_292030;xboxone_1799887933;xboxone_1111111222;gog_1207664643;gog_1425895904;gog_1428055479;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001017;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001016;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0000743;psn_CUSA01440_00;psn_CUSA01439_00;origin_5;battlenet_5;psn_CUSA00527_00;psn_CUSA01441_00;psn_CUSA01470_00;psn_CUSA01490_00;gg_292030;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0000744;test_CUSA00527_00;humble_thewitcher3_wildhunt_gog;nswitch_0100BFE00E9CA000;itch_e24b6f654169e2e8d9622deb5840a9f5b74668f31a21211104f00524;itch_e1b518d66bfc6c08ffc4c4dd0cc056dd2359fa5b93eb954b86160ad9;origin_6fa071681b97926e99e8584f490b30ab585d02fe;origin_c2fb6d80f6b21168e3cd12c86bee994daa7f9a2c;origin_e480ceaedb10cd8a6a789442f22def9b03d2abc1180619b7eed877d88cf280e0;origin_4bf539aaa95923322fcbe63619d8a9b2e6f977f365134e05236cd16657f2bce8;origin_d1b5e504cb1771f0cc7564b6146d6b3a2625fd3cb0ef1cc7cb37080f05ee5369;origin_f13a4b8087602c0d2746d0ff1f0ac259a2628bef;nswitch_0100A0800E9C4000;epic_14ee004dadc142faaaece5a6270fb628;origin_1207664663;origin_292030;epic_292030;test_292030;test_499450;steam_420699;psx_CUSA01439_00;steam_steam_292030;origin_42690;test_/the-witcher-3-wild-hunt-free-pc-download/;test_the-witcher-3-wild-hunt;playfire_the-witcher-3-wild-hunt;humble_thewitcher3_wildhunt_gog_keyless;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0000843;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0001672@gifting;nswitch_01003D100E9C6000;gog_1425982292;nswitch_01