2000 - Tomb Raider, Chronicles (GOG);Tomb Raider, Chronicles;Tomb Raider, Chronicles;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\TOMB RAIDER\2000 - Tomb Raider, Chronicles (GOG);;OK;images\Tomb Raider Chronicles (2000).webp;2000;GOG;Core Design;Square Enix, Eidos Interactive, Aspyr Media;17/11/2000;Tomb Raider: Chronicles is the fifth game in the Tomb Raider series and the sequel to Tomb Raider: The Last Revelation. It was developed by Core Design and published by Eidos Interactive. Like its predecessors, Tomb Raider: Chronicles is an action game with puzzle-solving and platforming elements. The gameplay is very similar to that of the previous games, with the addition of a few new skills. Lara can now walk on tightropes, swing on horizontal bars, and somersault forwards from a ledge while crouching. A grappling hook has been added to her inventory. The game also includes a level editor, allowing the player to create new stages for Lara to explore.;Adventure, Shooter;TOMB RAIDER;no_section;gog_1207663523;steam_225000;gog_1207663523;origin_Origin.OFR.50.0000695;psx_F3OKF6B6S2;psx_Tomb Raider - Chronicles (Europe);psx_SLES03336;humble_tombraider5_chronicles_steam;psx_Tomb Raider - Chronicles;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200409231749;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200409234105;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200409234445;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200409235000;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200409235549;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200409235809;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200410175728;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200410175902;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-1081-20200411074355;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200416082539;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200415212444;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200415202330;beamdog_4cfaae18-5f56-4e59-8400-830c07bbace0;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-4-20200415200541;beamdog_48e7db49-95ea-44b4-8e19-d19f6469c2a8;minecraft_48e7db49-95ea-44b4-8e19-d19f6469c2a8;minecraft_1c70127c-ffdf-4574-836b-b284df8b5aaf;minecraft_a9fa16b2-d