World of Goo (Epic Games Store);World of Goo;World of Goo;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\WORLD OF GOO\World of Goo (Epic Games Store);videos\World of Goo (2008).mp4;OK;images\World of Goo (2008).webp;;Epic Games Store;2D Boy;Microsoft Game Studios, Tomorrow Corporation, Brighter Minds, 2D Boy;13/10/2008;World of Goo is a multiple award winning physics based puzzle / construction game made entirely by two guys. Drag and drop living, squirming, talking, globs of goo to build structures, bridges, cannonballs, zeppelins, and giant tongues. The millions of Goo Balls that live in the beautiful World of Goo are curious to explore - but they don't know that they are in a game, or that they are extremely delicious. Congratulations, and good luck!;Strategy, Indie, Puzzle, Simulator;WORLD OF GOO;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/22000/221257/21672c15713f01e9302f64b5bc27391533e53923/1751245968/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1556898313;epic_Anemone;steam_22000;gog_1421855536;epic_Anemone;humble_worldofgoo_android_pc_soundtrack;humble_worldofgoo;test_Anemone;humble_worldofgoo_freedombundle_steam;humble_steamandroidbundlebta;humble_worldofgoo_steam;totalwar_worldofgoo_steam;d2d_worldofgoo_steam;humble_androidbundle3bibsteam_0;humble_worldofgoo_conquercovid19_steam;test_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200408000828;test_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200408001150;beamdog_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200408125141;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200408214058;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200408223931;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200408233931;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200409003932;gamehouse_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200409080600;humble_GAME_FROM_DATA_FILE-458-20200411074355;minecraft_8c583d4f-3d4f-4f3f-baa4-940ae14a72ae;bethesda_b2a6e23c-9990-4033-8c3a-ca62c522efc9;nwii_WGOE;test_22000;test_/world-of-goo-free-download/;test_World of Goo;test_95df5508-3e99-4911-940d-dc39caa6a87f;test_45f6e9e5-cd9d-40fd-b94c-4b70dcef17e2;xboxone_1631991649;generic_5129543334