Armed with the latest high-powered weapons, the Enforcer is sent into alien hot spots to fight in adrenaline-charged battles that rage on city streets, across rooftops and in the sewers. YOU are the Enforcer.";Strategy, Puzzle, Shooter;XCOM;no_section;steam_7770;steam_7770;gog_1445249599;humble_xcom_enforcer;humble_xcom_enforcer_steam;humble_x-com_enforcer_bundle_steam;generic_51295434216492615;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
