2014 - Xenonauts (GOG);Xenonauts;Xenonauts;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\XCOM\2014 - Xenonauts (GOG);videos\Xenonauts (2014).mp4;OK;images\Xenonauts (2014).webp;2014;GOG;Goldhawk Interactive;Goldhawk Interactive;16/06/2014;Xenonauts is a strategy game in which you control a multi-national military organisation defending a Cold War-era Earth from alien invasion, using small squads of persistent soldiers to eliminate the extraterrestrials and recover their technology in turn-based ground combat. A detailed strategic layer allows you to co-ordinate the defence of the planet, using your interceptors to shoot down UFOs and researching captured artefacts to learn about your foes and unlock new combat equipment to use on your missions.;Strategy, Simulator, Tactical;XCOM;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/223830/21852/a6f98f0677fc3d7b817b1ec37c7e75d40cd64d93/1751246611/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447362294;gog_1207664803;steam_223830;gog_1207664803;humble_xenonautsstrategicplanetarydefencesimulator;humble_xenonauts_bundle_steam;humble_xenonautssteam;discord_031408ec-f94d-4911-b258-96e4ffda7d67;test_223830;test_/xenonauts-free-download/;generic_51295434855004073;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
2016 - XCOM 2 (Epic Games Store);XCOM 2;XCOM 2;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\XCOM\2016 - XCOM 2 (Epic Games Store);videos\XCOM 2 (2016).mp4;OK;images\XCOM 2 (2016).webp;2016;Epic Games Store;Firaxis Games;2K Games, Feral Interactive;05/02/2016;"In XCOM 2, the roles have been reversed, and XCOM is now the invading force. They are hampered by limited resources and must constantly evade the alien threat in their new mobile headquarters. Players must use a combination of firepower and stealth-like tactics to help XCOM recruit soldiers and build a resistance network, while attempting to expose the evil alien agenda and save humanity. 

XCOM 2 will introduce gameplay features such as procedurally-generated levels, which will make each experience unique to the player, as well as offer a much deeper level of modding support. Additionally, XCOM 2 will offer a variety of new content including five updated soldier classes, increased soldier customization, more alien and enemy types, evolved tactical combat and more.";Role-playing (RPG), Strategy, Tactical;XCOM;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/268500/51671/7f347059cb4a0a9fa2d45369a8391397e51fad67/1750499227/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1454648692;epic_3be3c4d681bc46b3b8b26c5df3ae0a18, gog_1482002159;steam_268500;xboxone_551688870;psn_CUSA04530_00;psn_CUSA04552_00;psn_CUSA04554_00;gog_1482002159;humble_xcom2_row_monthly_steam;humble_xcom2_rucis_monthly_steam;psvita_CUSA04552_00;test_CUSA04552_00;humble_xcom2_collection_eu_steam;humble_xcom2_steam;test_CUSA04530_00;humble_xcom2_brazil_monthly_steam;totalwar_xcom2_row_monthly_steam;d2d_xcom2_row_monthly_steam;humble_xcom2_asia_monthly_steam;humble_xcom2_feral_steam;humble_xcom2_india_monthly_steam;humble_2kplaystation_bundle_bt20tier_11;itch_a7e6042470d84dc662ceb84174e25d93cd1509c5c08f8ad253aa5e67;itch_XFxSYWlkc2VydmVyXGdcTXkgRHJpdmVcRml0R2lybCBHYW1lc1xYQ09NIDIgW0ZpdEdpcmwgUmVwYWNrXQ==;origin_bd73086eacdabd3a87bd387e9a9e9532c7ade9ff;origin_d9f9ed44752ddb3f1bfc547cd82504fbe3fc50a65dc23a8342370070652d402a;humble_xcom2_row_choice_steam;humble_xcom2_br_choice_steam;humble_xcom2_rucis_choice_steam;humble_xcom2_asia_choice_steam;discord_cfc8b304-ae92-4894-8554-7def8d687c08;humble_xcom2;psx_XCOM 2;humble_xcom2_india_choice_steam;humble_xcom2_cn_choice_steam;test_xcom-2;playfire_xcom-2;humble_x-com2_europe_bundle_steam;humble_x-com2_row_bundle_steam;humble_x-com2_asia_bundle_steam;epic_3be3c4d681bc46b3b8b26c5df3ae0a18;beamdog_00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000009399;beamdog_3be3c4d681bc46b3b8b26c5df3ae0a18;test_3be3c4d681bc46b3b8b26c5df3ae0a18;humble_3be3c4d681bc46b3b8b26c5df3ae0a18;egg_3be3c4d681bc46b3b8b2