TankHead;TankHead;TankHead;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\_TEMP\+++\TankHead;;OK;images\TankHead.jpg;;Warez;Alpha Channel;;11/12/2024;"Embark on a thrilling journey as Whitaker, piloting a drone-controlled tank through the desolate ECA. Battle fierce enemies, scavenge valuable parts, and fight to survive in this fast-paced sci-fi world, as you strive to reach the mysterious Highpoint.

